eaning after work,final inspection.   Everything done by professionally. I thank you to A batter .","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1NZIs0xxVknpnuleRn8gCE6tzb45Ke9ZnRINbIgy8vFQcSJs3WXf_klsJRB12dIZ-D1vgtKV1q8ZJfrf_RTvk1A7lSRfgl-Kgin7_MyNoaLcG7kx5Zz6SRu5cf8U1hJWLWxBjnScBnplL9=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-27"},{"Name":"Amy Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJ707ePkaYiW9YH19OJ85gSl6nDlurnTmB5_tZUWXXijZzUOZxTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experiences with Alan, Christian, and Alex when I got my roof replaced in 2024 (job included removing many layers of old roofing, tricky skylights, sun tunnels, steep pitch). The crew worked quickly to minimize disruption and the roof looked amazing, and I’ve had no issues! Communication and coordination with other contractors was top notch. Alex came to the rescue again this month (February 2026) as insulators were working in the attic and requested changes. Great communication, reliable, honest, fair bid from the beginning and they stand by their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Quinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjErfJK2Ttcmp-QgS5pbtZN_v3M2KmiEnbbpjVAtyE5yXlcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second roof, replacing one 25 years old installed by same company (still problem free, just older).  Took the crew just one day to tear off and replace.  Impecable clean up.  Still very competitive bidder for the job.  I rarely write recommendations for service providers.  Only when I can recommend without reservations - Better Roofing is one of these companies.  Absolutely a no brainer to go with them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Ondrake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcYy2PyrWQFqABRuCdEgi9mwXiDbAORl7AmD-kBjOLOy8WS8I_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The company was prompt, thorough, clean, and performed precise, high-quality work. The office staff, crew, and the site supervisor showed professionalism and a focus on details. The finished product exceeded our expectations, the price was very reasonable (high value for the quoted price), and the crew left the Job site spotless","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vincent Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-dIWiToyKp6y1Row2YxXkAkXh_gz3OshKk8X-HBuf4MfzuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From beginning to end Better roofing  exceeded my expectations. Pricing was well inside the budget, but the stars of the show were the installers who dis a first class job on everything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tricia McChesney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqK6-0RRZYQgSib-D1_hBSN-iotgyz9whhTLY_NU9X3KZ1yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Better Roofing Company did an outstanding job on our roof. Their bid was competitive and they gave a list of houses in the area that they had completed so we could view.  This company is so professional. The roofers finished the job in two days. They did an amazing job. After the job was completed I was so impressed with the way they cleaned up . We got so many complements from neighbors walking by noticing the roof. The customer service is great. They answer the phone and answer any questions that you have about the job. I would recommend this roofing company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave V. Will","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9X1cFK4zK7DwABQnphYicjj8S7CQUpRyNJrVu38DSAwK_Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Better Roofing Company did an excellent job with installation of my new roof. Old roof was torn off, a few Sheets of ASB replaced, and then new roof installed.  The best part of the deal, besides the nice new look, was that all old materials were totally eliminated (cleaned up) from our property. It looked as if no one had even been there. No damage to any of our plants or flowers! I highly recommend this Company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Bowie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKC1QqU7A7s2Qi6pFSqxcp3IH7i_lhN1U8ZLxoWUIkc4Aq9Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their quote came in well under every other bid that we got from their competitors. I was slightly concerned that a cheaper bid would mean I was sacrificing workmanship, which was not the case. Their work exceeded our expectations in every way possible. Our roof looks great and they stayed within the time frame they quoted. From the estimator coming out giving the quote, to the final walk through and invoice, this was probably the best experience I've had with a company.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1GwzKAr5W93k5LV5mQU16FOB7kWv6McxyZLhPbD5hJdY9GNNA4pcnKWB-N-E--B7PwfKVPMRqTNSrUkWSNxS8ZkaqO2axwVriePW-cN_Wpmw4IT64QAwHffMVGiEc1TzGNgMWJ=k-no"],"When":"2019-11-11"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
