ever experienced with a contracting job. Every day, Jared, the owner, sent videos and photos showing the progress from start to finish, so I never had to guess what was happening on my roof. I was also impressed by Jared's honesty. He actually talked me out of work I thought I needed, which saved me money. He only suggested what was truly necessary and even identified ways to improve our roof's water flow. Finding mold on the roof boards could have been a major stressor, but Jared handled it with total transparency, walking me through the updated bid and the solution. The detail work on our flat top roof is meticulous and perfectly sealed. I also appreciated that Jared is a great resource for broader projects. He coordinated work for our deck replacement and gutter installation, which saved us the hassle of finding separate contractors. To top it off, the crew cleaned the site entirely at the end of every single day. I would highly recommend Rainier Roofing to anyone who values transparent communication and attention to detail.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1i-6j8tENCgw7kVQ6Oco_zw0Hdnw5XXsgAF0E1d5l-do1AZ3uYH3MLX8W4mr4O9Upo8Fo9q8lpbTg2MaTDNaGECz5j_-q-lupQJX5IO2AgebUq_R35Quv_y2fTY4nJWybGyfl59FpNEQW9=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Uft5AEhmLVl7hYdVbvrFHlE1RajlV2Lfap0w4lKrJ4uQcC5uIvoFrSUBsnLE1Eo3kGR4CHHz1-KjviNdTMEj5XjazBQnmfncHbk4DB0M6yFVejvbUR42ZVaql8N53owXIFl_XpkRONgw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn00Bb5cJhUjZHperC0VjmKbFz1nJIoxR_lB0wPOpFqpvUqCAzzZkh6P3PH_qaqz9vKR-Q5fQIcfRwGKmIFo5OJWQCLEr4gAQ59iZeQn8a2VGuTEhB0DvY9TAA1g73lR4FhAx7eUQMNkWgI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Eo-TXphWR6-SleN-00ms5nrqMVINGCCvnovoJGA46ZkzTFEd7H-9Me9fDQx0l119SXpbnYqwEGGI8NtZseL0PoRoDx1yg8YN-YYsuQXkD11U9rPro_PYxAJZFZh-FRf6e6YtQGbePKQbY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FqgTkIRjLBF3DhIuzANVufJWqYm8ZR5LW1CSh4G54YHCm-FMYxC0dSBEN6CGVKtiHR5VKlwGql5CiIPvrKyW7CXFOu2BgBdmkrT91yyQkLpR4BpFte131SzGj8gDpWJP0iSdUmRt619BW=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-17"},{"Name":"David Matthews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL5qwK7qKvxpyhWnQ5u2SmeLcvA4DZvgNL5De3pTuYok33Yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an awesome experience with Rainier Roofing. They did an outstanding job on my Renton home. They redid my roof and installed high-quality underlayment. That truly makes a difference.\n\nA special shout out to Landon who managed my project start to finish. He was incredibly helpful, making the entire roofing process, simple and stress-free. His professionalism and attention to detail managing things really made a difference.\n\nI appreciate the quality of work, their service and their communication.\u2028I highly recommend Rainier Roofing for the roof services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phil \u0026 Jenny Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGzd-_UG9PzZXDWwhXL_U6xZ6ZAi5Bm_TbwiAIvs5_f4uofQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently purchased a new home in need of a roof replacement. After researching roofing companies, Rainier Roofing consistently stood out for its stellar reputation. To ensure thorough due diligence, we obtained multiple bids. Caleb from Rainier Roofing impressed us with a competitive, detailed bid delivered promptly after inspecting our property. He took the time to explain the roofing process, patiently answered all our questions, and encouraged us to reach out with any further inquiries. Caleb also guided us in selecting the optimal roofing materials and colors, sharing photos and addresses of previous projects to showcase their work.\n\nOnce the project began, our project manager, Landon, provided exceptional communication, keeping us informed at every stage with kindness and professionalism. His proactive approach ensured the project stayed on schedule, and his dedication to quality was evident throughout. The roofing crew, led by Junior, was courteous, hardworking, and skilled. Despite heavy rain during the installation, Rainier’s careful weather monitoring and protective measures kept our home completely dry. The project was completed on time, as promised, with outstanding craftsmanship.\n\nFor a high-quality, competitively priced roof delivered on schedule by a reliable and customer-focused team, Rainier Roofing is the clear choice. They earn our highest recommendation.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2n9YkD04Hq-3816uLjYp9CuuHGDno2jXkBeP0juAfAqOk9Bb5LCABGgJoTC1M5cEEaWtoReP8yxeQKFjWRU_rNNlO4Vz5vzHh72hqdZEevpxorZlELFdCEr7NNZ_24Y533OlCmZF2SyC4M=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Z5yrLL5Lz0exPs7AfoLIsT3LjdoTKBAfvIMWMu8HfpC8SeF4iay8d1zNUxk3CCeEbBqNqExaDbek9r8c5q_g5ZNl9RZwd94S49MamdUxlrU4fFKOlGBW8FPEa0_iryazLMABytc8Glv03=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-20"},{"Name":"Morgan Roe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIb7OYMBDyFirMMoL3DlTli02HQJru9kUDo3NImDt9vVuXCUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rainier Roofing is hands-down the best!! I got several quotes, but as soon as I received Rainier’s, I immediately called Caleb to move forward. He was upfront, honest, and never pushed the most expensive option, just gave us clear, thoughtful choices. Our roof was long overdue, and they gave us a realistic worst-case scenario, which we appreciated. Landon kept us in the loop every step of the way, and the crew, was respectful, efficient, and left the site spotless. The finished roof looks incredible, it honestly feels like Christmas! I only wish I had started with them and saved myself time getting other bids.\nShout out to Caleb, Landon, and Junior for a job extremely well done! I will rave about them any chance I get!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Vv2R1TovapKvThVBh_YD3R4cAyXwDaj04ymqAzYZMoXlMPkJ8DcspZvkUyVbrmHpf1jjCKHqKXO5Z34JPX2stoTr0k-Kmg2LOwVdSjYQRXnxw_-97ssPkR4FZjsPbLbmid8BCVpoTdDM=k-no","https://l