e us the confidence that we were dealing with a true expert. Zoom is incredibly easy-going, thoughtful, and makes you feel like the entire job is in capable hands.\n\nSince the replacement, we've gone through periods of heavy rain and are thrilled to report zero leaks! The quality of the work is clearly top-notch.\n\nWe highly recommend Seattle Roof Systems and Zoom for any roofing needs!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
