 that was heavily leaking into the upstairs walls of my house. I am impressed with their outstanding service.\n\nFrom the moment I reached out to Perdigon Roofing, I was met with professionalism and a genuine commitment to helping me waterproof my house. Colin truly went above and beyond to solve my urgent roofing needs. Despite a busy schedule, he made the effort to come over immediately to assess the situation and then on the next non-raining evening to address the issue.\n\nHere are some highlights of my experience with Perdigon Roofing:\n*   Punctuality: The owner and his team were not only punctual but so so efficient. They arrived on time, well-prepared, and wasted no time in getting to work.\n*   Quality Work: The work they performed was top-notch.  The interface between the replaced section and the older roof is really well done.\n*   Cleanliness: One concern I had was the potential mess that comes with roofing projects. However, the team at Perdigon Roofing was meticulous about cleaning up after themselves, leaving my property in a pristine condition.\n*   Communication: Throughout the project, the owner maintained open lines of communication. He patiently answered all my questions, kept me informed about the progress, and ensured I was satisfied with the final result.\n*   Affordability: The pricing for their services was fair and super competitive, especially considering the speed and quality of work delivered.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ec1NhVAejj8iftYWMh-KzAVRPek0_L2QcYMESiTcol4sHaqnJVNghzYMbGIyC48nTiFnypS_tc9wkkszVb5rfxKNl3DUFe2E5BOUt9YErIBEhdtCAqobEqokGERi6qjIgF4kk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2YVKfYJvfI75kbFjGoNeNmTYNu0n9hK-6wLp5dFu-tSEQrToU_4x7TAtDJ6z1_osA_JmvlMrNd0JlErE_QDkTuyqhHUDRjKSss_iaQOXvDHS_sAPYG2HhlEZtfwHxMagODlmmo=k-no"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Cody Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXESd8M8u_k-ZtSbGXv6dkX_MbJSeh8QJ8u8phQkF3OlGqlFu4=s120-c