m in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"pretty kitty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-aDSqHhP802LNDKVNSxze5PUb3vWJvzfbAe1gSrI16A5gxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding professionalism from Pacific Roofing Company Seattle, they explained everything they were going to do, recommended the best materials for our chimney and siding, they are really knowledgeable when it comes to any exterior work. They are hard working, punctual, they keep the area clean, and they always do what they say they are going to do. We got 4 other quotes but we truly felt like they were the best option because from the start it felt like they care the most and put in the most effort. We’re glad we chose them at the end, our new chimney and siding look amazing. I would definitely recommend others to work with them too.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
