 and Diamond and I owe him a nice bottle of wine for doing so.  Obviously getting a new roof is at best a twice in a lifetime event that can be stressful with all the roofers and options out there. Eugene was a pleasure to deal with.  Always transparent with options and updates.  His crew was professional and left the workspace spotless.  Most importantly the roof looks great and it was done at a reasonable price compared to the other estimates I received.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alan Abrahams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHGwGWsp7KBG5Qj9YcshKjmUuL7BY1TBqSwZFPIw-uzQJFknJdUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got several quotes  for my re-roofing project and Diamond Roofing \u0026 Construction came in with the best quote. Eugene's team did an excellent job and he kept me informed of the progress throughout. Eugene's team went around the house after completion and cleaned up any leftover debris. I highly recommend Diamond Roofing \u0026 Construction.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Christoffersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw0yWbkfgbokIBGx-sBt_dcqgCtrpNVqNjeOPy4SSeS-rY8Bat=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely good work. I feel like I paid a fair price and the work is way beyond my expectations.\n\nI'm usually the guy that fixes my friends and older neighbors roof problems, but replacing a roof was too much for me. I have been planning a new roof for 3-4 years and spent the time surveying work done around where I live. Diamond Roofing did my neighbor's house which had a flat roof and I was very impressed by how they consistently overlapped the sheets correctly. Beautiful origami on a difficult roof.\n\nI called for quotes and their price came in at about the middle.\n\nI was keen to have a bunch of tiedowns on the roof after they left - more than is strictly necessary and they were happy to oblige. I opted for malarkey legacy shingles in silverwood. It is a color with higher reflectivity so keeps the house cooler in the summer since the house has no ac.\n\nI was there watching for 2-3 hours every day of their work. Great precise work on every step. Each and every fitting that pierces the roof was beautifully sealed. My old kitchen vent box was ruined so they provided one.\n\nPictures show what a nice job they did. No pictures but they also did a perfect job cleaning up.\n\nThanks Eugene and especially the crew. You guys are amazing and *really* know how to work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3abvWGWcAhe1pHjreBTHZDoIJr_-s3s_xWK4xrkgtw2au1DME1DSrr3DRzoYwYmxQ97offB07C-cno3JSUzaqpcDU8UQgnjoChqeAWoVu-d9VUl9Gx8FtWbC8tbeFS_rtAnESqQ6mOmlM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3RpUPRnvyGU28mq8nZVC32DOfWhwgWLAEdhXxZoI2YvahTeAxCNuKyThgsy-1lrdZsxlEBPJ6zef60Wi5UiNChBvmjaHXV14PeefA77M9fs-iA13kH1750cTFP5iBvk6PlPzENfB2M--qW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vO0hpucQflEEmnlupyJXX8CDXwMy1PUBe98JJsRyeC21vy5N8d-8rdWyZ7AVWrBPph4ClllgDzI3rk1Vf3s8ihndqV88dtDl1_sAOK4Bit01zBEE-gOs08VoiR8_YYxL5TVasouB2kS_b=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0CrXN9QuL1Ctwx8cGmFvxzPR_1vAqM6JayedJq3-0wu5vEnGMVN-zkL9rkyyJv8-CWaRBE3HQ9ZKueCoMq3MqQeAMGMH1s7tqGqBrnc_93WgdTrOvsqFf8h8qVjoQtGnhLGGZx5xRtxIA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QIue2ymBIZt0vg3oP2JMPz_q8Vo1HlI7giIBW9MvWc2Z_qEvWeBAHva6388nNqgrJDNvA3kRru6-OE6iYFXrT9NYhn5c093-2zE4PKQgOJOljEg8ZZLPBEPeDnoWmeWhdgJP4O9nF-S0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0fj0ZufRL7aXaNefL9Q4MBWlq1avt35lNAG1-bgATVVWTFInC9xN8HJfJNIEMqDBb7h8zulvHXILK4O3isD7926lPaG9YeKEr3hD9_eTTKmJj4nuyTrXE8M4uba6belMFUsWFoDwUk17g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0TQYEPho9hktfIfajZcSK1PtBES7s_23vi11ZO4JoC5yrqKqP8JIOTpqzhpKpZOwpfNRIWzN55T7EJNxPa_HnYDGPf-j-enriCWH8ECM7KQNDoycLoxecgpoFU4r4WpL_PnA8keDymKes=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1YR0_l5kUF1EGRFiMWm5