rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would Highly Recommend Diamond Roofing to anyone wanting an honest bid, hard workers and good communication.\nDiamond Roofing is an awesome company to work with. I called and asked for a quote due to the reviews I read about the company. Eugene responded within a day and I got the quote within a couple of days. The estimate was right in the ballpark of others and lower then some.\nMy roof was old and I lost many shingles due to the bomb cyclone in November. I had hoped they could start soon. Sure enough Eugene was able to put me on the schedule for the following week.\nEugene and his crew were great. They kept me informed of all that was happening and Eugene would send me photos all along the process. The job was started on a Tuesday and they finished by Saturday morning. They worked hard and the site was cleaned up at the end of the day.  I was very impressed by their work ethic.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VMT7K2xSFxQ0fnp-h8wF5_czAOn53RFzNWk0ZtB7WTiEXXugUaOOZEehMK__RT37fPrsTvCduv4hKrE4JhF9FQJo1fEXz6_bEIuTGE3njliNeIiO8xIlk3kSznZJNf1T66A73XA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FcDN2FjUCQwNWDUAMjTK49A4l9j6zZPLUVs9iUdWJv_xHcGSOJ9FbKxeHwrcoJwWIWI3SKhlBaifmjwhzgEbmXwe9wC0pXsn7g_B1fnDrhTw55Q9NndCKMBTn9jG6y7kBcoYH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pS_L4LNgyt6244__cJC73W5rO8ZKRfTq2OgR7n1778AQg7BH5jLsbvi7ZrAw-xVaQhKUJtymyWqACqjnXp4ZguU3owMZr21ovBcTXCghye9hBvaMm9qtEmYNRFBR9PACNb9xCvQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cWCbIOXSq_bUAMgZIFinC5uOsXl6VLHSopRhyqp7f3h9Hin0VnG3ziSYlW1Stj5q3KsYa4ylzfnuLILMClQLps6RxZQDTyAr6Q0c8ifKX36tneg25Ffma02dNebtUQPnQddDq=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0psDnwionUQZZzls5lJ3kXJWVNzjiIJ-7yurQvu0cqkDr7JyCIJ7sdZ07KI4aZT-USm2IotUm85tS_9q1Gleuk7Z7xpykzL5wHktXngo-brDRMJH0AxNiHcq-JU1INyvzIwAFlcw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39pL-MpFfzDoTowPavrb442XLPmLP_TIWJfQZzEHzx-kBujX0UGInNgjP21NDBanCeUsZMZ_FYDPoA4sqafx5Z3PP8QyuyNxGlx0MrFc5NYD5Kvy6WwZHqzPuxt-EE4VJbxXzV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2hCT1J7s9v8Lifig-iiBww8NAZ2dBgI0yyrZEoTpPGX2EWg-9wzBnGMlbGr3qu7TOj4RTkIphW2x_nra9h1iJanLSx5yHKwBhq3FIydakHH3Hz2yJuzUyZ69W45aUEE7atheG_wA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2OETJuWumREYxcDDHzPTvUZR9s1NZNTqrydt4Ka_yVMlBoFtVLL9aguv4WNnpJY-Vmiw9GlGptZoXadD-_oDTtYQluLo926n3YvEozqTdM0EEFIgtUPEZIuw8JEjNp2WaD-POe=k-no"],"When":"2024-12-30"},{"Name":"Shu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkk5H0UKkWzdvD4f2TewnRpxUY2MPY9gE50THnsQT1aJ9KNGPC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eugene and his team did an awesome job replacing our roof. I would highly recommend Diamond roofing for anyone who wants the job to be done with a great price, reliable work and clear communication. I found Diamond roofing through google review and I hope my review here could save others some time finding the right contractor/company for their roofing project. Here is my story:\n\nShortly after contacting for a free quote, Eugene showed up and went through our project. Unlike other company’s salesman, he inspected around the house, and explained the process with professional opinions including potential saving points. Once the quote is out, he answered all my follow up questions, and revised the contract for multiple upgrades upon my request. All the communications are in-time and clear, the quote price is pretty good compare to other competitors, and I decided to sign the contract with Diamond roofing.\n\nThe work started on a Tuesday morning and completed by Saturday. Throughout the week, Rene and his team members always started work early in the morning. Unfortunately I have to stay at home during the project and hear the noises. But this also gets me the first-hand experience to share that I DID see the crew worked so hard and paid attention to the details; Rene was on site all the day and supervised team member’s work from time to time, and Eugene followed up with me for questions and shared tons of photos everyday.\n\nA specific thing to call out is about our skylight. The original skylight is not the standard size and model. Eugene and Rene figured out a solution quickly and explained to us for approval. The solution requires additional wood frame to support the skylight. Rene painted the wood frame to match our dry wall. Check my photos, it is beautiful and looks like an original design. In the end, our skylight got upgraded to these fancy ones with remote controller, and my kid got very excited about it.\n\nOnce the project was completed, Eugene took a final check of the roof and reminded me multiple times that once the trash bin is removed from our driveway, I shall sweep the driveway again in case any nail was left.\n\nI do not have the expertise to judge if the quality of their work is really good or not, only the time will tell. But for what I experienced so far, the team is professional with their on time work, rationale to pay attention to details, in time response, and clear communication. Our new roof looks beautiful and I would recommend Diamond roofing for others to get their premium service.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VABaGvrdL4f6yY7Gx8acev05LNC5-dlkRtDCeMctfJ87CnRCt42fpiVwCwauibsV0FJpCAGPjbDuMnffAHbreNhvA4o1mcGT114ni0bmVgOTkz9Bo7F_Z-gxaxGBq2mMY5iWU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ncYVGyaXKkEmopuxkj-2HTK1k2ySzETmE6e4FzCwXn9RQMGBiGIyBEPsF3Vlr_kFtZwIx6-nc6pMg2fJvdqFhjNkHWeIyv6XbSUKKxAXCQctLMC9fbJwKLwlqKjjl_Eg25tXykw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3HdtKnpWevz6MbBbjN5oyjZqD6Ikv1m2THLmhx3tP2_08d8ChRIIATGVzMUoc9IBHPQRFnn2lnTct88g2lGYvz_fn_kcu2fQdhePqwXIdWj1owUS_1wnLt7BNGOwdvhOcnqic=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2RIb-H0vPfAP1WRKDmgwkmHL8vCLzp-vzriZVPxVfxx-t0jsb0sifoDu2Oeilycc4WrKgIeEgI8DMu_y9y931UWEQU_A99vujMYoGVQ_Eay-rwh_glx7-KpPOEMKrk2bqHHm