},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Lucy Milojevich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYm2YzYu0MwQWexVvVsdb1Zx-4TaddjoW7u5-FXfrWJAA_sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Valentine Roofing came quickly when I found out I had some leaking in my roof. They gave me an excellent and fair bid, and I admired that I gave them an opportunity to sell me new gutters, and they said I honestly didn’t need them!\nThey did my roof in less than two days and the crew was diligent and cleaned up so beautifully and were so careful with all the details! Plus, they got me in very quickly in a short window of no rain And used roofing materials with an excellent warranty! I have already recommended them to several people and will continue to!\nThank you for your excellent work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Len Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIomt6GcuHYmcVlMOyOb7SR_-MH_y2eLcv3ZxEh_f-hKkkR7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dani and his crew did an excellent job removing the old roof and installing my new roof.After a couple of delays for weather the crew arrived and started work and you could tell that they worked together before because they each had a job and did it. All the two days they were here I never saw any one not working.\nThey replaced several sheets of damaged decking and installed a new venting system for the attic and were done in two days including cleanup.My yard was actually cleaner than when they arrived. Any question I had on what and why on some items where answered to my satisfaction.The materials used were very good quality.I had researched all the materials used so I knew beforehand what was being used.\nThe large dumpster was removed the following day.\nDuring the whole process the company kept me informed really well as needed. I should not need another roof for at least twenty five years or more but I will happily refer anyone  I meet needing a roof to use Valentines. They were thorough and made the project as painless as possible.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RQnp5wAiFyc3-VYy7baC3RRsl1R7GjFX2czL_h9F-wuB3w_e0S6ArhdWGQZibVasupqhsra7fnBrCYqgecbR7xNiibUU0W4qLfpjvlHNEkq9Nro8mFmSa-2gxk0RHpeN32ETl6I9JHYQ=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-23"},{"Name":"Sandy Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOI3Ow38KVwMaEhJFMjN-uqfFNa44ajy0iR7wilS4LkWgKUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are very pleased with the service we received from Valentine Roofing. They have always done a great job cleaning our vinyl membrane roof , as well as cleaning out our gutters. They also added exterior window washing at the last minute, and the windows look great! The Valentine Roofing staff are always respectful of our property and never leave a mess. Thanks, guys!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dwyer Gruver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5yPmwom88XuSYXLu0I1tFuWmw2dS8oJ8hURjnDim9-1Qkjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Blake texted me the morning of my appointment giving me his ETA. He arrived on time and immediately started to work. He efficiently cleaned my roof, gutters and washed my windows.  Blake was professional, courteous and effective. I would highly recommend Valentine Roofing and truly appreciate the work Blake completed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marilyn Dohogne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXktyTieDFr_ExnmRjfoT7eeiAq60Lu75Ewg8FFIaPXwW0Lw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alex Courpas was referred to us by our realtor on some inspection items that we wanted peace of mind for closing on our house April 2. Alex has excellent customer service. He was very thorough in looking at some discoloration in our attics, Insulation, checking flashing at the edges of our roof, vents and gutters and explained in great detail the conditions Of these items which he reported to be still in great condition. I would highly recommend Alex to any of my friends, neighbors, etc. to get a roofing estimate. Excellent job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yi Fan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXivobv7sHzGyG7YUvSFUbbY1GChFWJy1SRhfwN8EuOvBwIeeY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We felt incredibly lucky to have Gwen as our neighbor on Whidbey Island, and her service in selling our home was truly fantastic. She managed the sale of our Oak Harbor home while we were away in China. Being overseas during a home sale could have been stressful, but Gwen made the entire process feel organized and under control.\n\nOur home overlooks the Saratoga Passage on Whidbey Island, and Gwen gave us thoughtful, data-driven advice about pricing, timing, and market conditions. When it didn’t sell initially, she recommended taking it off the market for the winter and helped us adjust our strategy with confidence.\n\nDuring our absence, she regularly checked on the property, coordinated contractors, and kept everything moving forward. Through her strong local network and skilled negotiation, she secured an off-market sale and guided us through pricing and repairs. We always felt informed and able to make the best decisions for our situation.\n\nIf you need a knowledgeable and trustworthy real estate broker on Whidbey Island, we highly recommend Gwen.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendel Patterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL19G01kmsC6F3zirCqXSHVcxyY-2RR2DyWduEkAChGoRJpbg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I delt with Chris from Valentine roofing. He was relaxed, and very kind. We had a great conversation, It was a premium job he was describing. He addressed our concerns and explained all aspects of the project in detail. Most of all he wasn't high pressure.\nI would work with Chris and Valentine in a second.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liz Mitchell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKc-WwCeUkBY2BL4nQN0AHdj5IZZychUToh9kpYukO0lGF4GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Heard about Valentine Roofing on a local podcast and decided to give them a try after the most recent storms.  We needed our roof cleared of debris and gutters cleaned out.  Last time we had this done (with a different company) they were up there for maybe an hour or so, quick job so that's what I was expecting.  The pricing with Valentine seemed a little high at first when I thought of the last time we had this done.  I was wrong!  Valentine did an AMAZING job and were so thorough.  Not only were the gutters cleaned, they checked and treated the roof where needed for moss, meticulously cleared the roof of debris (we have a pond that they needed to avoid), and cleaned up everything when they were done.  They were here most of the day and the roof and gutters look amazing.  The technician was extremely polite and communicated throughout the process.  Worth every cent and we have signed up for their yearly maintenance as well.  Would highly recommend and we will also be checking out some of the other services they offered.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
