lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8_iNJLVY-XOORmKgMjlp58towFcTo86JxZSgnJs6X1DOO9eI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently upgraded our roof from a basic builder-grade shingle to a premium shingle with a full lifetime labor warranty provided by the roofing company, along with a 50-year manufacturer warranty — and we could not be happier with the entire experience.\nFrom start to finish, the customer support was amazing. Every question we had was answered promptly, and the process felt organized and professional the whole way through. The crew was respectful of our home and incredibly thorough. They kept our yard clean at the end of every single day, which we truly appreciated, and did a very detailed final cleanup once the job was complete.\nOne thing that really stood out was that they sent an inspector out afterward to verify that everything was done properly. That extra step gave us so much confidence in the quality of their work.\nWe absolutely love our new roof and highly recommend this company to anyone looking for quality workmanship, strong warranties, and outstanding customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"brian hsiao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCSkCCRFSdbSWMvmwHrgt9BjQT9S8lZUQ4_Z75IUemfKcvsrzd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had great experiences with Pro Roofing on our new roof.  Great communication from quoting, starting to completion of project. Crew on site were very professional and efficient.\nWe were very pleased with the results.  Highly recommend them.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0JrxwwdPf59Dh1nDljaE9ICqp9V-c4y-Lghff25X_r5kxSnS9REuhiFC3_rfhM-uu34moWLhV4aGqg-O8cGscrWol5L9DD7L4QsVSYYqczpvPlRdfyMOHkwa7JC8YizD6hkKpo_fGf4pB0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37RAsVYu4qSQ7KOKim_KQA9cXjVac-omb2FJdsCibp1qqy7VbaYBYKDiGmvv8ERhTnlwGYUYrw0aPize3FjijcVpq0J11kkaaYfzynOeckv34SeV7RF5ctVbC49xgvG3iY7w5wnKmiEUbv=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-11"},{"Name":"Ankit Sud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA_6WbUhLAMzYhDuj-anNF-3N37u8oMjNXFdo68sJh1aaZoSkzLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"While the company was prompt in their initial outreach and provided a quote quickly, the proposal included products that were ill-suited for my specific needs. For example, they included 'Oceanguard' paint, a product designed for coastal, salt-water environments, despite my property being located inland and offered me a more expensive 24 gauge option when its not really needed for a residential roof.\n\nAlthough the initial interaction was friendly, communication ceased after I asked for a revised quote without the unnecessary upgrades.\n\nThe pricing was significantly higher than expected (2nd highest out of 10ish quotes i had), which seems to reflect a focus on premium upselling rather than providing practicalsolutions. I recommend potential customers scrutinize their line items carefully before signing.\n\nWhen I told the company I never heard back the salesperson told me he didnt get any messages, despite twice telling me he would send me a revised quote and never bothering to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7RekiHgo025Xd6zqbtyPd6o89Ilm6Af_xPjfdS-Wom7QyKN0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I used Pro Roofing NW for both a full re-roof and gutter repair/cleaning. In both cases, Pro Roofing NW has had very competitive pricing, great communication, and has come in on or ahead of schedule. (One company quoted me twice their bid!) When I needed roof decking repairs, they sent pictures as proof and quoted a low price per sheet (especially compared to the other bids). They carry multiple manufacturer certifications, which not only gives you a longer warranty, but also means they consistently follow the high required standards of installation. I’d high recommend and use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ethan Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI2nRM2d-vRgjnTha4_Wm_esosCO1PFkSY5vMC3gLkD__ysccUWA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After looking at several quotes for our roof replacement, it was clear that Pro Roofing NW was the team to pick. Not only did they offer a very competitive price, the warranty and variety of products they offer was unbeatable. They provided clear communication leading up to our start date. On installation day, the team was efficient and professional and left the property in great condition. I can tell that they provided great craftsmanship and stand by their work. Absolutely recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate Barr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsnFbYFg7HHgamuIyMrcQ0wx4PQvqwf0U3GIDglKfzy9TuTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pro Roofing NW performed a roof inspection for me, and as a result they carried out a small repair project. The inspection seemed comprehensive and the summary and photos they provided afterwards made the results easy to understand. The price they quoted for the work was very reasonable. Christian was very responsive to all inquiries, and the tech on-site was clearly experienced and efficient. I would easily recommend them to a friend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Carey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0G1kJeZGm8MNoaSyGj4XcokS9NqgiZN6S8JGhbW_lzJpSTcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The crew cleaned the roof and gutters.  They did a great job and also cleaned the debris around the house and on the outside walls and windows.  I will definitely use them again.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
