ntent.com/a/ACg8ocIuwjQcYNOwDn48xmC2ieeprNAzoMfWLRqvhs3I0bHFfK92cg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service! I hired this roofing company and they were absolutely great arrived on time, worked quickly and efficiently, and delivered high quality results. They were professional, responsive, and made sure I was happy with everything.\nHighly recommended for anyone looking for reliable and skilled roofing work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leam Tait","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnn0Bk45j59rGenNbOZqw2-vcUZpmFDVBf7i5q7ETtPdRVQW4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Near Me Roofing Company rebuild our roof, gutters, insulation, attic vents, and all of their components totally. It was an extensive project that did an excellent job. Ari took the time to go over all of our options, thoroughly address all of our concerns, and even provided colour advice for shingles when I was having trouble deciding. He and his team were kind and professional. Our home appears beautiful, updated, and brand new. They professional roofing company in kirkland, WA. I would highly recommend. Thanks!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Coral V.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhiQmKRUScoAlsFLTRgf-Aao7eigUHhLGvMx-KEOO4-CSy_3k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Near me roofing responded promptly to out service call. They came out to our home and helped us inspect the roof \u0026 the attic. They were very informative and professional, we eventually went with them after taking over 8 estimates because we were confident in their presentation \u0026 transparency.\nThey removed our previous roof and installed a new one,  they did an amazing job, they were very thorough and worked professionally.\nI would definitely recommend their services as I am very satisfied.\nThank you guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"chatie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITcaQKzP8N3b01lqqUwtY6Kimy4OhVf-opIcr_btZ1OBvRYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very glad to have chosen Near Me Roofing Company.  It was an amazing pleasure to see a steady progress to finish.  Ari with his roofing, skylight, and gutter team were very professional, quick, and responsive.  I was really impressed when I got status at the end of each day on the progress and could ask questions.  Also, I was shown pictures as work was being done on my roof to completion, and I found that really helpful and informative.  I still remember how nerve-racking and confusing it was in choosing a roofing company and am very glad and relieved to have found Near Me Roofing Company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Demner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs7iRIIEl0ey_sChSP4x1blaVCJ8hnL_W7NnhbvPdX7y742w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In May 2021 I purchased a home that needed a new roof.  I made a few calls and Ari from Near Me Roofing was one of the 3 companies that came to provide a bid.    One of the company sent a subcontractor that came and went without my knowing and sent me an estimate but I had some questions and it took days to contact someone to answer my questions.  A second one came and went, they also had no contact with me but let me know they were coming.  Ari came and introduced himself, talked to me and helped me out with some of the issues surrounding my roof.  He was very professional, friendly and personable.  His bid came in the middle but the bid seemed to include all costs so I felt like there was not going to be any additional charges later.  The next strange thing to happen was that I was unable to proceed with the replacement until Oct.  Ari periodically would check in to see how things were going and when the time came kept the bid at the same price.  The weather had changed and he kept in contact as to when there was a good window to replace the roof.  His team showed and completely all the work in one day.  They were efficient and professional and did a great job.  I would definitely recommend Ari and Near Me Roofing.  Not everyone needs to talk to a roofer but I was thrilled that Ari was there  to help me out.   He also contacted me when it was over to make sure I was satisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI694gXy4ooXocp2Up-5oPtMV_VBJFQoH1FrVBN4t0xapFsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Near Me roofing company came out for an emergency roof repair and had the job done in 24 hours! And they did an excellent job. Don't hesitate to use them. Thank you Elijah for the good work!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shanna Ruby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkQ3Bwz7Az8UrUDlLqTJKSfn_XBmNoT51O-3ouX1uIDEI5cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the estimate to the installation, they are extremely professional! In the last 1 years, I've used many  roofs on  different places, and I won't use anyone else in the future! The greatest roofing around me is Near me Roofing company. Their employees Elijah and julian were so efficient. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
