s the project manager for my company. He was responsible, professional, and a great guy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kuyoc Itza Misael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdo2ZsyWmDSJTv5krkHmhaJfL5GnKXWyz1y6xoJfNJggxi-eco=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Oscar and his crew did a great job. They were fair-priced and very thorough. The leak was identified and repaired in just a few hours. The repair was done in a clean manner and the area was cleaned afterwards, so I couldn't tell that they had been there. Oscar is my first choice for all roofing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saba Saba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFhtLr-IHpdr_W81yI-dLhGS8LzC2WfD_XdGlmc5vg7b8MHj0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chase and his team were great. They helped me work through the insurance approval process and were patient, even to the point of connecting me with an adjuster to navigate my replacement approved when the insurance company was not responsive. I would not have gotten my roof properly taken care of without their help. My results were great and my roof looks great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hemanshu Dabas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwwLSrDoaVu2Kq13IKuuqknj1cFHWYh7qiV7CI2k5Rp7BVmRME=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience. Ty countess helped make the whole process easy. Brantley and his team did a fantastic job. My roof looks fantastic and no longer leaks. They are highly recommended to anyone and did all of this for a very affordable price.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
