wd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Perry Sproed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfAFkMsyRbZu3f1m9XM83h8BJRnwthXcNCJk080G0CaKvyo6dC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an absolutely fantastic experience with Summerflex Roofing! The entire process, starting with the estimation, was incredibly easy and straightforward. Communication was top-notch; they always answer the phone, which is rare and hugely appreciated.\nThe work itself was done professionally and efficiently—the crew completed our entire roof in just one day! They were very friendly and polite. What truly set them apart was the cleanup: they actually mowed the lawn afterward to pick up any tiny debris, leaving our yard cleaner than they found it. We highly recommend Summerflex Roofing for their speed, quality, and exceptional attention to detail!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Valter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvWITbWsGCN3qVr6r1nVQFstsJSULASSG02TdaJDwNvbMk1qs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So I have been loyal to another roofing company for years, until recently when they told me to simply caulk an interior window for a leaking issue I was having in my kitchen. This felt super wrong, so I called Summerflex and they came out within just a few days to check things out. Within about 10 minutes, their site manager found several problems that no doubt saved my roof and possibly the rest of my home from further damage.\n\nThey came out just a week or so after that, dodging rain, storms, and such, but working tirelessly to discard rotted materials and replace things in a way that blended seamlessly. They even redid all of the flashing on my house, not just the part that had been done poorly by another company leading to the damage.\n\nThey also texted along the way, anytime they were running late or headed my direction. I was never in the dark about what was going on.\n\nIn the future if I ever have another issue, they are on my speed dial - every good review you have seen regarding them is 100%!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1_8_03NT1Zm6wAItxVPqBt2In9Nhgqc2cH-KPPyYegl3Wl1RcfK_fUoopwqFlUpUFG3GyMWrHnwlhHJfXQI-TIMuYLDcfetpDa-I1OPY-u-ntjSvVTDcdFsjAHdOPLsVYUjtQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0JtWKFHFKi8ZenCNnUarhXAP4O9hFbVlv0pURCtkHn5XNWZnbP8xWueowF5h7om4OTRAGo81JME_XBuetuUeYmT7ghEilcqSMNEAqfm9B9V01KaUwlrPZZ7oBhNo1wUKEUNDP9uA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3kyZVxJGVVMLwHdNPuD8snY3DSK304OB5nqi_9scL1_k2acU1Tt_0a_aut-xU55ONh692-O7PEOWTBOvgdjqZDlYx9-nKHb3sjVWrFYLLUGXBRVbveN1ce0Aaj0KG4gYr3ALgl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3dyDwkrnHOkwCGi0eL3M1C1hZ8RwSN_YLJEgV3bNexyVs_IfzYIDDxJ_tiJAjUosPUaaqrwM2Y4-YJzTohA-wsnVdXt9pbza_QkqDth3m6ScDvw0oMTztMWvWFO6LLoYRiLfhloQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0O8b98ffLQKfV9TVNWyD_gnI3MVSFnmO3JGUqJ7u-DT7ulM1uJLCrhSLKcWZmzfAnQUm67s8yvXS6phV1ZDQLDKSVhKCvKRy2LRW5LuF4n8o2fRx9ZWnsDWK5SO3WWBIrXmMY=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-25"},{"Name":"L B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4BVzW-vi9ezel4cEJqEYmRq6_h9YgHw9y5ZQGVC9LDmJTLN7fwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Summerflexx did a great job on our roof after a tree fell on it in November: they were prompt, had great communication and reasonable prices.\nI had every intention of using them for larger scale projects--like replacing our roof in a few years-- but I haven't been happy with their customer service after the project was done and there was a smaller project we asked them to do-- repairing a hole in the roof that rodents were coming through. After giving an estimate and agreeing they could do it in early November,  communication devolved. First, I got a message back that said because our project only takes about two hours, they needed to fit it in between other projects, so \"the timing was flexible for them\". I get it that we're not priority because it's not a huge project, but the hole was a priority on our end.The next time I checked in, in December, they said the floods had caused a back up and we agreed they would get back to me in January. It is now mid- February and, after more than ten texts over the course of three months asking about scheduling us in, as well as leaving phone messages with no follow- up, we've given up. We really wanted to use them, but we can't wait any longer and are disappointed in the way they've handled it. We would have appreciated better communication: customers with smaller projects still deserve good customer service and follow up. If they weren't interested in doing it, they could have saved us time by just telling us and letting us know we should move on to another company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ana Flavia Ribeiro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPH4gkG1LYLY-8rzO2ds0L3TfpOQ7O0VKtR0qHRTeqMrLRhNs1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After comparing several companies, I chose Summerflex — and it was the best decision. Giovanna and her team were extremely responsive, answered all my questions, and delivered top-notch work. I’ve already recommended them to my neighbors — honest, dependable, and great value! I totally recommend. Thank you guys.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauene Silva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWX7tNBSV0AnaaNH7Fiajm3uMdu1dTX5olnOhycLk7LlrdOXIU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a bad leak coming from the rooftop deck that damaged three floors of our house. Summerflex took care of everything — roofing, insulation, drywall, and all the repairs inside. They finished the whole job in just two days! Super fast, honest, and professional. Out of four companies we called, they were the only ones who truly cared and told us the truth.\n\nThanks","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ken Xie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIK-iIiNA9ph9AEl7ug0u-0YWClDfkz8r9d7RVewYUUM_ObQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"During the bomb storm last month, a big branch penetrated my first floor's gable. I have contacted multiple companies for the repair. Although they all performed free onsite estimate, only Geovana's team offered detailed inspection including roof top while the others only took a lookaround on the ground floor. Without Geovana's team, I would not notice the multiple cracks on the roof. Their quote had a reasonable price. They did perfect jobs on repairing shingle tiles and gable, cleaning roof and gutters, and removing all the debris from my yard. I would highly recommend this company for roofing jobs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1i4Y3oiTGkPiwlxAcP58OT8eQMMFsWPrcDdn1UJ9IBaXKR1lnE10Tr2v_fg2Y3cHXsGSqaR27uO4GObzi-w810FJvQnoGt-Pqiap-hg4S0SCVMpyYnCeohAkQZZcifLarz9d3b-g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IAh7lzmYUM-v51gElcUF_Z4R0_sewFj8g8wdfHlSwj_X3wd7vDhVcGaRkOeWxXqQfbEydgqRAPbeXfcDUtkCNwO8Fun2WJ1J0Wr5kL-QhAZq4xQ3_K0Eqs4K_d-H76iSzMVtu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2v9mfMY_g5qI2rkN8LXCfyHGD5meDObCkKhYVWBWuD0BRUbQWoTxNFkHzYqOh5g06kEo77oogEhYzLvKVdWaI3258_6KZea-o13Vx2KWHSRMO9nftik4rA2rwzUeKCgu1V1i4ypw=k-no"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Kirk Harbaugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIw318m0QGOoZ1y1mUynYaoIzrMT8fxsqm2Eed02U5moUgpmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Summerflex was scheduled to look at my condo building's roof. The first visit they showed up late and didn't call, only did a drone inspection. Their findings were that our 8 year old roof is 20+ years old. Red flag one, but I tell that's not the case and they should come look at the actual issue from inside the attic. We rescheduled, confirmed a time window. They did not show up, wrote to me an hour after the appointment that they couldn't make it. I reschedule one more time, and in the middle of the appointment window they send a message saying they got a bigger job and they are no longer taking customers. Wasted my time 3 times. I would be skeptical of their quality of work given their drone estimate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisbeth Salander","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJV_mXFQl5c9lW-th21PFctupSn7myf9s4OxjtmDPVkzm86IA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad that the great people from this company could show up right away to tarp my leaking skylights. The repair work was done two days later.  Very professional and great to work with\nas well as at a reasonable price.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
