YMc56r3NtfK_9CVyzr0gRZLIK8bEsgh7Y_WcQa5Nou5k1DCYJ=w447-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=2X_aTG323x6VGn5_aM0gVA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=205.00887\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"112176615483730009125","name":"Roof4life (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112176615483730009125"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Inglewood-Finn Hill","street":"13459 108th Ave NE","city":"Kirkland","postal_code":"98034","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Viswanath Ramanan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk6E0_rOg-WgoCMcP5XYN_CR8DiiACFyWUkv_GiH_t3FTC5EA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a leak in my house. I decided to change the entire roof and I worked with Roof4Life to get it done. It was great to work with Mike. He was polite and clear with his thoughts. The initial report that was sent with the estimate and photos was very professional and thorough. They were accommodating and gave us a good price on it.\nWhen it came to installation, there were 7 installers who finished it in a day (8AM - 8PM) which was great for us. They didn’t charge us anything extra and just fixed up some OSBs that had rotted.\nThey also left the place like they found it. It was a pleasure working with Roof4Life","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dushyant Arora (flyingmachines)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsEmsBZI4jsvI1KDYxolCSetaEKiHJtJOubxOBjkSXbOXc-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roof4life team is excellent at getting the roof replacement project done well, on time, and in a cost-effective manner. Both Mike and Gio really take on a hands-on approach with each house project and support the owner at each step. They educate you and ensure all things are taken care of systematically. I would recommend them to any owner in Seattle that wants to get their roof replaced by professionals.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2b-olfjwa52q3UKXqu3q-t0kQxhYrbtecti2gg4Ri6EzAFVnLWeXeh-P5eK4ft4Vl-WhbVjAlloMfHmr3GOyWeZNxe8cAfmTfIIqTYhZBP6sUhnpISEj1Tqo_54LaRqsBUpj3OMQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Alec Cattarin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5x9bwLUb0IcLdwzmVzvf_U8nQUdA2wysqJ5Jk1-sns8y28R4M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We bought our first home in January of 2021. Given the state of the market we had to waive inspection. Even without the inspection, we knew the roof was a major concern, and my wife and I were dreading the process of replacing it. I collected 18 quotes across 6 different companies, creating a detailed spreadsheet that covered costs, material, skylights, under laymen, gutters, and everything else related to our roof. Roof4Life was the best priced option out of all the quotes I collected.\n\nWe loved our experience with Roof4Life. Claudio came by our home for a quote, was very knowledgeable and asked a lot of questions, highlighting aspects of the roof I was unfamiliar with. It was really nice to have him to really help educate me on how a roof is replaced. From all the companies that came out for quotes, he got up on the roof to inspect it, and gave useful insights to the job. He didn’t treat the encounter as a sales pitch, but more of a educational opportunity, helping me understand what it would take to replace my roof, and the various parts to it.\n\nLeading up to the job, Craig at Roof4Life often communicated with me via email, providing quotes, and was very helpful for any questions I had regarding the quote. As I was new to the process, I had many questions and he always replied in a timely manner.\n\nThe job took a little over two days. The team that worked on the roof were all very polite and considerate. They moved vehicles to help me leave in the morning for work, and then knew better where to park from then on. Although I gave them permission, they never once came inside the house. They all seemed very aware to be as least intrusive as possible. While the property had the typical debris across it throughout the workday, they cleaned up every piece at the end of each day. This was actually quite surprising as the debris was extensive at times. In addition to the removal, disposal of existing roof, under laymen, new plywood, flashing, and roof material, the team also replaced all our fascia and barge boards. They worked with me one of the mornings to provide me with time to paint the boards too. They even helped me paint them. All in all, this was a great crew with incredible professionalism.\n\nLastly, the workmanship was superb. The roof looks incredible, the colors of the material were exactly as they depicted. There were no through-nails in any of the eaves. Our roof had several skylights, and they did a marvelous job installing them. My wife and I are so happy with the new roof, and thrilled we decided to go with Roof4life, they were the most competitive in pricing, and we were worried that would represent a loss in some other aspect of the job. However they were exceptional across the board. I highly suggest you use them if you are considering roofing work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0F2kqTJx1Vlhii-UkTlv4RknLVM-3PV8O7zxhZ8HOfv7HGRAjH7-vGUXIzMrVw7TYGAgpdlMBWCF9qnRGAucjGzeV_GBlX-FOum3jqi27ACE6yeG7bXYLxn_qGjzomRYl1ezx8Hg=k-no"],"When":"2022-7-13"},{"Name":"rob fristoe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZOFcfsooZ8LlQXtyD5OrJIlEBXK4qgTxpj30YTDDE0MKy3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roof 4 Life did a outstanding  job replacing our roof. Every aspect of the job was completed with utmost quality.  I performed a rooftop inspection after the workers finalized the job and did not find any mistakes or shortcuts. I have roofed many houses in my younger years and  I can tell you the new techniques and materials used are far better today.\n\nRoof for Life used ice/rain shield on overhangs, valleys and ridges as well as drip metal throughout perimeter. We had vent-a-ridge installed on multiple ridges and it really made the roof look fantastic. Not to mention\nit is far superior to regular vents.\n\nI acquired 9 bids for this project and they came in 2nd best price by less than $200.00 dollars. The salesman/foreman won me over with his knowledge and professionalism.\nI would recommend them for sure.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3lmurqj794B04qXtNk4a552KD4kVEVmx2lbkeRdN8MGFj8Y5fEx_zdMVZh-eG99T8f6f_f1_Pup--eWIgDWPxo3MJXIB9QQceOiO_IHgMkWPh7lyM6QZzGA6K0v0E8xIhbYnRngA=k-no"],"When":"2021-2-18"},{"Name":"Michael Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJz7kgBMly1T7n2JPlOFPJWyXdDXxWePDDjKZVcHFzRGYR24Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike and Gio were very professional and easy to work with. They were both super communicative and made sure I was informed on everything that would happen and that I was comfortable with everything before moving forward. The work was completed well and in a timely manner. I will be utilizing their services again for any future roofing projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZkltgHvJcnsURYHsPfPMlga-kbvN69f70pPc5zgxaftSFE6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We would definitely recommend Roof4Life to anyone seeking a quality job at a reasonable price! It was a pleasure to work with them, from bid to completion!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21nwXkO8Xcavjdw48SgjJ7uX_HNk8XozgfJXGKrjYEMMgkYEMpw0G804XvoT4grJzWLR803LQBTKNiQwQOjmUx8xZVBw5GKCJwkCO3r0BceTmNcMPhT9ChQZKuDt9x5S_sRHSPMg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Mqr8cDQ0xS7hwvtyCxrTNZRQQbC0Zsb4H7zQ3p8evuTXJtGgB8D3P6n0vXj2VrS5u0fUbI-eVObi_V4-mBxGlWezLG3AgW3vN4Qf6XnMCFZOcOhNnMkJSXCPQGiMxTy8jjuA3=k-no"],"When":"2022-9-21"},{"Name":"Karen Gray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKF2C51zm6a3p9vhFEKrLLxLMESjlnyp-sHkwiHrZ9rL5r_BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roof4Life did an excellent job with my roof. The roof is great! The lead had about 25 years of experience and the team were all exceptional with their skills. The customer service was terrific in responding to my questions and knowing all aspects of the work.\nI highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fabio Kang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ89tl4g_88Itqh73472dnoOPKdWeoGahXuMHl-1y0iaFDmRGi-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been looking to replace my roof for years and contacted several roofing companies. One did not even look at my roof and inside my attic, and another told me I needed to replace 43 pieces of plywood. I decided to check Roof4Life after a referral. Still, I could have had better expectations, but after Giovanni came and did a complete inspection, I felt very good with his honest and technical explanation. After that, I had the pleasure of working with Mike on the roof replacement proposal. His patience and friendliness were exceptional, making me feel comfortable and respected with my questions and requests.  I hired Roof4Life to replace my roof, and they did an excellent job. I highly recommend  Roof4life; a few of my neighbors also ended up replacing their roofs with Roof4Life.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
