r choosing State Roofing for our roof replacement project.  We have high expectations for a positive experience, and will update our review once the work is completed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Shahidi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrGd-waEZwq_MIYoLNYEqoJETT7o5ujYvI85UFk-bjRSeocw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an excellent experience with State Roofing. Greg came out to take a look at a few concerns we had with our new house based on the inspection and I walked away with a much better understanding of those items and several others that I hadn't thought about.\n\nI have had good and bad experiences with contractors so far, and  you can tell the passion and professionalism with State Roofing. Clear answers on questions, going above and beyond in evaluating various conditions, providing tips on maintaining the roof and what to watch out for...I couldn't have asked for more.\n\nThey have my future roofing business for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim Stettner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViC-yuCecl9vivslYYn5f0WD9kK4MMKAjf66kpYAhLTIdi_2QM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Greg came out to my house to give an estimate for roof replacement. He was very nice and thorough. They gave me a very detailed quote and explained the what the job would look like before, during and afterwards. Even offered to help me compare all of my quotes! Very nice man and seems like a good company","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sue Schultze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu5ovoufpKsbsQp7wKLn5ECfG7Avm2Oz-6Qbdsr_R3VTTqnsM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just a bid so far, but truly a killer experience. Appointment within days. Got a text w pic of rep and mini bio. Guy even called and asked to come few minutes early. Competent, polite, knowledgeable and friendly. Just a stellar experience. Just solid information. Bid on the spot w zero pressure to “close”. Having a random dude come into your home can be creepy these days. State made it a positive, comfortable experience. Thanks Greg. Fantastic meeting you. You were professional, knew your stuff and, between your family and scout troop activities, clearly personally invested in this community in a big way. Way to go state\nRoofing. Great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jayson de'noble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk8P4R_55baZD6QOpqELKSHrLL_-cRsqGHX1OSVjGOZNyfUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had them out for a quote today and had a very pleasant experience. Jade came out and looked over my roof and showed me a couple options. He didn’t pressure us or try to sell us things we didn’t need. He did give us every detail from type of material to cost and was very upfront about everything. What he didn’t know is that he wasn’t the first estimator that has come out. He noticed things the others didn’t, he explained the what and why and at the end of it they even had the best price. Would absolutely recommend to everyone I know.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sue Pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIPQW-pUSoK5pzHgK8buyPfw2YrLd_1Zg2F_AUDoUnnLzN-Vdwdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"State Roofing has completed several jobs for our homes, including deck builds, roofing, and balcony waterproofing. They’ve done an excellent job providing information on available products making selection a breeze. The installation crews have been awesome, especially Demitri who built our decks. The city inspector told us that the deck construction was the best he has seen. 100% recommend State Roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheri Andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4mf9Mi5eKRRWASOQy6C_OzkS9qZTBZMsgMzioysH7j-RfvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just signed on today with State Roofing via Aaron, who is an excellent representative for the company! He is very personable, well informed and thorough. He explained our options with pro and cons for each, in relation to our needs. We will Erie another review when the job is completed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marina Hardy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtWg53pRZCcFD-j7jyPEZCFysxClcW2-W8PGVxHfF8vv8B4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have not yet had the roof installed but was very pleased with sales and estimate process. No high pressure car salesman back-and-forth with a manager.  Very high tech measuring and photographic software. Very nice, very professional salesman, Jeff. Very professional, thorough, and effective person who answered my initial call","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
