ecently, I had the house’s gutters cleaned and received a moss treatment for my house’s roof from Daniel. He was incredibly responsive from the start, answering all my questions and keeping me updated throughout the process. The service was professional and efficient, with a quick and direct response. He helped me understand the process and shared before-and-after pictures, demonstrating great transparency in his work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xiaoying Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9Jldm9lM_VMRZyP41HD5l4htg__-ct0F3fm3kaWVFr2FzkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brixton\u0026Windsor has helped me with moss removal and gutter cleaning. They also helped with a leak caused by the built-up moss. Their response was quick and price is reasonable. They had excellent communication throughout the process and the job was done quick and clean. I will definitely recommend the service and will come back myself for any future services. Thank you Braxton\u0026Windsor!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
