EvPrXrOuBKxNJlAOoQIJMJa3g_4x498kv05Upfg=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-9"},{"Name":"Warren Takata","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZpkNOV0xXBQJ4wVJUH09xDytA-Tnwj29WKWXHy2dQpfkQdRwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Guardian roofing exceeded our expectations with our roof replacement. Alfredo and his team did a great job. They had great communication throughout the process, professional, neat, cleaned surrounding area, and completed the whole job in one day.  We are very happy that we chose Guardian Roofing and feel that we have the best roof in our neighborhood.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qFAxdqIelSn4jSH4yUtIeCQ7OiarAgv4Eqp0IDTzjFOg87ZzrcYPWr8ZccQhLwm4IuTAywIS0KViZy5k79P1nQ_ED_SUV54CV2KeiLTmeYdi-KPdZzvEPmGWYfoRS16lJRYSiAKIJKjYm=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2dUeNyc8xcKt16jTLzZzMuV7QL9pc4Si8JXoqNC19c3rorfTHoldgGCMAdyh3_-zchpDcqG4gE9rzkBVVVDUhNHvLHjamtnsyvoHM3jE585LXOup5Aqo0_rCv0rDIJfFVXQkILrx6IOVNx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15QD0cyPLlKVC6vto6V36ryPfimZrr4pbOOFyW78maTY2D8mM9m5LRO1NkWan6IHXCBYS_sxLGKQpu02e2hy-iCdiemdoXpVP1aSsh4S3VV_Deha5FWlfKQzz_dsKInQjo2-nBegS-h0Sg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3rlFiVJr6qR3B3To8vWpWGDghG8uDEt3J4QB5jP-QhCLKMvRGgjzCOSyTaesYVCUFvUeqyvBQgzV156t7h0kIMs26fqWDyEC2pRKTihn4a3GxpJIOe5dkO7M6qNgsPbGkHzSUu8FZ0oGob=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-25"},{"Name":"Ben Bailey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOD8De9-w-gQzdiJAg8gA8qpYZ3Z5sqz6O7fZbykDxlJCEFefS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at Guardian Roofing did an amazing job putting a new roof on our home.  The quality is excellent and communication very thorough.  Jorge and his crew are professional and friendly.  They left the area cleaned and looking better than it was before.  I recommend the Guardian Roofing team.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ULpl_GunGl8_J5giXmTEt7w8cTOZVwSA8hxCI4Q-HDUsdGgjxMFiSUPHVR0TJlZnsydkYhxPWIC5RFiLab8VmJKgpCRU0LWgSVG5QtBKDTLeDTVszsHqPx1bfFqwb6oEJFQkCSgVSNKJG=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31LQR32mGolBh4k8fZ58iwDLPD2q2_TWTO64g9d-mJ5j9bTgWNMobbIutBHE0LsWPFQ1TCOHaqP-jauJk8bJh_gnk6DAtiwkuQmNe5CFUYAGNATCIkUvClaKKlLiEYJDqUaPBKZflxzTk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1k8ufgr2DKa42O7aTn0CAVHSLaNb412hi7hNmgFQEOdhMm0tDE2nqWcOdOWaaguu7KQHwLuNd8ihw5oW3um3mQqBDUoC6jcfagCKXI9HbxaGq1gGtGpbibNL34LN7nB7XQjQSh9m4pHJg=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-8"},{"Name":"Renee Rains","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIrq8JxuD87ZpUJrFixDMhi37EUwrjyfGwgKKBDAg6UACMNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Guardian roofing and chimney mason crew started within 1 week of me speaking with the inspection person. They walked me through all stages of the process, answered my questions, tarped the perimeter of my house, and completed daily clean ups so that our dogs and my family were always safe to enter and exit. The detail of the work was beyond what I could have hoped for my chimney and roof repairs. They even took additional steps to remove every single old nail (which were all over the entire roof) a prior roofing company had left hidden under the shingles. I was able to see before and after photos of the work for peace of mind. Highly recommend Guardian!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie West","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUQGMSzJoJeAem3GuHCT27PtoOV6nSzjjWvxARXrLGxsgHCmuU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The guy who does the sales and initial inspection, Dallas, was excellent. He was on time and very detailed and caught some issues that a different roofer didn’t catch (the other quote I got was DOUBLE the price of guardian as well).\n\nThe actual roofing project, however, had some hiccups. The first day they shot a nail through a wire which shut off power in half of our house. The project manager was prompt in calling us back and sending out an electrician the next business day to fix it which was great— it was just a freak accident so we didn’t sweat it. But then, the next day, they messed up our water heater exhaust vent which could have given us carbon monoxide poisoning if we didn’t notice. They came and “fixed it” but it was done improperly a second time. Someone came to fix it AGAIN and they didn’t do it right either (it needs 1” clearance or else it’s a fire hazard— it was touching the attic wood). Finally after a lot of micromanaging on our part the foreman came and did it the right way but it was a very long process with a lot of missed work shifts on our end to let people into our house for a project that was supposed to take two days… The price was reasonable and the project managers were very prompt to send people out to fix stuff but it was very stressful having so many things go wrong in the first place and makes me worry about spots that we can’t see/double check the work on. I’m glad that we are savvy enough with home repair type stuff and could double check their work but if we didn’t double check we could have had CO poisoning or a burnt down house which is very worrisome.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfWJ_c4TmMQCEAkK0LJqy3YCMStqSRgSwa7oPjOjCfDx9DcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our roofing specialist, Ron Otis, went above and beyond during our roofing consultation. He was friendly and extremely knowledgable, providing helpful insights on the possible cause of a leak in our roof and going as far as 1) getting on our (very tall) roof, 2) putting a scope down our vent pipe (potential culprit) to understand its shape and take a video for us, and 3) inspecting our roof/gutters/caulking around the edges to help further pinpoint the issue. He did all of this at no cost and was very honest in his assessment, as the solution ultimately did not require a roofing company to do any work in the end. We highly recommend Ron and Guardian Roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jana Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdIY3KFTmJ7jv_AnurcvEzE_hY8jXGx_hFDpe3wM0LFo4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our experience with Guardian was excellent from beginning to end.  Jimmy who came to give us the bid was super through and the video to see what was going on and a step by step explanation of what the process would be helped a ton.  Antonio was the project Superintendent and he had great communication, and kept us updated and made sure the project went smoothly and informed us of any updates or changes that would be happening.  We'd work with them again!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
