":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Christine Eicher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8U0v6FH6J8XHoUI_7TGRXNU-K-Salxj4eiEdIJrJEDJD_rHRS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an excellent experience with Skilled Roofing from start to finish. We originally found them online, and Adan came out to inspect our roof. Our roof had been replaced about 8 years ago by another company, but unfortunately it wasn’t done correctly. Adan and his crew discovered rotten wood and soft spots that had gone unnoticed before.\n\nThroughout the entire process, Adan and his crew were incredibly thorough and transparent. They kept us updated every step of the way with pictures, clearly explaining the damage they found, and they truly went above and beyond to fix everything properly. It was such a relief to work with a team that clearly takes pride in doing the job right. They kept everything tidy and cleaned after finishing the roof.\n\nSandra was also amazing to work with. Before the project even began, she was extremely communicative, consistently following up with us and checking in, especially during the rainy months while we were waiting to have our roof redone. She made sure we were doing okay and always made herself available, which meant so much to us.\n\nWe truly feel blessed that we found Skilled Roofing. The professionalism, care, and attention to detail Adan and his crew showed us exceeded our expectations. We are so grateful for everything they have done for us and would highly recommend Skilled Roofing to anyone looking for honest, reliable, and top-quality roofers.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21ofQottytRyGZlCu-atrExAkP_cu111IEWaY7SrjXQXOixjd8CnV5kH9WnpSAuiFYASES2cKt-wB7XpshrgJARkg4dcTQ1RE-RuumxFQhi06PfSnXvbCqjjdyBxkjfuv3oCOhY47zrfA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3pKZmkVzibw_lrTyI2vnrujueUSHmbZMI5