c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience with Skilled Roofing company from start to finish. Communication was excellent throughout the entire process, and the work was completed within the exact timeframe they estimated. Their quote was the best out of several we received, and they were incredibly flexible with payments, which was especially helpful since this was a complex project involving 9 different owners.\nEven with a few small hiccups along the way, the owner was truly outstanding, always responsive, professional, and quick to find solutions. We are extremely happy with the final results and I highly recommend them to anyone needing roofing work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reese Conway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIohd_2SwJqakM2LEHkb6rNgtfcX9zifoTyQU1Z735V-Op8nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Could not have asked for a better, more helpful company for our roof replacement. We had a unique situation for the project since we are an HOA and Skilled Roofing was the only company willing to work with us all to find a financing solution. From the start, everyone I interacted with were extremely communicative and friendly. The project ran into various hiccups that made it bigger than we initially thought it would be and they handled it all with ease and great communication. Cannot recommend them enough","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Johnny Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgEejVnNucO3a40lTdFtm0i5x9BjaO8JGU8TmMhDblnxVm-ts=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I live an hour away from Seattle. I got their phone number from a friend, so I decided to get them a call, they even willing drove an hour to come up here to do my roof. I really appreciate it. It is the best company so far.  they are really reliable,  very friendly to work with, great service , awesome price. I would recommend skilled roofing to anyone.","Images":["https://lh3.googleuse