 installed a new gutters with the down spots white color\nThey also help us to install a additional ventilation I’ll bring it up to the code","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Jelvik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV4sH1J-Txovao14h3QLIB1ihqi2gHsChlt6B-DwIjwz4eMtY9cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edward, our salesperson was very knowledgeable. He inspected the roof and gave us a written estimate. We had estimates from three other companies but decided upon Forever Roofing. Their bid was comparable to all but one.\nThat was a big company and they wanted quite a bit more than the others. They wouldn't leave or email an estimate for me to show my husband but wanted to do a second estimate when my husband was available.\nWhen we called Edward to accept his bid, he was back to take precise measurements because we decided to also have all the plywood replaced. He mentioned they have a husband and wife team and we requested them for the job. The dumpster arrived within the week and the next date Henry and Lucy were up there removing the old roof down to the studs the first day. Their supplies arrived the next day and they were hard at work again. They finished our 1500 sf roof with several peaks, in 3 days! They walked around the house making sure all debris was cleaned up and then called to have the dumpster removed and after thanking them for a fantastic job, we said goodbye and they left, leaving everything as they found it, except for leaving a beautiful new roof.\nPictures are before and after.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn05A7Ee3i5WZguVBEDcuvjPoOzG1mm4RiS4GMexrhh-h865hBmYOwuvdYfWPg1LDq0xtjDXIWELK7GPE1fJoTivVKpFIBnE8V7suSPs0WEsNIs5rW6AbnVOci7DvvzXgCsjirU6cNQyLdrX=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1fjRSxuNt5TMcSNEJHZ2nUcJ_Haaa5xf77dzfd7w_G7dIogYHPcjk3ZHDEHXn7c-FBJhGhg1oz58eD590IhH5kSoVzIUU3sMmPVFOMCo94vd8XtTnw8fgjp_t5ophTE35DJKhjuD1c4kqw=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-17"}