cluding drone shots) and communication updates.  I'm very happy with the entire process and how our project turned out.  Upper West has my strongest recommendation.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn18Egt-7DpAFzC9RH3_Q7jDsfQ1vUETzDM5-eOw27aCcWVHyTNH-KgV8mAEll0nwtyecKC9_8ZH31CjJcimT-PlAI_eebFiLGG6yGuqkU2SSJ3TsTL72xxdOtd8VwMwzPQ_a6rHoqXN979M=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1I_cynhKylMrP_DqdQE-mbGpkDWAb_z2ULv1MUG-9RdvSMW_DVOu71VFxREV1BAn07AcU_qIYD-LHGafaS79RsKQ00JLd54PX2zdqiCwTrYmYI35pFMHqTkUCk1tl3Rfk-qR3cTVRPrbvP=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-2"},{"Name":"Christopher Cappello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWm6QKvU45i35L5B0qQi_PHFWR-zJxL_FYf8FflFmuKWccYgfQayA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Upper West Exteriors did an outstanding job installing Govee year-round lights on our home. The estimate was clear and accurate, and the team showed up right on schedule to complete the work. They were professional, efficient, and left everything spotless when they were done. The lights look fantastic. I would highly recommend Mike and his team to anyone looking for quality exterior work and great customer service.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0p91aGpUjnvhCphSlW-PqiIM_IZqiB_xeeAKP4hBVzG5A2Sa-jZeRE5RWM6Urt-4E3ISWdpcixtetSGr8M6XKQ8v_zecWWL_jMjInjN-OdQbi6421nbSpjvlprdZUFagRy5xbAWsKL-A2v=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-17"},{"Name":"Joe Baird","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaTgf2sN9QT0Ohg5Ab_rLWLAKwTU1GmiwxtS6tfF7MQJErKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Professional, friendly and fair from start to finish. My families experience was top notch. I looked into having multiple companies do my roof. It was clear Upper West was the right choice and they lived up to expectations.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vl9ih0w_Yads6h04rSpduEsoYuy69Q_oMfVCY9Ii5QD_nMdcXlx4tGjUD3krS-ZYWtD9ui54fa2xsSbSuMqpVEioX9IqdN8ZHriLsAlbomvw6B3YEsl25QOR8CeAHhCnR6r2rdRgQky43=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-2"},{"Name":"steven parsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfoJLm9baHX5MiH9gUw1dB1qU4o0J_J-VhQbCcg7sEShVNIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Upper West Exteriors was remarkable in all aspects of my roofing project.From the bidding process with Mike Tappert walking me thru the needed tasks.The communication with his team that included a daily photo log.This came in very handy as I was out of the region during the whole removal and roof replacement  which provided an ease of mind!The flexibility of adapting the original plan and providing a discounted charge for materials needed.\nThe efficiency from start to finish was expeditious! Upon my return the craftsmanship of the roofing and gutter repair was excellent! Mike and his team also coordinated with other contractors I had on site in a very professional manner.\nBottomline only one choice in my book for your entire roofing replacement and gutter work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manu Chandel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBqnZbZrbNPtYsdnCDDQNE9KizTnzaTl_jqRhLkkbvrtN_2att=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Professional setup and great work. They reached out quickly after I made a call. They gave clear quote and their technician was on time. They made a patch on my roof on a bad weather day, talks for their commitment. They are licenced and Insured too unlike others. Would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Huynh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeWt9xlGYmnF0oQ8ClFo-ZGEAHHgAI8167Z8zEUij0sVqZd3o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike at Upper West Exteriors were phenomenal to work with! They completed two major roof installations and gutter repairs for two of my clients. They were professional and the quality of their work was superb.\n\nI will hire them for my future real estate clients and highly recommend them for your next project!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeremiah McNeal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQLfjq60A92SZF1zMrJ7s7dNGsJoJkWgIg5cxXF508LvYcZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Upper West Exteriors! They installed my new roof last year, and the quality of their work was outstanding from start to finish. But what really sets them apart is their incredible service when disaster struck. A few months after the installation, a tree fell on my house during Thanksgiving week, causing significant damage. I called Mike right away, and within just a couple of hours, his team was at my doorstep. They jumped into action, clearing debris and providing everything I needed for the insurance adjuster that same day—no small feat during a holiday week!\nThe insurance process went smoothly, with approval coming through in just a couple of days, and Upper West didn’t waste a moment. They had my roof repaired and my home back in shape within a week, beating the next storm by a day. Their responsiveness, professionalism, and expertise are unmatched. Mike and his crew truly went above and beyond, and I’d recommend Upper West Exteriors to anyone without hesitation. Five stars all the way!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eG1F3VBQvDTXJxqa0Ktts3tnLobvq9Lt6aBDfJKXcBKuqCR8XXkC2cu-tMyNz2mYG4zL5iqd15nFgZMP2HUiASE83_A5-l7DNHqEcGRMPQAeavdd2cDNvBOkE4LKhqknIyq83=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Mn1tLdiSpkjREFweEWOx3E6WR-w_Gmn8VkIuaBLht4qc_1huf4r7emb-PI79briRbAvwPVFtHBoLOeg714z7ruC3hgiQKiScb5ZY56sjpXzpL4uFMhsE8Fv5beWfJCQ8f_8HU=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-31"},{"Name":"David \u0026 Lisa Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDCtQ9SlrI6_b62EAsMJO9_hIUxbGZHQVLv3I9xZOo7rpd2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great company. Most professional company I got estimates from. Communication was the best and from all