e leak is fixed now. I will definitely call John again for my roofing needs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2fNBgcoNYq9WHbzOpgmAnY02F_hw8E7yvoPAq6CrDlZu9I1qLw1ziEEk7NcygHos4ruEhKUthUlhy8GMMwn5Onh6Y5N_qm-U0gaoDSwXEf3OfmWcv5HjN2OLQj7o776WtkI5hK=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XYnhv0Tpkziox0vw9Q2FLhfU2BYMrBjSlf7tXYYyRw6zK52gIzGmeRYnOEiRnUBfCJizEHH7fyyRo13uBtDsGRG5QEI1Y_u_pVDYv2Chzzp_20l-1toJMUcWQvpSOO0ipZZtoCw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ouX8Ah3JAP90ofrhN6HhS2xz97owj0u-7uSBxcACsBwP4XtCI1ITMNx3kYtGrxMjEtK0-VYYuf1zAAxjJeHmxTJPXlBzN0jYcywEhqzKE08kD_tU68-UBdIl82OcDadT7Xdbk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tfX2Ezi11ZXh1SHm9GN2zYDgVAKj12zdE4528WXGUPuqpqjXKFsBp_o5t62Jr12KIe-x2z-R8pYpy_3Sjm3JLb1lx206RIMVpalU09-QbtniqYrQhyb-KF4r1MkKBwuwwKUhD=k-no"],"When":"2023-10-14"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
