o"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHkz7YTHa0WSLOvlDHwyguDJaCoUnR8iL1A4dowdX_D47mbLqXQ4sJeNiP927y2eR--nuK_4OPa6l8Kql3S8byKvPs-Rz_g-5_hqYL29QSBFqYjGBprb6NlArh9EY5-Dg=w397-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=t9l3sZdPNMhBsprM_3oeTA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=9.0495825\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"109993385638865641876","name":"NGB Roofing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109993385638865641876"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"19215 80th Pl W","city":"Edmonds","postal_code":"98026","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kaleb Lora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWucY1hRYzHtqyaabEM8dSxgDzVIz0Cs6U1i1EvajmIsKtcM9Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick at NGB Roofing was absolutely outstanding. He came out the very next day after I called for a quote, which immediately impressed us. Even more remarkable, he stopped by after hours to help us get an inspection done as quickly as possible.\n\nNot only was he personable, prompt, and professional, but he also took the time to thoroughly assess everything and explain what he was seeing. He found and fixed a few small issues on the spot, which really showed his integrity and attention to detail. It was clear he genuinely cares about making sure his customers are getting their money’s worth, and more importantly, that their roof is secure and built to last long-term.\n\nIf you’re looking for someone reliable, detail-oriented, and committed to doing the job right, Nick is your guy. Highly recommend NGB Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0nZDCUq7zUGwKeZ9yKYf81nYQeDiaXqGks6nw7JIYZ5Tb1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m a GC that has worked with many roofers over the years, and I can say that Nick and his team are as good as it gets. NGB Roofing is a well run business that is responsive to its customers, and does excellent, precise, clean quality work that stands the test of time.  I rely on Nick for his expert knowledge, integrity, honesty, timeliness, diligence and fair pricing on everything from simple repairs to full roofing projects. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Dolan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJhdQ9UlCAS3EguRqjrwTZTEugEIAI6BrxX9K4bCFKDOUmwzS2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick was fantastic! It was a tough time of year to replace a roof with rain, snow, etc., plus getting materials was unpredictable. He shepherded the entire process of re-roofing my dad's house with care, thoroughness, and great communication. Had to build special structures to navigate the replacement of custom skylights. The roof and skylights are fantastic! Definite recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alec King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItE_VmkyrottCNGDtGax_CiOb8lR16BR0s1vLKBVfKuiHv6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had NGB Roofing perform some maintenance on my roof, and I’m very impressed with their work. They replaced a broken plastic flapper vent with a new 4” metal flapper, sealed exposed nails, and took care of sealing the skylight flashing corners and the corner trim on the chimney. They also cleaned out the main rooftop gutters, leaving everything neat and secure.\nThe team was professional, efficient, and detail oriented. I appreciate their thoroughness and the quality of the repairs. I would definitely recommend NGB Roofing to anyone looking for reliable roofing services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Kaniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGy7vagRTvkSiZcVunvP6IOgupTH1yYDZbUNO6q0_d591vEJn-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick and his crew are a great bunch of guys and amazing at what they do.  I challenge you to give him a call.  If you are looking for an honest and fair contractor that won't lie to you but give it to you straight, then look no further.  I know the work is solid and am very happy with the roof he installed on my house!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph Picciano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLn73IDhVMP0z9CtWmiTPaJxs5AXkjdQx-x8XZ60hZD7qHQkw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick was incredibly helpful when we needed a roof inspection (home insurance related) on short notice. He accommodated our urgent request, fitting us into his busy schedule. He was professional, extremely knowledgeable, engaging and a pleasure to work with. We will certainly be contacting him in the future for our future roofing needs. Thank you Nick!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Lockhart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHJ-CwTkLdog7-PFu6OJ3FmddawzkmpJwvDC9WWHFjyIiQLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick bailed me out of a time crunch, replacing and reworking 3 large skylights and installing the correct ductwork and vent for a shower stall fan that the previous owner had vented into a small closet (!).  Very much enjoyed having the guys on my property and roofs.  Their work was without fault.  I'll have them back for anything up there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVrDc0x37V5_SuAfy3hlALEkNZku69ZKYQGxbwcdBlzJJ7prWN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"NGB Roofing delivered exceptional service from start to finish. Nick and his team are professional, punctual, and communicative throughout the entire process. The roof looks excellent, and the quality of their work is outstanding. They completed the project on schedule and left the property clean and tidy. I highly recommend NGB Roofing for anyone seeking reliable and high-quality roofing services.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
