\u0026yaw=2.8242471\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102337313453441275677","name":"Seattle Roofing Services (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102337313453441275677"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Seattle Chinatown-International District","street":"654 S King St","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98104","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as veteran-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":false},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Assistive hearing loop","enabled":false},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":false},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible seating","enabled":false}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Tommy Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfe0lNiJ2sZthIEE2R1fwoTpb_KsJXEKgHqNKlpACGDX2jGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this roofing company. I found them in a local directory of trusted roofers. Their crew showed great skill and did excellent work on my home, which has a pretty complex roof layout. After the job was done, Gerald came by for a thorough inspection, spending a good amount of time making sure everything was up to standard. Gerald even fixed a small issue with the siding that wasn't part of the original job—he sealed a gap where rain could have gotten behind the vinyl siding, which I really appreciated. The sales process was very comfortable—no high-pressure tactics, just honest advice about what roofing work actually needed to be done. Before choosing them, I got five different quotes, and while their price was in the middle, I felt confident in their team and trusted their experience more than the others. Some companies offered lower prices, but their workers didn’t seem as qualified. I also liked that this roofing company shares a brochure with photos and names of their team, which made me feel more comfortable having them work on my property. When I decided to add more work—upgrading from just a couple gutter replacements to having all the gutters replaced—there was a bit of confusion about the discount applied. The discount for the extra work was smaller than the original, but everything was handled professionally and the final invoice matched what was agreed. Overall, the team did a fantastic job and I’m very happy with my new roof and gutters. I would definitely use them again and recommend them to anyone in Seattle looking for quality roofing services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeoWsajBrKBPzmAIruxhE-ai1qSmg38ty5Ef7OUQvtB1E7QBI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After owning our home in Seattle for about 8 months, we kept hearing good things about this roofing company from lots of neighbors. When we had a big storm and our roof started leaking, people recommended them again, but at the time they were super busy. We decided to wait on the repair, and fortunately, we didn't have any more leaks. When we were ready to fully replace our roof, we reached out to them. Their response was really quick and they got us an estimate right when they said they would. This was a nice surprise since we’ve had trouble with other contractors before. The team took care of all the permits, and once everything was approved, they got started right away. Our roof was finished so fast! Whenever we had any questions, malik or norman were always available, either answering the phone right away or calling back soon after, even during evenings. After they finished our new roof, they checked in with us and were able to handle a couple of last-minute requests. We are very happy with their work, their customer service, and the way they support the seattle community. We feel lucky to have found these roofers!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Mcdaniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdIQLNA7-tftOCVen-4qvQc5wMPWdTL6gFWiOKKnUYtPD1BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After reaching out to Seattle Roofing Services for a quote on replacing the gutters on our home, I was quickly contacted by Malik, who scheduled a visit right away. Malik arrived promptly, took thorough measurements, and provided a very competitive estimate. Throughout the process, communication was excellent, and all my questions were answered clearly. Malik also gave helpful advice about roofing and gutter options that fit our needs. We set up the installation to start at 8:00 a.m., and the crew showed up exactly on time. The entire project was completed in just a few hours, and the workmanship was outstanding. The process from start to finish was smooth and stress-free. My wife was so pleased with the results that she immediately wanted to know what other roofing and exterior services they provide. We’re already planning to use them again for future projects around the house. I've worked with several contractors before, and this experience really stood out. The team’s dedication to putting customers first and their high level of professionalism truly sets them apart. This is definitely a 5-star roofing company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garrett Weaver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCeqxK5evI9eL_3m_zyqz296GOV6nmTOB9v5dP1Ibudb0QEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience getting my old roof replaced. After getting several quotes, this roofing team offered a fair price and went above and beyond with their service. They did a detailed inspection before giving me a quote, making sure nothing was missed. Norman, the project manager, helped me pick out high-quality shingles with a lifetime warranty, which really improved the look of my house. The crew worked hard to remove my old roof and install the new one, always using the right safety gear and keeping the area clean throughout the two-day job. Norman checked in with me before, during, and after the project to make sure I was happy with everything. My new roof looks fantastic and I would definitely recommend this company to anyone needing roofing services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacqueline Alvarado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUt8ywuTN_dAeUG9icMdtvyrAovXbpYEerGVuZtKUwhqw3aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently, after my roof repair, Gerald from the roofing team gave me a call to personally apologize and made sure that a detailed receipt was delivered right to our home in Seattle. It’s clear the company is making improvements and working on better organization, which really shows their commitment to customer satisfaction. If I ever need more roofing repairs in the future, I would definitely reach out to them again, especially since they’re making sure to provide clear documentation of all final costs now. I’ve noticed others mentioning similar experiences, and I can see how communication can be improved, especially regarding warranty details. For example, I was told my roof would need an annual inspection, which seemed to be different from what some others heard. When we had a leak in our backroom, I called for help and was quoted $75 for the service visit. Gerald came out quickly, did a thorough inspection, and fixed the problem right away—he was friendly and efficient, and the whole process took about an hour. After the repair, there was some confusion about the final cost, as it ended up being $400 instead of the initial quote. They promptly came by to collect payment, but we didn’t get a receipt immediately. We followed up several times, and although there were some delays due to their office moving and switching locations, the team kept in touch and made sure we eventually received all the paperwork we needed. Despite these small hiccups, the original roofing work was excellent, and the repair was completed quickly and professionally. Overall, I appreciate their willingness to make things right and the quality of their roofing services. I would recommend them to anyone in Seattle looking for reliable roof repairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melody H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2KYnZkGuEkWjoUWWI52gaqe10SsN2riQsvSDyrvI6iDL-jA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had to quickly choose between getting a shingle or tile roof for our home in Seattle. The roofer gave us clear and affordable estimates, along with honest advice about which roofing material would work best for our needs. Their team was always responsive and made the whole process smooth and fast. We’re really happy with our new shingled roof—it looks great and feels sturdy. If we ever need roofing help again, we’ll definitely reach out to this company first. Gerald and his crew did an excellent job!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mila norris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJu7nNdxwWnieEmjBGA6LWOgFs-IBdUecfSyiLo0DgC4GdeOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seattle Roofing Services replaced the shingles on my home, the attached two-car garage, and a separate pool shed. From the beginning, the experience was excellent. Gerald did a careful inspection, provided a clear and detailed estimate, and took the time to answer all of our questions, making sure our specific needs were addressed. The roofing crew showed up right on time in the morning and worked hard throughout the day until everything was finished. They were respectful of our property and made sure to clean up thoroughly—hardly any debris was left behind. The Owens Corning warranty included with the roof gives us extra peace of mind. I’ve already recommended this company to friends and neighbors in Seattle. The office staff was also friendly and helpful whenever we called. Overall, we’re very happy with the work and the entire process.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Meghan Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEd77z2K0085v-FGbYq6zuN7QPoIMQZdEAm9eK-JtXbMRVEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough great things about Seattle Roofing Services—they went above and beyond my expectations! Diego was the main person I worked with, and he’s one of the most genuine roofing professionals I’ve met. He really knows his stuff and even impressed my insurance adjuster with his expertise, all while keeping things friendly and professional. The crew that handled the roof and gutter installation worked quickly and quietly, leaving everything clean and looking amazing. The owner made sure every detail met the highest standards. At one point, I accidentally damaged a few shingles right after the new roof was put on (long story!), but they came back right away and fixed everything, no questions asked. I wouldn’t trust anyone else with my roofing needs. If you need help with your roof or gutters in Seattle, this is the team that will make the whole process smooth and stress-free. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
