e.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=276.49692\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"104610776163141510071","name":"Adams Family Roofing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104610776163141510071"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Seattle Chinatown-International District","street":"507 7th Ave S","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98104","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"D Rice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuidMD8fMfMinNJki2N10CFn5TAhhumHmIP0O5Td1PLEsFUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We met with Taylor, who clearly explained all our roofing options and offered helpful recommendations. Everything was scheduled quickly and the team arrived right on time, handling the job with professionalism. They made sure to check their work for quality and took care to do things right. We had a sealer applied to our flat roof and patched up a leak, and the results were fantastic. The price was even better than I expected. If I ever need any roofing help in the future, I won’t hesitate to call Adams Family Roofing—they are truly reliable and trustworthy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Douglas Lozano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvbR8Y5Mb_9R3fdWg_jZDJBXtK2qouwvh5iPW28ADN0W0A9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After my brother had a great experience with Adams Family Roofing for his roof repairs, he recommended I reach out to them when it was time to replace our skylights. I sent an email to ask about their skylight replacement services, and the very next morning, I got a call back to set up an appointment. Damon came by the following morning to inspect our skylights and go over different options with us. That same afternoon, we received a clear and detailed quote by email. I called back the next day, and Damon quickly took care of ordering the new skylights for us. In less than a week, the new skylights were installed on our roof. Right after the installation, we received our bill by email, and paying online was fast and easy. They also sent a payment confirmation and receipt right away. The whole process was smooth, with great communication at every step. I highly recommend Adams Family Roofing for anyone in Seattle needing roofing or skylight work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"pauline weiss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItcxyz79WxVlzQQ6MToSuaBnM_DhRqn2aKSlgDZDnZsQh8bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adams Family Roofing did an outstanding job when I needed help with my roof in Seattle. I came home after work and noticed water leaking from my office ceiling and running down the wall. Joe came by the next day to check out the problem and quickly found where the leak was coming from. Later that same afternoon, the crew arrived and took care of the repairs right away, which really put my mind at ease since I had to travel for work soon. Everyone was professional, paid close attention to details, and the price was very reasonable. I highly recommend their roofing services to anyone needing quick and reliable help!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kristi herring","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-UHobT2XRtC8tiDF8PYVpfTjLtB-d5xp4pxnVUeEdEfqbbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We recently had our roof and gutters replaced, and the whole experience was excellent from start to finish. Taylor came out to give us an estimate—arriving right on time, clearly explaining all the roofing work and materials, and making sure we understood the value and protection we’d be getting with our new roof. That same evening, we received a detailed estimate, and when we were deciding on shingle colors, Taylor even provided addresses of local homes so we could see our options in person. Communication throughout the process was great. Damon kept us updated on the timeline for ordering materials and reached out to schedule the installation as soon as everything was ready. On the day of installation, the crew arrived early, and both Taylor and Damon were present to kick things off. Damon checked in several times throughout the day and at the end to make sure everything was just right. The roofing team was very courteous, took care to protect our property, and did a fantastic job installing the new roof. The next day, the gutter installation went just as smoothly, with Damon coming by again to inspect the work. We are extremely happy with the way our new roof and gutters turned out—it’s made our older home look fresh and well cared for. We highly recommend this company for anyone needing roofing services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann Simon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYS8pL5NyRmYdfsnjhMK25VojbroTF1JUqIuwl6x5Jyr4GQ_U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The roofing crew did an excellent job installing our new gutters in Seattle. Damon, who handled the estimate and explained our options, was very knowledgeable and made it easy for us to pick the right materials for our home. When the installation team, Manuel and Russell, started removing the old gutters, they discovered some rotting wood around the edges of the roof. They quickly adjusted the plan and replaced the damaged boards with new ones to make sure everything was solid before putting up the new gutters. Even with the extra work, Manuel and Russell finished the job in just one day, working hard the whole time. The final result looks fantastic, and we’re very pleased with how the new gutters turned out. We highly recommend this roofing company for anyone needing gutter work in Seattle.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Axel Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_Qj3hDP27VDk0x_ewbILkX1-D8BvOJgGsAxDuGtRpSDfKe542=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I decided to go with Adams Family Roofing for my roof replacement. I had a few other companies give me estimates, but only two actually followed through. The first one never even got up on my roof. Joe from Adams Family Roofing showed up right on time to do the inspection and was very friendly and professional. He spent about 20 minutes carefully checking everything and explained what he found—turns out I had two layers of roofing on my house and there could be some water damage to the plywood underneath. Joe took the time to walk me through all the different parts of the roof system they would be installing and made sure I understood the proposal, which listed everything clearly. On the scheduled day, the crew arrived promptly, covered my home and the yard with tarps, and started removing the old roof. After a few hours, they had stripped everything off and began replacing the damaged plywood. The team worked efficiently and did a great job putting on the new roof. The cleanup afterward was impressive. They picked up all the old roofing material and loaded it into trailers, making sure to keep the area tidy even after the tarps came off. I would recommend Adams Family Roofing to anyone looking for reliable service and quality roofing work at a fair price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bryan edwards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWm_T39cc-9YOTKwCYWCEMFwcStRzGP9eC2aSTAsUvRihJUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve hired this roofing company three times—first to fix a leak, and then to replace each side of our old roof. Every time, the work was top-notch, and we never had any problems. The crew made sure to clean up everything once the job was done. Arthur and the team were always professional, friendly, and explained each step of the process clearly. They managed to schedule the work quickly, which was a big plus since it can be tough to find fast roofing help. Their prices were fair and upfront. I highly recommend them to anyone needing roofing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jada19 W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQh_K9WOEpAuRXbYeAlT7_fHQ7owHkm7Zy_ymlGjxzRNpuyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Joe and his team did an outstanding job on our roof! They worked quickly, kept everything tidy, and showed true professionalism from start to finish. The crew was clearly experienced and paid attention to every detail. Our new roof looks amazing and we couldn't be happier with the results. The office staff was also very helpful and easy to reach whenever we had questions. We spoke with several other roofing companies in Seattle before choosing Joe, and we're so glad we did. He was highly recommended, and after meeting him we understood why. Overall, a fantastic experience with quality workmanship. We went with the black onyx dimensional shingles and love how it turned out! If you need a roofer in Seattle, we highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
