ful new roof installed by Three Tree Roofing, and I couldn’t be happier! My old roof was 37 years old and desperately needed replacing. From day one, the crew showed up on time, worked diligently, and kept the area spotless throughout the entire project. Their professionalism and attention to detail were outstanding.\n\nNow, not only does my home look amazing, but I also feel safe and secure knowing the job was done right. I’m beyond pleased with the results and incredibly grateful for the care they put into their work.\n\nThank you, Three Tree Roofing, for making this such a smooth and satisfying experience!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1LMyJB6ijGveM4j_WGQeHlAFHvqOemXLOvBvbWhIt8Jd2RSXvFFHPy7vzz2OLYRZCaGwwncdBa5zuQWpZhXczNbktJBbztsACI5QdDR4ut1g-Wt2Djm0BG7gHX444jQjseog00DknTCPzu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yZy1N3yAI4X2UIphxfe9kr4EW5r03YgsgVbyR8IjO6Q4QuTjcsKYN-sr1JBpyznCiiochEJc3WfvodoUwGMOqSg80kvo-wHAtAjwq6N1a1qnNqizo3rlmgTE8EJCCdIAMU0WQqCyg0lfQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2klbKuj4ybin4iGI9AmEF-nSj6PAYPiUd-LPVSSgGxoEqzBR2hjcU8T18RGhWDSPuQVVjTCtw7FYYGReYP6sTMEfrknHKUYPg-sClhFB2x4EQzVhi_Wk9GxsM7sWxfonYMKdpo--VvfHvT=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-12"},{"Name":"Rachel Epstein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5foaRIPGvZAYmI5zZTT_c-pXS8mXnAQdRdzC4NXiFHAg_7lWR0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our neighbors referred us to Three Tree Roofing based on their own positive experience, so from the start, we knew we were in good hands. Every single person that I communicated with was professional, informative, helpful and kind. Caleb took the time to make a thorough assessment of our roof and offered his time and explanation afterwards. The company helped fit our job in during the busiest time of year, for which we were immensely grateful. The work was efficient and the quality incredible. We got three bids and this was the best bid that was also certified. We couldn't be happier with the outcome. Thank you so much, Three Tree!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbYiMkWytRhb8U4USUnRHTtigeEyGItZ0dwtwirrFcCUxoSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After receiving many quotes we chose Three Tree Roofing. Their price was in the middle but we liked the quality of the products that they were using and warranty. All employees we encountered were friendly, professional, and helpful.  We had them replace our roof, skylight, and gutters. So happy we chose this company and very satisfied with the end result. Would definitely recommend Three Tree Roofing!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-RSV_GJw9CmQ4tlhVo-F3fhZ3A4k3-AdCn94ZISQFaSfQLExjj-mVlE7BXl820rcP1BK8HHwkjUxyinPiBwmWd_OC-J0VXUWmdyDV4iYFrUlxOf-wKeQNKvLkkYPKjMnRiBROeXFFSSQW=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-22"},{"Name":"mike l","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKED_nd_PKozTZa5XXy0sMshXw2HZZSfe0IouAvfOqXHX-dIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Three Tree Roofing did a great job on our roof.  Every step from initial bid through completion went smoothly, and all the people we worked with were very customer service oriented.\nOur roof is a flat roof membrane, so we got an experienced crew that specializes in that.  They were really great.  Very steady and efficient on the job, no messing around.  The crew lead was very nice to us, and took time to explain the job steps and any issues.  Equally important, the crew lead was very good with his employees.  I think that says a lot about the company.\nI highly recommend Three Tree Roofing did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLhKnXCpxi2WBLlV5fT5Wiwxp8ojgyXLYIjn07nGUzX0dQwA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my new roof.  Three Tree Roofing replaced my roof August 2025.  Their price was competitive and I’m happy with my decision.  Thank you Caleb, for giving me a list of homes with shingle colors I was considering.  I chose Heather Blend.  \u2028\u2028The roofers came and worked hard on the hottest day of the year.  They worked over 10 hours but nothing felt rushed or compromised.  I chose to have a dump truck pull into my backyard and I had no damage from doing that.  Again they worked too long and hard!  I hope they got a bonus for completing early or on time.\n\nMy gutters were installed a few days later.  I spoke with Ben and he made one of my down spouts work for water collection  Thank you!\u2028\u2028I appreciate the owner calling me during the early demo phase.  The foreman Godo, found an issue that would increase the cost.  They communicated and documented the issue thoroughly.\n\nI used an Office of Housing repair loan to pay for my roof.  I don’t own a million dollar home, a roof is a big decision, but Three Three Roofing made the process easy. I left for 10 hrs and came home to a new roof.  \u2028\u2028Three Tree Roofing worked hard on my roof, they communicated clearly, was respectful of my property, finished on schedule——-again, they worked on the hottest day of the year!\n\nThank you. ~Tina C","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"cici gurney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8Ocr-CIrjU9NskUqMAi5DQlTCcyhx8fOYba3y22OC5W3E9fyyFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"100% Satisfied with Every aspect of this company ! Professional and efficient at every step of the process from a thoughtful, thorough bid/estimate (which came in at what I anticipated from various sites online), the office staff's amazing communication along each step, to the actual crew and lead operator.\nI have a 1942 house that needed a full roof removal and replacement. I really did my research into roofing companies since I knew it was going to be a real undertaking.  I boiled it down to 2 choices and the shear professionalism of Three Tree Roofing was what made me choose them. They sent emails including videos of exactly what to expect ~ from tear down to replacement and clean up. I was provided a packet with all of the roofing material details and provided warranties for materials and work.  They also offered an annual roof maintenance/gutter cleaning program, which will cost less than I have been paying currently, so i added that option on.\nI am SO happy I went with them !\n\nThere was a little gap in their schedule, so they fit me in weeks earlier than anticipated. Even with wet weather, they were done in 3 days. They had a dumpster and honey bucket delivered the day before, so they were ready to go. The team was early each day and up on the roof working at their designated start time.  Our yard and driveway was left immaculate when they finished, as if they hadn't even been there !\n\nI appreciated having a different person from their team specifically in charge of each step and they would call me or text if I preferred,  and always followed up with a thorough email outlining anything discussed. There was no guesswork or worry at my end.\n\nMy new roof is absolutely beautiful ! What a bunch of wonderful people to work with ~ I feel very lucky and know that I made the right choice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Basirmand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgk0RxMILnnrKMeONUTU0YXBJKmxx6hRJVx5uF-YTwr5CEa5Ze=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Three Tree Roofing was an absolute standout to work with. From the very beginning, their communication was clear, timely, and professional. Every step of the process was explained in advance. They were responsive to questions, easy to get in touch with, and genuinely made me feel like my project mattered.\n\nOnce work began, their crew showed up on schedule and kept the job site impressively tidy. At the end of each day, they cleaned up all debris, tools, and materials, which I appreciated more than I expected. It never felt like I was living in a construction zone. Their attention to detail and respect for the property really set them apart.\n\nThey completed the entire roof replacement quickly, without cutting corners or sacrificing quality. The craftsmanship shows, and the roof looks fantastic. You can tell this team takes pride in what they do.\n\nWhat stood out most was how refreshing it was to work with a company that clearly cares about its customers. Roofing isn’t a business that relies on frequent repeat clients, yet they treated the project like they were earning my business for life. That mindset alone speaks volumes about their integrity and work ethic.\n\nI highly recommend Three Tree Roofing to anyone needing a roof replacement or repair. If you want a company that communicates well, works efficiently, respects your home, and delivers an excellent final product, they’re the ones to hire. A truly phenomenal experience from start to finish.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Leach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7con5n1XQZ6RuB8Z5ma6yY-69ePl8QaAgm2O2lNhch8pNKtrr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Three Tree Roofing did an amazing job on our roof. The crew was hardworking, polite, and paid attention to every detail. They cleaned up after themselves each day, which we really appreciated. The roof looks fantastic — we honestly couldn’t be happier with how it turned out. Highly recommend them!\n\nBrian and Michelle Leach","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
