fcG6nr1_8qv0sr-JKWIa-TEy_Iw07-yJ8sm3=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-19"},{"Name":"Christian Mangune","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSvAYJ0mFXK0Utgelhclh9EZY7quGgL1vXyNelrFiWsMN_OEwk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We recently had our roof replaced with interlock aluminum shingles and we love how it made our house stand out in our neighborhood. I would have given 5 stars but there were few things that I wanted to point out.\n\nRoss arrived on time and did an excellent presentation. I specifically asked him if their installers are contractors and his answer was no, they are employees of interlock. Turns out they are contractors which is no big deal as long as they do excellent work, it’s all about honesty.\n\nPrior to installation, the installers told me that it would take about two and a half days to finish which is great, I said no rush. The installation process took two weeks, I hope everything will go well this coming rainy season.\n\nThe only thing I didn’t like was at the end of the day they leave their tools in the driveway just laying around and the worst they leave their microwave plugged into the outlet with damaged power cord.\n\nBut with all things said, we love our new roof and only time will tell if it was worth the price.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn00J5NFQNauISbt8YxtG9MXvv7hvRGfazUvkBHgPLFJnuEyrirKywILtTnJu1x0vb-pSNJTiqOQHdYPALalp9PIJqc8uas2QfJsYZ4luAzoock2nikftWB6jiEngvbL3DM2sgMao3NVyrb7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RJ0A2rdvJxsJB1p6jPzfl_S7_Igrj1vRbBKJlqnompqRK4tRiu6mAeBD3TjJ0780xlSDKLF6udug-db2E0JoI1Aia6HnRNWQOWtOqSV-563N0R8YL5pddYiM8wbVWwTreyMFPf6KvD-5c=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FUlfTitpF-PF5ks1aDj6eynhZRHy9EXm8tXV8MRsqYcY5qO6DMZCSfuXriAuYn8eK18OF6uFGX6nxOKAXRd3BnrylNGQpEKVPZiuvcH5xnIvSP0YgxhUzDskuuvcQGqZPtZ6HTnATMqI=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-14"},{"Name":"Nadzeya Shedava","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDH055aEgYdiFT3JcQWTx_McqFs560kBcrPlwRmHyojxDYTFY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had our roof replaced with aluminum shingles and are very satisfied so far.\n- Easy Sales Process – Thank you Ross for making everything clear and straightforward from the start.\n- Great Value – The price was very reasonable compared to other estimates.\n- Better Than Expected – The finished look exceeded our expectations and really improved the appearance of our home. It’s not as glossy as we feared, which we like.\n- Fast \u0026 Efficient – The crew worked quickly and finished everything in just 2 days for our ~1,000 sq. ft. house with two layers of old shingles.\n- No Issues – No noise at all, despite common concerns about metal roofs.\nTip for others: Ask for the exact model and size of vents that will be installed before the project starts. Our vents were only a few months old but couldn’t be reused, and the ones the company brought were the wrong size. The crew had to buy replacements last minute, which worked but don’t perfectly match.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jcKSddyxsvj41WRGPxScryydBnHtv_uIJ-c127N5SVsCyjHesrBimCkED5oWh-tl4OWJUwuXf2hGQ54ytlya-P9dJ_da7T3oXnOm2BhrkxCQ_tObr5PKUJQDwrh_6xIq1n2oN-rIb9tc=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-21"},{"Name":"bird homan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLygV_Dd8XpM2qc89tvxfIhlUKSXGlKbPdy6qvHKZawrbFoeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very pleased with the entire experience with Interlock Roofing. Ross did a fantastic job of showing me all of the options available, and explaining how Interlock is different from other roofing. This was not a hard sales pitch. I was pleasantly surprised by how affordable a metal roof was. I had five other estimates for a traditional composite roof, and the price difference for a forever roof was negligible considering all the benefits. Next, the installation. These guys were amazing! Only two guys doing the demo and reroof, but very hard workers and did a fantastic job. It seems rare these days to find skilled tradesmen that take pride in their work, and these guys exceeded my expectations. I also took advantage of Interlock’s financing. Drew was very helpful and accommodating. The whole process was taken care of through Interlock, making it super convenient and great communication throughout. I will highly recommend:)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VcTx5nsqGeX_gomJyWe_MlqH4dJCC7F8SdRaGGMdq8nMEacSC2AOYfZQEXNsY1rP5ynElnfKsinv7CybCCroUEyY9rp6xmvdXF7NRxDRFsX41MgyDTfQmyRQIcUQmOBo2sCpBuVHIPgSV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tidgh1Ny6GMOrX482iG2bKFZRgWtRwy-d2MFJk25pmkrdtDprgMk-dyJ7RxZhmkRTPftGeB3x2sWg3beDmlPh5v8I8VNt5iYkB_K-BfbQlG_ZZrZmT6jLA0jPGq9yMxN4di0X8N3ez4w=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-19"},{"Name":"David Kenneth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKW6jCYNEBHBskYYJWvqyCRH45irzHodHcpO-jAW4pF86NnkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s such a relief to have a beautiful, reliable roof over our house now. Patrick, Tony, and the installation crew had their work cut out for them with our 1911 Craftsman’s steep roofs, several bump-outs, and other added details. We’re also nestled pretty tightly in between three other houses, so access points were somewhat limited. But they rose to the challenge admirably. Tearing off the old composite shingle took the better part of one day, but they managed to get new underlayment installed everywhere by the end of it. Unsurprisingly, they found some water damage along the way as well, so they had to replace a few boards, which set them back a little. But all in all, they finished within the week and we’re so pleased with the result. It rained hard the day after and all the old leaks we had stayed nice and dry. Our neighbors complimented us on the new roof as well.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2d-eDUmtFETQUhKpYHm2ZBjgEZZ18juz6oY1tTKSMLDh9p8rUZkb1XSSuzmTfCKnij3wnefun5cc3kLSeTHtw9iWrFmatGDGeBmPpoUiV36NnoUUspGradpmfSqg6QkXRpsisgBA=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-10"},{"Name":"J.S. K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhTWSSydCEB8sZ1GNzOYw1Cxi3ol-xrZz7mrQm_-5zMPtXHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the black slate roof put on our house. It looks great.\nThe workman that came to tear off the old roofing and the crew that came to install were great. Tony was so respectful at all times. He always wanted us to be satisfied, and he did everything he could to make everything perfect. We would have anyone of them back again at any time. Thank you Interlock.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tqBKhGJP37vPpXxY53628yoq1QNtgj5BXdlg7wd4sRJ2OMD00h1pzSkDP7Id3wJeLqnWH7xuCCISLY6Tyl5W-ddIEZeMue9GSW0OfvWI5xtJ7j6ElG6jMaV42EGO7yO3Sg1Z06Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2cSeJJCWPS4gC00utKV6XvmfeA7EY-vmGpp9lY7ult935U3iI5G4I8CKmFwBumglSaOZy4F4hkOK0NrDhtra5YqNvxxmykCoRiJq4HfE37SHbTVuTeF4sNVKYqzkN5WW7IqB35=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2bvyav9BxGBJXh8yvRg6kLZmq5CGhLgYd29593HEtp3TX6ngkNgczm2NM2zgeIEJ4rzZ_KOZ6rtpe_3PSQ6EDvjGecEhY0HJhA2V4YWiXuht4JCVXNsaKBUuK-_n_5vQwT8uKBkg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MUWldiG0E3981qtolM3w4nrxA26EQ2xtYmo_eE_PIAvQ_Txnji5J6BHprCFHUKfjXVLb8m4Xun8TK1C1Z2D-sI6rclUVebMJqPegtiVa6q52D6b4DHgQp_2DbQzQHWMh0LxP1Hg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3qiFwwcyfOGOL07-_brNf8F02JdCu8RxkJRWLxAK12fPZ1AA7cYWChB2xzB2Dq2YfAoWxWMMB52B-zp3viU4PUKblUI57DqSPie2eFhqDZ8cQYYnFnbawneGzCsps-K1RllxvJ=k-no"],"When":"2023-6-29"},{"Name":"Aimee Conkle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOdVAsUZkOEcX59bIYFOAu6vVfR7WP42F_Vp6alD60-BwLTVhv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My roof was old and leaking and I found out the original roof flashing around the chimney hadn’t been out on correctly so it had caused some damage. I did some research about metal roofing and, in particular, roofing that is secure in windy and rainy conditions.\n\nInterlock had some great reviews. They also had financing options available, so I could make payments. As I am a single income household, that really helped me.\n\nThe install took longer than I was told to schedule, by a few months. When they did install, though, they came in and were done in less than two days! I was shocked.\n\nWe had snow after the install and it was so much more insulated. The snow just shed off the roof too, which scared me but it was sooo cool!\n\nThe neighbors love my roof and after I paint my trim and doors, I think it will look even more sharp:)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn04nUi7ymUm6Y_vlXqdzT0LCBbzpVi3ADc7Hmuv2z_-xCOIgNYjqmJuz9zMMYHZFGEbfyJvrLwNgc8ZK3d45sCKQWVZRyHfCFNv_LfUXtXKSvjo3KGCuUuvagacl75FUdpUG0QK=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3JLMy1BZ2PTCb9z_HKrnRK7sb0mFhfJmqr7oorN_SCAtpZh1W52v0HrOvTuApt7ffkgRUkz64r-atsaHqTc9BmlcPIzRq74iDjYi32CQDQlQu0Bsqe6iWZyO8x0X1wcQBzwfBm6g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0f6iNo-bbLSixi02SzpRUSnPJ8Qz3W1iANmPr6XlQGsXCaVVxQr-sbt5rYRR2t5k5u5B7aXuQNyfxJdO2yokCABp-EI87ynEoihmtOr0DHNT1oJk5ulnCo2inqNmLXzXXNODbi=k-no"],"When":"2023-3-5"},{"Name":"Annette Kleist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIU_G48Hu6J5G2h4AdsfMJQPCdo8W7EY9Dt89mpJyyuk8DEtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ivan replaced our exhaust vent on the roof that had some leaking issue. We were impressed with his professionalism, courtesy and fixing the problem to our utmost satisfaction. We certainly  would recommend him and the company for any roofing issues being it a new roof or repairs.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
