D84AVxVz9DizN6RkEiDp8NutKkOYJhI_2Vc1apSmLSQiquK-lL29JTO9AWKD3LmgA5UWa1PqLtD_oOPsuv8KpB-ldVGi_Xd0o5UKWX=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=f6PqbqjBbuzFQ2y-XbnhZA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=252.31258\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"103305827903137791094","name":"Davis Brothers Roofing \u0026 Remodeling (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103305827903137791094"},"complete_address":{"borough":"University of Washington","street":"3935 University Wy NE","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98105","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kristine16 G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfGdWQyIK-H34hhynTcrVaDuiucer0aRHjtU9Oqs-Z_B-ZPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My roof was really old and had a huge leak, so I decided it was time for a complete replacement. After researching different roofing materials that would last a long time, I contacted Davis Brothers Roofing \u0026 Remodeling for help. They arrived as scheduled and gave me a clear estimate without any pressure. Miguel and Billy worked carefully on my roof, making sure every detail was handled perfectly. The new metal trim and shingles look fantastic, and they made sure everything was finished neatly. Now, when I compare my roof to others in the area, I’m really glad I chose this company. Everyone involved in the process was polite, professional, and respectful. If you need roofing work done, I highly recommend them for their excellent service and quality craftsmanship.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Mendoza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFmlVQQyCmBjbxoR0b9ufVl5y27mEtx2XLdH5MG2mbPuBT9V0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This roofing company first replaced the roof for a friend of mine who is very particular about good craftsmanship. My friend was really impressed by the attention to detail during the estimate and the way Miguel explained everything clearly. The crew's quality of work and strong work ethic stood out as well. Later on, I had my own roof replaced by this team, and they handled everything smoothly with my insurance company, so I didn’t have to get involved in any back-and-forth. I also recommended them to my local church when we needed quick repairs and replacement on three of our church buildings. Once again, they communicated directly with our insurance, making the whole process stress-free for us. I’ve suggested this roofing crew to many friends from work and church because they truly care about the quality of their roofing jobs and always go the extra mile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"david morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHf_EDAFmQEWJa9o5_rFK0N6IwcwMcwpPElyRE2sts1Ohi5A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a roofing crew in Seattle come out to install Velux sun tunnels, replace our ridge vents, properly connect our bathroom fan vents to the roof (they were venting into the attic before!), reseal the chimney crown, and put in new gutters. Miguel and his teammate took care of everything except the gutters, and their workmanship was top-notch. They kept us informed throughout the whole project, did a thorough cleanup, and paid great attention to detail. Later on, a chimney sweep even complimented the quality of the sealing Miguel did on our chimney crown. I highly recommend this team for sun tunnel installation and any roofing needs. We did have a couple of small issues with the gutters, but the company quickly resolved them—usually within a day. Overall, their customer service and roofing skills were excellent.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hudson16 P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpJMz9YlVUgMdJlMDNNyvevTNVuwdN4EQ59S3xXzJ0IygomUY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Davis Brothers Roofing \u0026 Remodeling has all the skills, equipment, and experienced roofers needed to handle just about any roofing project. From what I’ve seen, they work on all types and shapes of roofs, no matter how big or small the job is. My home is over a century old, and I needed several different roofing repairs: replacing a metal porch roof, fixing rotten wood around an old chimney, and installing a new section of gutters by the potting shed. Even though the work took a little longer than expected, I cared more about quality than speed—and they definitely delivered. From the initial inspection by Miguel to the careful roof repairs done by Billy and his crew, I was impressed every step of the way. The new gutters were installed perfectly, and the whole team made sure everything looked great and worked well. Overall, I’m very happy with the quality and attention to detail for my roofing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"natalia andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs8e5XV7pTTCJKLv2IOlRS_rvvUZaG8dNqwzB8qdFHdPBU0vo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely the most professional, skilled, and caring roofing contractor experience i've ever had in over 40 years of working with home service companies. this team in Seattle is truly your go-to for any roofing project. Miguel was my main contact and made the whole roof replacement process so simple—he handled everything from coordinating with my insurance to managing the roofing crew. the crew provided excellent service every step of the way, always keeping me updated and explaining every detail, even down to the types of shingles and nails they would use on my new roof. these folks are top-notch and really know the roofing business. you can shop around if you want, but if you want a smooth, five-star roof replacement with no hassles, definitely go with this company and ask for Miguel. you'll be glad you did!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLA-DgLa4I7VDJZuNViodnrQ6bqGdioWTuGtMesA9mTjz-MEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently hired a roofing company in Seattle to replace our old roof. After getting a few quotes, we’re really glad we picked this team. Billy and his crew did an outstanding job. I had to be at work while they were working on the roof, but Billy kept me updated with lots of pictures and even video calls to show the progress. The new roof looks fantastic and really improves the look of our home. If you need roofing, siding, or gutters done, I highly recommend reaching out to them for an estimate. It’s great to find a reliable and honest roofer who communicates well and does top-quality work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Neil S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo31joVUlljBREfg_ECzXJkBfSvLXJJrG2_2mqnPszYkZ8ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Getting a new roof can truly change your home, not just in how it looks but also in how well it protects you from the weather. Recently, we worked with a roofing company that really stood out from the rest. Our roof was in bad shape because the last owner tried to save money by doing it themselves, so when a big storm hit, it was clear we finally needed a professional replacement. Even though we couldn’t get help from our insurance, the team made things easier for us by offering an affordable payment plan, which really helped with costs these days. From the beginning, the crew, including Billy, showed up right on time and brought a lot of skill and a clear dedication to doing quality work. They carefully inspected the whole roof, explained their plan step by step, and answered all our questions in a way that made us feel comfortable and informed. Billy was especially patient and supportive as we figured out how to move forward. What really impressed us was their close attention to every detail. They didn’t just put on new shingles—they checked the flashing, reinforced areas that needed extra support, and made sure to leave our yard spotless when they finished. Now, our old Victorian home looks amazing, and we feel so much safer knowing our new roof is ready for any storm that comes our way. If you’re looking for a roofing crew that brings skill, honesty, and real care for your home, this is the team you want. We absolutely recommend them to anyone who needs roofing work done right and wants peace of mind for years to come.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Walter Kline","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISDBf0T8U02Ixq_17628SSWsDlL7zAh0VNpgOVncc8acnqbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a big windstorm in Seattle, our roof suffered some serious shingle damage. We filed a claim with our insurance, and at first, they only agreed to replace the shingles on the back of the house. Our roofer at the time found more damaged areas and helped us get coverage for those individual shingles as well. While this was going on, Miguel and Billy from a local roofing crew were working on a neighbor’s house nearby. They stopped by, introduced themselves, and offered to help if we needed further assistance with our roof replacement. Eventually, after waiting for months, our insurance company closed out the claim without doing any more repairs, and our original roofer stopped getting back to us. That’s when I reached out to Miguel and Billy’s team. I was honestly amazed at how quickly they got to work. Miguel put together a detailed report of all the damage, included local roofing codes, a video showing repair attempts, and lots of photos. Within five weeks, they were able to get our insurance claim reopened, secured approval for a full roof replacement, and had the new roof installed. Miguel’s knowledge and organization were truly impressive. He kept everyone updated at every step, making the whole process smooth and stress-free. The crew did a fantastic job of protecting our yard and cleaning up after themselves, and they managed to remove the old roof and put on the new one all in a single day. If you ever find yourself needing roof repairs or a full replacement in Seattle, I highly recommend working with Miguel and Billy’s roofing team. They really go above and beyond to make sure everything gets done right.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
