JTSV6j=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My neighbor recommended True Shield Roofing and I am so glad I hired them! They replaced the entire roof on my 100+ year old home (insulation, sheathing, shingles), installed ventilation, and replaced the gutters. The experience was terrific from start to finish. Their attention to detail was impressive, and they conducted themselves with professionalism throughout the entire process.\n\nOut of multiple companies I requested quotes from, Ildefonso and his TrueShield team was the best value and the most transparent. Quotes I got from other companies buried additional fees in contract terms that made them seem less expensive at first glance, but after reading the fine print they would have been at least +20% more.\n\nTrueShield also stood out for their trustworthiness and exceptional communication. As this was my first time replacing a roof, I appreciated how clearly and patiently Ildefonso explained my options and provided guidance when I had questions. He was consistently respectful and made the process feel approachable and straightforward. I was even out of town for a portion of the job and trusted Ildefonso to everything on track and well managed, which he did. After the job was finished, TrueShield thoroughly cleaned my entire property as good as new (probably better) - not a single stray nail left behind. Thank you Ildefonso and the TrueShield team - highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jody Daugherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDCYvk9-KTEhZB9MfRK8WGDsqH6oSq0NEBY0yvdrVWUhVGPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had Ildefonso and his True Shield Roofing team replace my roof, damaged plywood around the edges of the roof, a leaking vent roof, and bring it up to date with the current building codes. I've been very pleased with the entire experience from start to finish.\n\nI had interviewed 7 different roofing contractors and I chose True Shield because Ildefonso was professional, communicative, and answered all of my questions without hesitation or making me feel like I was dumb for asking all my questions. When we asked for his honest opinion about which product he would choose, he didn't hesitate with his answer at all and explained why that was his choice.\n\nI was impressed with how quickly they were able to complete the work once they got started....I was expecting it to take an entire week and it was less than 3 days. The crew thoroughly cleaned up their work area and were respectful of our home and my new roof looks AMAZING! :)\n\nI've never had a roof replaced before and I couldn't be happier with this experience for a first time and I can say that I'm ready for the rainy season without any worries of leaks now that I have a new roof. I will definitely be referring them to family and friends when they are looking for a roofing contractor. Thank you to the True Shield Roofing team.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20Oafabwm4Hmjw3kYRYvTnsW3o3YOydenrBVEkmbgO8-M850VflihbnFvlfYC_SZrReY8nrfZRnCTJ3EzSQeE4Y9FyEllMpIA8M-6B8Ohun-eFotSXUF7nVL7ppchC8c2wGSII_gdzdDWC=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iTYyD1en76d_35zYtLqo1J2dapvMM4DiE6yTf7JtT2VBvxpBTtmbWsovRh4IGVNqDHaGblQlHL8xJ06Ocuw5xLPKnr_EXLORH70RtTOfA457OF0ptq4br4KjvwNsG__dy4fvoInBcZvC3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FhLro16p2eWI4ruZCoVXS8u0PRTSesTn70axWhJ2FKhX1BBTmjM2va6kjZZRyEQeYF69TjlzPSV95EhICJYCB5vf1A2UOO-gC73sG6ZTy7KvKWGqCJSnw4RGmnDMWIWMfmG30uk8e0Ow=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-28"},{"Name":"Ken Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi1PTuWY79tR39iPzM94QRtbuCGasbahOZpdSFfR6il1N0sw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently reached back out to true shield roofing due to leaking from the rainstorm we had recently. I had previously had work done by them 2 years ago for something similar. They helped replaced a few of our flapper vents on the roof and they did a great job. This time around they diagnosed the issue and did the replacement free of charge due to the issue being something similar to the last time they were out even though it wasn’t necessary for them to do it for free. I was willing to pay but they thanked me for being a loyal customer and it being a simple fix they didn’t bother charging me this time around. I appreciate it especially as we are budgeting for the holidays. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Cox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxO6F_4KeM20nF8Se07noQ7lPIoTtQmCSfMQ5MNbrTOnrcGYTI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience all around. Got a response and quote quickly. Had a leaky roof vent boot that needed replacing asap.  Guy that came to give quote found all 4 vent boots were trashed and needed replacement. They provided pictures and full details of worked needed to fix the problem right. Price was fair and the work was done the next day. So far so good no leaks.  Couldn't be happier! I will use True Shield again if I needed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Stirling-Talbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrW52aBD9NRVOb3fUsbKxdY-0QZo6daWGF36OjcxJB5twuwr4mLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not be happier with the work that HEIS roofing did. It was high quality, quick and they were very professional. I contacted a few different roofing companies to give me a quote to replace my roof. HEIS was quick to reply and come out and look at my roof. They were very professional and helpful in helping me understand what needed to be done. They had the most competitive quote of all the roofers I got estimates from. They let me know they were busy and it may take a week or two to get me on the schedule but then contacted me to let me know they had a cancellation and were able to come out much sooner. They promised it would be done in 2-3 days but were able to get some extra workers and worked from 7:30 am - 8:30 pm and knocked out the job in a day. It is rare for a contractor to under promise and over deliver. The roof seems to be very well done and has ended all our leaking problems.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3kPy79oDD9vag2dgI4emXRPi-CfI0G9NHXzg2F1Ss3wmrjUHjMdnB0-R6UTH6EtRbLiA3RWi4itb1jQxY1vRr-UkhIQyhxyK52bEmQyPDH9ckxnT2Kejx6qjLV-Df8SNJiOSKy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3rj2gjusxImZVhcSSulFwRmja1CeOlzvOK1ZzkHc9RVxQkI7007QKxS1-sldhvpteob9_mgb0C4CfRwiGHRtE3EqXz8yChNsFYTk32g1uPk0fnlShpesnkk1cN3uyPnWf_LRU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2nCGYbVQ_duRdvLHSCL0HziMEuOVQ-6GgXlkGQmQnnlIGrNqk-CeOQIpr8BLA7_hm4EZaG5aZfuwqKQZ0PE-ihz85WlFogQovS21HuMwbGsZPWZx9_EnNL9yO8bcgvjPIQ9ERp9g=k-no"],"When":"2020-6-14"},{"Name":"Lulu Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYXxtXmvgt1f2jqttaIgOFuE2sHPmlw32bDYLNqkdWTPt_PzRW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ildefonso and his team have been absolutely BEST! Over the past couple of years, they’ve replaced the roofs on three different of our property, and each time they’ve delivered outstanding results. He is professional, communicative, and the work his team does is high-quality and reliable which I like. The work was completed on time, the clean-up was thorough, and the end results speak for themselves. Everytime we couldn’t be happier with how everything turned out — the new roofs look amazing and give us real peace of mind. Highly recommend for any roofing needs!\n👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
