stions with professionalism. Tony and the rest of the installation crew did excellent work—they kept everything neat and tidy, and worked nonstop until the roof was finished. We are extremely happy with our new roof and will definitely call them again for any future roofing needs. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"aiden suarez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWHt0iNWUZ_xd7_hXge45R-sOA_Ctw-yeWMtVkPYb95sjkBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The roofing crew showed up the day before to unload all the materials smoothly from their trailer. They used a cherry picker to lift the shingles and water shield right onto the roof. The next morning, the team arrived bright and early at 7:30 AM. Four hardworking roofers got started right away and finished the whole job—including installing shingles, flashing, and replacing roof boards where needed—in just 36 hours. They brought two dumpsters and made sure to haul away all the old roofing materials. I was extremely impressed with their professionalism and efficiency. After this great experience, I asked them to come back and replace the vinyl soffits with aluminum ones on my three-story home on Mercer Island. The house has large overhangs on all four sides, some up to 4 feet deep and 50 feet long, which made it a big and tricky job. Once again, they sent an experienced crew, including Gavin, who used a sturdy ladder scaffold system to safely reach all areas. They completed the soffit replacement in just 36 hours and did a thorough cleanup when they finished. I highly recommend this roofing team—they truly do outstanding work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reese Hobbs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcyIu4mNbn9OxMS3HqIagN0zEpNifRJtNxtwUSUUGvb1LHeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After searching online and gathering several estimates from top roofers in mercer island, I decided to check out some companies in nearby areas too. That’s when I found porter family roofing \u0026 construction and was impressed by their solid reputation and high ratings. I reached out and spoke with tony, who gave me an estimate. While their quote was a bit higher than some others, I felt confident that the quality would be worth it. i scheduled a date for the roof replacement, and tony’s crew got right to work. They completed the tear-off, put down underlayment, and had the shingles ready in just a few hours. It was a warm day, and tony made sure his team didn’t overwork, letting them finish up the next morning. The difference in my roof after they were done was unbelievable. what really stood out to me was how well they cleaned up. I came home from work to a beautiful new roof and couldn’t even tell any work had been done—no mess or leftover materials anywhere. The workmanship and attention to detail were excellent. highly recommend for anyone needing roofing services in mercer island.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tasha Kane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2PDTarfclMwTaq09y48oTGvkHcgMvcsE77-ORKz15KN9lUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When my roof started leaking here on Mercer Island, I needed help fast. The roofing crew worked closely with me to find the best fix, even with some supply chain delays for important materials. Everyone I spoke with—from the office staff to the roofers and management—was friendly and always quick to respond. I got five different quotes for my roof replacement, and this team offered both the lowest price and the clearest explanations. They took the time to walk me through each cost, including different options for insulation and roofing materials. I also had an old, custom-sized skylight that needed to be replaced, and they handled it quickly and did a great job. If you're looking for a reliable roofer on Mercer Island, I highly recommend this company. They made the whole process smooth and stress-free.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carlos Maxwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9oDxh7aXSt7yUrkrn-p7maNF_Hqgk23ew7TinXMHxr3SxWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Porter Family Roofing \u0026 Construction did an outstanding job from start to finish. we got a fantastic new roof, perfect repairs, and the price was really fair. everyone we spoke to was friendly and caring. a big tree from next door fell on our roof, causing damage to the roof, gutters, and trim. we were already stressed and worried about the cost, but nicolas and his crew really understood our situation and helped us find a solution so we didn't have any out-of-pocket expenses. the team showed up on time, kept the site clean, were respectful, and did top-quality work. our beautiful new roof was completed in just one day. you really can trust these roofers to take care of you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jayce Mullins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMJcy8UGXHAs36WzgjBdxC4FvD7bfJye40hx-8pGgvV35j9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our roof replaced recently, and the whole process was smooth from start to finish. The roofing crew did a fantastic job—they arrived on time, worked efficiently, and left our property clean when they were done. I was especially impressed with how well the team communicated. Jayden, who helped coordinate the project, was very knowledgeable and answered all my questions, even when I had some unique requests. It was clear that everyone involved was on the same page, and nothing was missed. All the necessary materials were ready to go, and the team finished the entire re-roof in just one day. Watching them strip off the old shingles, install the new ones, and do a thorough cleanup showed me how experienced and hardworking they are. Any small details that needed extra attention after the job were taken care of quickly and professionally. I really appreciate the quality of both the materials and the workmanship. While I could have chosen a cheaper option, I feel confident that the value and peace of mind I got from this company was worth it. If you’re looking for reliable roofers in WA, I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marco wilcox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_5rT5EFBwD0UcWGJBb2FU-S4ESO0XTH8BM0myHi1GQvd0hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"we had a fantastic experience with gavin and the roofing crew. after discovering a leak that let water drip into our closet through a light fixture, we first called another roofing company for an estimate. that roofer told us we needed a whole new roof, which was surprising since the previous owners had recently replaced it. wanting a second opinion, we reached out to a friend who’s a contractor, and they recommended this roofing company. scheduling the appointment was simple, and the person who answered the phone was very friendly and professional. gavin arrived right on time, checked out the problem, and explained that only a small section of the roof needed repair—not the whole thing. the quote was much more reasonable compared to what we heard before. the repair was completed quickly and quietly, taking just a couple of hours. the whole process was smooth and stress-free. gavin was honest and professional, never pushing for unnecessary work. the team’s kindness and expertise really stood out, and we’ll definitely call them again if we ever need roof repairs in the future. highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandria C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgKvap1HMvpwSklgp8vS0r3tQn1of1g1pIoqhZA7WPeBkUrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for a roofer who truly cares about their customers, this is the right company for the job. Porter Family Roofing \u0026 Construction and their crew work hard to make sure your roof, the most important part of your home, stays strong and watertight. I had my roof replaced recently, and they gave me a reasonable quote, using only top-quality shingles and materials. After the replacement, I ran into trouble when another company came to re-install solar panels and didn’t attach them properly, which led to leaks. Jayden from the team responded quickly to my call as soon as the rain started and made sure the leaks were stopped right away. Since then, they’ve continued to support me and have helped communicate with the solar company to get everything fixed. I really appreciate their dedication and quick action through this entire process.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
