dicott Team was incredibly professional and straightforward with their communication and prices. The carpenters and roof installation team were very professional and fast with their repairs. We're incredibly happy with the results, thank you for all your hard work and craftsmanship.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee Janzen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-3oNgRjxlQ_QUFZwcAfcYhaKkiWgZzwkr3L8b_086iSVhm8FfHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Addicott installed my flat roof for my home. Let's be clear. Roofing my house SUCKED. Nearly every single peice of fascia had been rotted through, and several parts of the roofing overhang as well. The original flat roof was just 2 roofs poorly slapped on top of each other. I knew it, they knew it, we all had a miserable time.\n\nAddicott fixed my roof professionally, affordablly,  and had the rot removed replaced and roofed back together in only a few days. They are without a doubt one of the best roofing companies I've ever had the pleasure of working with.\n\nIts been lovely now that my house no longer leaks on me! Thank you so much!!!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3lsH047tw10I_Hfae1GKApq6jtRltwOpSavxDx93kJDlbEI-8ssd5S9-fcqHvZsvJIPQ53rBfgZZJlQPcfbFPd5lubCNRNDgEKszjDvNpQDwdHWFaURusIF2Yd1LtrkLmTdVCtDQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lPyYAUsbOjLt4i4scjt377sXAu8jQNW1ob8B2xXPzgm6XhkN-TXC23UvUwDsURDqhldoWD3zRwFFVbaOUmXGaa_39v3s6DToSO6u_kVzUcW6AyJYGPujO8N-E_KtWg_5vEB0T=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dxWxGG_q6LNPp2PQRGEzxRPSz5gE5J2Cu9_rcbNf_c0Gfz0iKJUlQYRZg64acYtKDdrQ3TXcXx79TO23LE7GcLl8FXs0_YIFc6k1Bi5qb97EsUg4knYritFCx9hFUD3qRpbtF=k-no"],"When":"2022-4-2"},{"Name":"Long","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1aDvDMLE7XXcNpJ1rs2NM4H4ETB5Z2Vk9Es838DG1-9VWtg0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rob, Spencer and crew are the real deal.\n1. They don’t mess around with their quotes, very straight forward and reasonable compare to the other guys.\n2. Professional and timely. Got our roof down in 3 days, no complaints.\n3. Great communications and flexible.\n\nHighly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C Marshall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCAEgxbYGGbpwKwy-w6sWXpS1NWyR7DHYShFS4wXy1meFbajoj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are very grateful for the excellent roofing services of Addicott Roofing! A portion of our roof is flat and the Addicott crew did a very professional, thorough and careful recoating (plus some extra helpful improvements). The owner, Rod Addicott, offers very fair prices and has been consistently honest and helpful over the years with our roofing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AVASAN CRISTIAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrTszYVL12f0XY-s3GXsxjYxY7qTv4_3qgUXI4Ifsqg6StDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I work with KGR Roofing for our commercial property, and they have been fantastic every time. They understand the unique needs of business owners and always deliver top-quality results. Highly recommend for any commercial roofing needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ken Grant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDj93dpwLXs7-oiqcPTJ0v63lhdWE_xGUJHgPMU3XQs0EZLz24sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Let's start by saying these guys live in our neighborhood, so that's a great start. But that doesn't automatically make them great. Thier finished product, the roof (and gutters etc) doesn't even make them great (although the roof is outstanding). What makes them the best of the best is their team. Incredible attitudes, easy to work with, always on time, competent, competitively priced, and professional. They don't just hire roofing experts, they hire good, kind people. These aren't words you generally associate with roofing contractors. But in this case one does. Amazing job, well done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Levi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPYP_9kFXdfHbqfKalkRePHnPyILdynwjR7ozrjAzns2KIow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Addicott Roofing did an awesome job with the roof replacement. They did good work on time for a very reasonable price. Kevin was awesome to work with, showing me and my wife the sections of rot that needed to be replaced and giving us options on things that we could keep such as the ugly, but fully functional vent cap to help save some money. I would highly recommend these guys to anyone who needs a roof repair or replacement!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
