-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After seeing reviews online I reached out to Francisco to look at my project.  I needed the entire exterior done:  siding, trim, doors, gutters, and paint.  The best part of working with them is they respond to questions within a few seconds about 95% of the time.  I had a lot of questions and a lot of little details I wanted to be done right.  I have done siding myself on a house in the past and I wanted a contractor who was willing to put up with 100 questions before the project started.  They were fantastic through the whole process and the house looks really amazing.  The crews were really fast and cleaned up at the end of each day.     I cant recommend them enough!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1LWu5DdzzB43jNCgLML8uVrfSo8sHWlDk1oEUsA9SLeiJuuX4P0S3qAZDrL_cmjqzANzbGi9nAgTHwxA9fF4u066pfnKn9ZdQWeZEmIPVHuGgjhIUjCVqW6u1mcgwcUT6filA81g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0rh30ZeK0I4TDaKa3b2xr6LCAUY7hsKjwE7oCm9u9CbRS9PrcqNf7cWBD1FW8xBFATlm6yPM9s8GvEBWLHFgeL1Qy6qCHDiCPY31J6ZCZ5iE6ctjcPVvsOqQw_nbd_yiy3miID=k-no"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Kelly M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeVSKq1JthoLFAEHsOJD3nrkiufvX-dq37GVMjvFxsBbCXnSg_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with Francisco and Revex! They acted quickly to work around the rain, and completed caulking and painting the south side of my house in two days. It looks fabulous, and I will absolutely reach out to them again as other needs come up!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn29ZaikGWG0V-zI3BjpX-lQ5JlLs7WTj_CbAs_nEU64Ko0K7xQbNKhwj4pONqir9f5xxLtjWJ4fu5EAGZkKj2yfFEwEGvfJcY13J6IbLKIRsv6wbpnBEFe2GBnSPm4v61YoqKSY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Gee5DcTRKf_HJ8pmf0YjdXNuLTnoIQQMTCMsS4QSrarlkL2lUNFM4AaB_3YGx8a9nstvpTjU1YtbOHTGVCerEQ2sQmGvbR5GKc8qtAoaL4GrHBHuNbjhyg9r-7ptvsWojAc6o=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Paul Buckley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpzrFlir7CYRhblTOPRqZlVINH2-ZXKWtwv9ei5SXpPb24QAGB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reveal Exteriors resided our house over the summer and I could not have been happier with the job and the level of service that Francisco, Tony and the team had!\n\nWe put in a request for service online, and later that day they were able to come out out and scope the job. Once we got everything signed, they got to work quickly and our place now looks great with excellent attention to detail and in areas going above and beyond the original scope of work (for example, re-trimming around our deck pillars to make them better match the new siding).\n\nThey were additionally able to be nimble and add on a few other smaller tasks we wanted done (painting the garage, re-flooring our front entryway) quickly and I appreciate how easy it was to communicate with them - I probably have 100 texts back and forth with Francisco with nit-picky questions from me!\n\nMy wife and I have recommended Reveal to a number of friends who have all also had a good experience. I highly recommend them!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cb8rYmRhQLnZ8IybaWyDjDx31xzhMp35629hieZgT3NAHjCv1MpMtJqoFnSszPJrmiFXi-TAb59vdPzl0mITACU1lckTORw-u_xXp7rzr1RTACU0iYTal6DSDXP5HghumVokaMA=k-no"],"When":"2020-12-21"},{"Name":"Casey Lisle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFprtmtEYEWwd-m4DzwrUnBNqasV8jlMhF8qBSF3VeESVwQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Reveal to do the siding of a new addition to our house. As well as paint the front of the house. The experience working with them was exceptional. Francisco was great at communicating and keeping me up to date as to what was going on. The crew was  very professional and respectful of the property and neighbors. Their workmanship is fantastic and we are very satisfied with the results. They were willing to paint only a portion of the home to accommodate my budget. Something not every contractor is willing to do. Over all I highly recommend Reveal!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taylor Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt3eZmSqJuV6crW9VWG1jutYfiEwxAvwXjV5oU1q8o6x9ksEUi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would absolutely recommend Reveal Exteriors for your exterior renovation project. The owners, Francisco and Tony are pros, honest and a pleasure to work with. At least one of the owners, usually both, visited our house every day there was work occurring, despite having many projects happening around our neighborhood and closer to the city. Francisco was great during the estimate process. He was knowledgeable and willing to talk in detail about the project. He was by far the most easy-going compared with other companies we talked to, answering our many follow-up questions patiently and was never pushy. One of the things I was most impressed with is he was willing to share (with the owners permission) addresses of previous projects and contact information from previous customers. When we inevitably ran into unexpected issues (old house, big project) Tony and Francisco worked through our options with us. I recommend Reveal to anyone doing an exterior project. They will definitely be getting the call for our next one.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynette Holden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZX8pB7jCrnl0Jeme3znCVsYAv0v6To06xA7_lLt7AyXmCxOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Revex Exteriors recently completed some siding repair work on part of our house to resolve some water intrusion issues. Isidro did a phenomenal job assessing and repairing the damaged area, installing flashing, thoroughly caulking all windows and around our chimney, and did an amazing job painting the entire side as well. Francisco also very helpful in terms of the initial assessment, walking me through the process, answering questions and providing scheduling updates as well. We’d definitely work with Revex Exteriors again!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
{"input_id":"03503648-78d9-4cf4-8a41-65787f6e558d","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Star+Roofing+%26+Construction,+Inc/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x549aa999b087f73b:0x61f14c8e209e1b10!8m2!3d47.844965!4d-122.2211116!16s%2Fg%2F1pty08q6n!19sChIJO_eHsJmpmlQREBueII5M8WE?authuser=0\u0026hl=en\u0026rclk=1","cid":"7057506264382577424","title":"Star Roofing \u0026 Construction, Inc","categories":["Roofing contractor"],"category":"Roofing contractor","address":"16912 9th Ave SE, Mill Creek, WA 98012","open_hours":{"Friday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Monday":["9 AM–5 PM"],"Saturday":["Closed"],"Sunday":["Closed"],"Thursday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Tuesday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Wednesday":["8 AM–4 PM"]},"popular_times":{},"web_site":"http://www.starroofinggroup.com/","phone":"(425) 290-7827","plus_code":"RQVH+XH Mill Creek, Washington","review_count":30,"review_rating":3.8,"reviews_per_rating":{"1":7,"2":2,"3":0,"4":1,"5":20},"latitude":47.844964999999995,"longtitude":-122.2211116,"status":"","description":"","reviews_link":"","thumbnail":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGm6NJtyk4FKaaffVGzP09JzuYAxibiGLOfqmDudQf3GTI-gajEHWMuflHbf0VqLH1eCds4ImK2olnSQGpYeIeskHIk89F6P0rJbe0cG7HNat88DRVHiqUopawjYerHipJ_pL_fGw=w408-h306-k-no","timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","price_range":"","data_id":"0x549aa999b087f73b:0x61f14c8e209e1b10","place_id":"ChIJO_eHsJmpmlQREBueII5M8WE","images":[{"title":"All","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGm6NJtyk4FKaaffVGzP09JzuYAxibiGLOfqmDudQf3GTI-gajEHWMuflHbf0VqLH1eCds4ImK2olnSQGpYeIeskHIk89F6P0rJbe0cG7HNat88DRVHiqUopawjYerHipJ_pL_fGw=w397-h298-k-no"},{"title":"House","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFo6-1Hhccpq2q93i3zsxJqkrz-f4-sCC78d1VBcBGPIByAMUhkjNvjG5TxCBR0h3r8PoV45f10U9vrrhPYkh1S0GR37yGCiOztpt8I2bQ6An3PYJCGLY2ETW4VRc5ECJ2RX-oE=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=pg3p7r8uwUZVwizMNVE-sw\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=264.89465\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"106610129410757746949","name":"Star Roofing \u0026 Construction, Inc (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106610129410757746949"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"16912 9th Ave SE","city":"Mill Creek","postal_code":"98012","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Connie Hawkins-Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYKWi849naBbphbP9Mc4xNPK-47FZDN6uGUN9t6nRbzLVw1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In 2010 we had Star Roofing replace our roof and they did a great job for a reasonable price. They also replaced our 3 skylights with new opening ones for a great price.14 years later we noticed that the roof was sagging by one of the skylights. Thinking it was a water intrusion I called Star Roofing as they have a great warranty. After some discussion with Chris, he sent Nick out to check on it. Nick sent some pictures back to Chris and he noticed the sagging roof bays were above our brick chimney. He thought it might be caused by no lower roof vents due to the chimney being there. He sent Nick out to remove the roofing on the effected area and sure enough there was no water intrusion and indeed caused by the lack of venting from the homes original construction. There was some damage to the top of 2 roof joists so Nick went and got material to repair them. He had everything repaired and the section re-roofed in one day!! Even with the fact that it was not their fault, they didn't charge me a thing. I don't write many reviews, but when I get such great service I have to let others know. I would definitely recommend Star Roofing not only for a new roof, but for roof repair also. Thanks Star, Chris, and Nick, J.T and Connie Adams.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve \u0026 Lisa Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXBRi541SbTRMJNNYaJFmOlH8L9RE94kYO063wHhVWaqfJNaHn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I work for a condominium complex and used Star roofing for replacing two of our multiplex buildings this year and two last year .I have nothing but good things to say. The company was prompt at getting us on their schedule, The roofers were fantastic, they cleaned up all the debris when they were finished and answered all my questions along with keeping me updated on the progress. I have also used Star roofing for cleaning out gutters and clogged downspouts. They are quick to respond and very friendly.  I would highly recommend Star Roofing for all your roofing needs.  Big or small.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Voce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjf6gBNJB0y_yZ-zHeouOQP1S2fhyi6ohKX2ULeInrEyCXlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my torch down flat roof replaced with a membrane and pitch package (flat roof) about 7 years ago by Star Roofing.  A pretty significant warranty issue was found by me and the owner (an old crew chief made an error). He fixed it in full and any subsequent small issues have always been addressed -- today on short notice a potential leak caused by a blockage in a scrupper was addressed. His current team I have worked with over time is great. I highly recommend them as they stand behind their work. When I have need skylights replaced, the process has always been smooth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrrNWHbU5pwXG0mjJ3BgxdrpbDU6dibdFfKl3e-onRUiFKwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"For all those 5 star reviews in here, I'm guessing you were not asking for a roof repair under warranty. If your roof leaks, and it is under their warranty, this is what you can expect to occur... you will call and they will be super responsive and send Nick right out. He will look at it and take pictures, tell you he will call back to get you on the schedule. He won't. You will call every third day, not to be too pesky. The secretary will be really friendly and promise to have either Nick or Chris call you. They won't. You will finally call early enough to catch Chris in the office. He will say he knows nothing about it and that he can't get ahold of Nick to find out what his assessment was. He will tell you he will send out roofers on Monday to start the process over. You will take the day off work, because your roof is leaking... but, they will not show up. You will call and talk to a very nice secretary again, who promises that Chris will call you before 7pm. He won't. Then what will you do? Report to the BBB? Hire an attorney? Pay for an attorney? Give up and pay another company to do it? What would you do then? So, before using this company, consider... what will you do when they don't honor their warranty?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garrett Disco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQOCel9SSM_HDAFzWSNjBNUXQWgxpYs-5VAmcfcO34OCErksg0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I called Star Roofing to repair a commercial TPU roof they built 15 years ago (not under warranty). They spent a few hours attempting a fix, but ghosted me when it was still leaking a few days later. Had to hire another company to finish the job. They just caulked it, rather than a patch / weld which is appropriate for this material. Wasted a lot of my time. The best thing I can say about them is that they reduced the volume of the leak until I could find some better help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsni9G4ZYZi4axrnLiqtBU2xkyC2z3a-821pgBBywXjWwPMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Had a new roof put on. So far so good. Had nee gutters installed at the same time. I boiced my concern about the facia needing teplaced to attach the gutters too., they said they were ok. Now have sagging gutters that overflow in low spots due to not being secured properly. We now have two phone calls into them with no response for close to two months now.  They are still under warranty . Would at least expect response. Bad business practice. Will not recomend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Peckham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5ACuDvnUaYWafSukfX3z8l_oHxUGbk57pkMrPGvMZ0RhP3-I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They did a great job. Took care of the leaks,replacement of plywood,cleaned gutters as need and cleaned everything up really well. And put barers around all the vents. I would highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jay mezistrano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAAcVx5gjT6OGjOQ4c9_e6_4Pnqq0fZT8f4JmU8QMTOtJoQRP_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"2/16/17 - I attempted to use Star Roofing and gave them a call - we talked and i emailed them the details of the roof repair/ I expected to hear back and didn't - a littler irked because the girl who answered the phone said she would get it to the right person. - Nothing happened so i called back on 2/27 and had the same conversation - i also verified while on the phone that she received my email - didn't hear back just like before - called again on 3/14 as i need to get the roof fixed for my tenant and let her know that this is the 3rd time. She apologized and said she would get back to me that day - which was 3/14/17  - it is now 3/23/17 and i am going to give up on Star Roofing.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
