"Description":"Very knowledgable team from ownership down to service techs. Great company that is honest, reliable, professional and has tons of experience solving complex roofing issues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIag9YepXHnd5TRbuydzr340fCvBXdfJGiYYDDJFoWR9qpgNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a bad storm tore up a section of my roof, I called Jimmy's Roofing and they came out the very next morning to assess the damage. Jimmy himself showed up, walked me through everything that needed to be fixed, and gave me a fair, detailed quote on the spot. The crew was on-site within two days, worked fast without cutting corners, and had the whole roof repaired and looking brand new by end of day. They even spotted some flashing issues I didn't know about and fixed those too at no extra charge. No surprises on the bill, no mess left behind — just honest, quality work from start to finish. Jimmy's Roofing has a customer for life. If you need a roofer you can actually trust, stop looking and call them now.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Powell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM0f5EhGdQaGUeeU5Py14WJfcaXI7YdHJjiovj-EB6eoyHMCXL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Super rude driver, was tailgating me and honking because he was in a hurry. Pretty dumb to do in a company truck.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
