wner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEo1UQN8CO30T4A1EyPdJ-JrTmc2bHWWaCtbMya4uY7j56rpQfbyaVeWId2A_hxQ1e5DGQN02hN4o5BPXbaQBnsDZYse7nyXltNQEsIYZJjm48DlbVqhVbdB1A_B8be-sBXH_3A=w495-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=WYaOMVfD1iDUNKacktCu8A\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=268.2716\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"116832832774798943264","name":"Sharp Roofing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116832832774798943264"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Matthews Beach","street":"10723 Exeter Ave NE","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98125","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Alan Travers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlAuukf3_Z5U57Jto0lXZEUUYOCs2IJiXcNKr6yMF_Qop4FaHI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Owner is an amazing human. Hard work for a fair price. Extremely knowledgeable in all aspects of his trade. Red Seal educated. Would HIGHLY RECOMMEND! Extremely grateful for my new roof! A lifesaver in time of need! Thank you Shane and family. 👍🏼","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kari Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGmPMcYK43_44nEuEAPHU4Mv3JGwy9DBh88mzeLQSt5iSbuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent customer service, consistently detail orientated and dynamic regarding the types of roofing services available. He has a lot of experience which shows. Don’t look any further, call Sharp Roofing today. You’ll be glad you did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimberly simmons-merino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS9miqYCV8uRD0Iy3lBH6fYIax365o_5Zyf1rM4i7yQtFKaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used Sharp Roofing several times for my cedar shake roof.  In every instant they have been response \u0026 professional. Their estimates are reasonable \u0026 they do not include unnecessary work, \u0026 their work is fabulous. I am also a real estate agent \u0026 I recommend them highly! Don’t call anyone else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendy Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR-E37uusONVsgAvGdj_MVEKrgICL2M5npSDzNbqJOMMhOTZkm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has been a pleasure doing business with Sharp Roofing, a first rate company!\n\nI requested new roof quotes from many different companies and Cliff (and team) replied right away and offered great pricing!\n\nEverybody on the team was responsive, professional, helpful and they completed the job quickly and with quality work.  They did a great job!\n\nWe called them after the roof was installed with a follow up on the punch list.  We made an unwarranted request and they came out right away to take fix the problem, even though they didn't cause it.\n\nWhat a great company to do business with and we look forward to doing business again next time we have roofing needs!\n\nI would highly recommend them to others...  Thank you Sharp Roofing!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Upham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNp71-56WgiRauEUEqK0gSkxScXC6Jr-jipmrO2oIQG52Qhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was prepping to sell my home that had a 16 year old cedar shake roof and was given Sharp Roofing's information by my realtor.  I was seeking an inspection to understand the state of the roof, whether there was any remaining life to it, and to verify no leaking had occurred.  The owner of the company responded promptly to my inquiry and offered to come out and visit my home the same day and he provided a detailed report with images a few days after.  A few weeks later at my request, Sharp was able to provide a roofing certificate to aid in our sale.  I have been pleased by Sharp's responsiveness and level of detail.  I'd happily use them again and recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samira Moshtagh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMmqGTxZcE4-8x1b4OTEntpN9PIo-K87AQmu-gfMo7yt9Zug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Sharp Roofing to get an estimate for a commercial property right before Labor Day weekend. Within minutes of calling, Cliff emailed me letting me know he was working on the bid. He went to the property and gave us an estimate right away. I would recommend Sharp Roofing to all my clients and friends. They are prompt, professional and won't charge you extra fees to just give you an estimate. I am extremely happy with their service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"April Shiosaki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSUegNC-wVhdhwgJ6y2NY3IKbiN-v_3vRy734MHXrpbtBShmdH9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We appreciate the communication and the work from Sharp Roofing! Cliff came out to the house and completed a very thorough inspection and came up with a quote with including details of how the repairs needed to be completed allowing us to make an informed decision. We highly recommend Sharp Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greta Niemela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJD3XQpMfMSTCGhJMO_M0AHF2Z8jPSYt7xlv_5CkdPn9pwTlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My husband and I called Sharp Roofing for an estimate on a total roof replacement on our 4-plex. Dan Gibson met us at the property and promised a call back within a week with a full estimate and recommendation. He not only did not call us back but has not returned our phone calls to him. Would not recommend working with this company - communication is key to any business and it is obviously not their strong suit.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
