ecting. I've had a very positive experience with Stout Roofing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36IRRSVhfr-6yfg_Dm0TbOZY145n8ObQi3RprlmVeqBp8iJsnzz35Wx7Xpp8XyJQg0QbK7DQ4UkrEQqoHRGpXqf_iHMdTAvRgc02zPrF_2M4o3MpiTAXwId42PCfIEeZVmCZypRNdri1M6=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2cY2wOSg5FH0j0irB6mFh__OrpVTRCcrL0_m9E3Z_MOUvL7yDnJgexq2wRGO80-t2P0vYSojwZOeDsbObvRJT7FjAa5dndjCnMot1MpdupV9J-6Y5W5VIV-zvX3byu053zhdm5ZxWeqa9g=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-15"},{"Name":"Grace Yao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqOJVIbrestfGNUsJGcIGoY0wP2P6eQXJr-PtHbGgOgU9Y4uNxlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The roofing crew did an excellent job replacing our roof over four days—efficient, professional, and incredibly courteous. They delivered high-quality work and left everything spotless each day. We’re very happy with the results and highly recommend them!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12oklvCyXI_HTZLigx1P7oMr3VyxtGGhpH63zKCBZioEmgrhNvF1WwbfEV7oqWTf-T7XqS289-PwZqRbmM8OiB4pdgACc_An0BnsZ3PRgy_LELHqN_yimTlnYwbFGAD7geXPlgSljvMrw=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-17"},{"Name":"Ciaran Rochford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpAsS6wy6za-Wl2oKAAaTWun9SgUnK_mUpRPRcHkyCJ43r6YaX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have hired Stout roofing to replace 2 different roofs for us over the year. We have been very impressed. Jake is very knowledgeable and helpful. They turned up on time always, did quality work at a very fair price, cleaned up properly and were friendly throughout. I highly recommend.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lrJ_CEVpHMt47w48llQ3bFW8CNQW3OwixZev510VdFbfvQzIHNWEN9nm0ellAKajP2006gbPAT8EbEvrDyiDUzwQTfShAYDDlESkCyOU6-T2uDjFMMiAAJBxiHR8aiE6Cdw=k-no"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Evan Mathiasen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzioaJreN17RCa8ryph6AMyAW9MakLwaLcRS9MDNkFbWaJJXKVWA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stout did a great job on our new roof. Jake was on time for our bid appointment and gave us a very fair bid. He explained what was included and our options.\n\nHis crew came out the day of, and started work immediately. Just a word to those working from home, your house will sound like World War III and an earth quake all in one. So don't plan on having any meetings or be very productive. It was LOUD!\n\nUnfortunate for us we had water damage from improper installation 25 years ago from the previous home owner. We had to replace 70 plywood sheets. Jake informed us prior to the work and we could see how bad it was. He also worked with us on the price because it was so extensive.\n\nAfter they were done there were a few action items left and those were taken care of promptly by his worker Jim, who was very nice and got them all taken care of.\n\nThank you Stout roofing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0W56kf5-0GBVur7Bt1UPtGL5oCf_75pzfZZSZGwObBd7Sf-3QusnFNXiee4NeMrGzEV-soyEGHHgRatEYqIB5ywPN0yZNgDuRazcQyTvT58kdOJFDn62p8pLMGAot7bXpr0VoEVg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0aH_mJF2E9xnTawcmvd7HnkQdUzR52LJGXaSHjkctkmGeYGV5DoxsT2laknC4J_LMZ74vqqhHbpK7iWXsDHzQ6Q_SRfzsP3riJ4D3PtaiMp9WUjfQ41jakyWeTun__o0_xOto=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2aCcdPgSqF2ShSwqbe2sa5VXpd2Zb7OhcSfFdasxXadQKz00CAXn3hjubNNSJHsOBwY_BJV_kHQzha3k75aO4C8e1_lu9zMB3mEVd_q6A_FuVwTW4iIf4zhOxcehAKsSsZVjkNag=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2IAu3asXKqmbcbrOOpcY2QGz-tfqHXTHkewpC3OdX4VT4kdpAFz_8vXd3InpB4OqX1WqdVVNvaM7Bboky6zoFlq-bTlJUqIyf1caaGXH_zqGHp7shaF0FBoiwlRu7TlO1h2rM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VI7XjcufpEk82vIRDnVrEb5foWjmaiTGtutVcr_Hx2uS-Qlen6kO7Vd5rkqQUcX15lo3mwaSYFEEfD0i6HqiTH146ZDDolDlhRD5dFQsNT6oT9f8g-ZAB5IftcFtV1jgaqgBx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0MmutgxqtSM2PnrDdXKro0FYwzHAIc8hn7yZ-Y-O8fU5F0zg_dz3b