-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Getting a new roof can be a stressful process, but Shaun and his team at First Roof Service made it painless. The owner, Shaun, was very responsive and professional. He answered all of our questions quickly and thoroughly via email, which made the initial process smooth and reassuring. The crew was professional: they were fast, efficient, and completed our entire roof replacement in three days. If I need to do a gutter or roof cleaning, I will definitely hire them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sarah armstrong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIt4J3DN0w5tiJh19aUJ-HzLAqY9t80LnbKKJ9bA3ZZ04Ms-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First Choice Roof is an awesome company.  We first used them to clean our roof back in 2017 and they did an outstanding job so we called them back to do another cleaning this year. Easy to get an appointment- arrived on time- very friendly - very efficient - great price.  We recommend them and look forward to using them in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patama Gomutbutra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHszu897KYXeHeR-jGdnHNaWTzOxlteko0PM2mRDSzFaQLBFL4OA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They do a good job at a reasonable price for roof cleaning. I’m giving four stars because, while the representative provided sufficient information, their communication skills could be improved. The service itself is fine, but if I find another company with equally good work and more polite communication, I may switch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elena K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpaU793b3nETYE7aAy5FZ7uZ08UjVIvb0rhA_BDycaQvFXJ0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so glad I went with this company! They did an amazing job on my two-story cedar shake roof, which is pretty steep and not easy to work on. I honestly didn’t think it could ever look this good again, but now it looks almost brand new. On top of that, the worker went above and beyond - he cleaned up all the debris, washed the deck, and even the windows. Really great attention to detail. I couldn't be happier, and I definitely recommend them to anyone looking to get their roof cleaned or repaired.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trish Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIVy-V67Xt59N3NnxK_b4tH1UUrxstDT11WfP7nyjuCR3uR7Dh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!\n\nEffectively finished re-roofing for two of our properties! The recent project was completed over four days and presented more significant challenges than we had originally foreseen.\n\nA big thank you to Shaun and First Choice Home Service for their exceptional efforts. Shaun's dedication and reliability are truly amazing. The work quality is outstanding, and although Shaun might not be the most affable person, his commitment to productivity is unwavering.\n\nShaun is always  patience in addressing questions and doubts. If I could, I'd rate him and his team 10 out of 10.\n\nIf you would like to get the roof done right at the first time, call Shaun. He will take care of it for you :) Above and beyond😍","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HNrshIwz_fsZIUqcJ2YFQm7avaywSCxXX-Qz95Gjjp7-YHnzf07bqM2VACcG93OAWorrKbcX5HVmmL8q0DXZEBixR1Tph7moOk7Z4dL_OXJxTuCrp2BLb8-lmf9EkLkdud_rW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xdkfucNzHXvmwWkCZsicEF9Sn4-SdLb8iNaXHQkLWZWTUi04JDEILGHW08IcspJwGoOVTHTYo3UuE5gzz74mMi1Nk8tNQEP714BipVJtVpo8sr_zbqkwS2C4TdIPONnFNiu1o4w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1G4s0WXo2h2yJcdpl5LFzFKBmPxZAqxTpL1WNw_-Nwp-ZyWeYnXQKEHocf1PHEvlKiOhRmZhgSq09DMd54ZkhsKAT3Ixykd0SI2EGRSHEx5MNuZQdi-eft9C3mee2mIsDPaYs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0adCqHx1mntyASewtQYvgIixRkY7CrKLxMg9eybc6vxRB7ctUEyhWLPiS41PW7K5x65TRmm6CBkKBXBQKAbMOgc5GxOC0jvQbOAr_pgtlM43czCAx6b7