Pq-JFdJLVdSyHM2YBd_iPZ5RM2I1Oxe1CxiGnGN3RTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Landmark by my colleague and she was right! The owner, office staff and all the crew members are all excellent, very responsive, reliable, on time and hard working. Landmark helped me maximize the benefits from this project while offering a great quality and competitive pricing. They will give you honest feedback. Make sure to talk to the foreman at the beginning or before the project to get the best results. I was impressed that they finished the project that involved a lot under the time they did while not compromising on quality. I strongly recommend Landmark.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Martel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJEBcfUOaaFyJTSRRQbrMfDuPmMDaJ9a-CA1jRtlbAqOeen5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had three areas where siding needed to be replaced. Rener walked the project with me before providing an estimate. After getting the estimate, I had some follow-up questions about the process and also wanted to make sure the existing siding would tie in well to the new siding. My husband spoke to Rener on the phone, and, after the call, he said “let’s book him. I like his approach.” Normally my husband is a get three quotes kinda person, but not this time!  Landmark did a superb job. The carpenter came out early that morning to take a look at the siding we have to match it as close as possible. The project turned out great! Now I just have to paint it, but the hard part is done thanks to Landmark. Overall, Landmark was communicative (shoutout to Kathy!), respectful of property (I was worried about my plants and flowers being damaged, but the carpenter was very careful and didn’t harm them at all), and thorough! Highly recommend this company.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2gbOP2VQFP4ITii_N2RzyR_mEoOYuhkpMrEqUNYWbUXeewN5r4m49shJiH46r_-nPFFxvaoesDA1KgIO9oD-iw8DweIXwLo