back to me soon. I really liked that the initial estimate was given in person, with a clear explanation of what my options were after doing an actual physical examination of my roof. I had my roof, 3 skylights and gutters replaced; the estimate was highly competitive with my other estimates and the final cost was exactly what they said it would be. The contract paperwork they sent was extremely well presented with clear expectations of what they would be doing. The work itself is excellent--and continuing to prove so throughout this rainy season. The workers were courteous and respectful of my property; clean-up was excellent.  There was a tiny glitch at the beginning when getting on their schedule to complete the job--but I know that at the time I was arranging my replacement they were going through an office shake-up that had contributed to the issue. Once I called to confirm that I would be on the schedule soon, they worked hard to keep me well informed by following up many times as they worked through the scheduling; they also apologized profusely for what was really a minor problem.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ravi Blake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrixNAmFk7VEa-P-QNDLPlzyjkcYolYz6w6lJlcdPc4FMz-9c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently chose Landmark Roofing and Siding for a roof replacement and the experience was solid from start to finish. The crew was respectful and clean, and the job was complete on the schedule we agreed upon. I definitely recommend this roofing company for anyone looking for a trustworthy exterior team","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ranga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvCOrOjzmo3y1wwcae6zR61QK5OTNqpefkpd6HcbQuho1853o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had a very disappointing experience with Landmark Roofing \u0026 Siding Company. They installed windows at out house and attached are some pictures of drywall work. The craftsmanship was subpar, and there was a clear lack of quality control throughout the project. They delayed the work several times and left many jobs unfinished. I cannot recommend this company based on my experience.\n\nThe reason for 2 stars is because of the help from the owner to fix some issues.\n\nUpdate (March 27, 2025): While I appreciate the owner's response, I must add that contrary to what was specified in the contract, the work was not inspected by the company's Quality Assurance team. I have no reason to make false claims - my only goal is to help other consumers make informed decisions based on my actual experience.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EUmlVptQuPa46MYnMsNr4f8Hc2OGQyJDQ62MyfxJW5-PzewN-Zf8pWK2dHW646eApxzy4u3NPuEGuVt4fPfrQwVpcLBgajxKsPvgVFso04Zv_ks0pkoUrw2tYhFkYYwTcXz9d_w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0TAzk8RHBGbH7tqgstwUwDmhjFN6f2PAL6ZAFwpW8l3vzawBudkjUHKkke6txZZdV6J83mzJqTUSbB9OOx6nrNJg5UIVXEE6xHlpSH6-TAzhpgpIgl_yVQ0pu38IHahOIdWZo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_H2cuvj3hZcnbfUlYrqFeIfwHzH3bled8JhKNg045W_Sq3XRzye8cdCs8uMZc8Wnbr_5-lsQFxifigPoqfJRkIXVQiIFAE09aPIl1DRrZ4QHvy8e_xxJVZqN0jrkoyQRSe1WPYQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0jTx-L3vbSTTJJPVB6lO5WVUvaI0aXu5DS2fCxYAuCDri2RTDX6twJv9NLOy03cY7WaWzM1U65uccQUdRTShL__AoW4Y-cVqtVCoWGhB2pHnRpAK_Y_lnq_5v5jIzWzEwrXEwX=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37sKEpfclEJuz_3f0AmYJzQ32jrb-Ku9HCFmMLl3kTq9X1PUqwEXdKqqvI5VvPFg4SAZHmNyYS7aPD09hGzBbMaL6-gPQQvEfveDsuMJMICQLxDRW1XCuU-F9NdLuaHS8ma7JGXg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1DFBJXm_oLz4Cu00ah8Ns_xOU_lwokYbgw4xsJ58OcsAuxbvQj3XHDu_9AWOe7ivHWxVFd9c7XRpuyUIN8Eq9N1QTNH8DlPLVzBi2cOAr2mM6negik0dlrUhEoT7E1acItfBWE=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-5"},{"Name":"Jason T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI40eTdAs-nSw_Yav_HgKil8BHzZdXj1LhcSFTZflj9RMo2Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"after a small leak showed up in our living room ceiling we called landmark roofing and siding for a roof inspection and roof replacement. The estimator explained option clearly, the crew kept the yard tidy, and the new roof and trim look great. for a roofing company that communicates well and delivers quality work they were a solid choice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Derke Norwood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV65iouEifAHE_nJiJ9kiaVHc4EAe1xEBjqhEhbIUCjjnAfkaxr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired Landmark for a residential siding repair job. During the project, we discovered additional repairs that Landmark could help repair. The team communicated clearly and has us moving forward quickly. I’m satisfied with the quality of the work. I recommend working with Jordan and the Landmark team.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
