ed":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Robert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8KxzII8swCDORzkIfqZEQokB-fbFqEMRXuEToY-nZRATwiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our roof developed leaks 6 years after a shoddy solar installation. We hired Pinnacle Roofing for their expertise in both solar and roofing. This was very apparent at the initial visit when Keith came to assess the damage. He was thorough (walked the roof and the attic), knowledgeable (explained the existing problems as well as product options and materials), responsive (always returned emails, calls and took action as necessary), and just a pleasure to work with. Communication was great from the time leading up to the project through completion.\n\nThough we chose not to have the solar reinstalled, we did have them completely remove the system (panels, conduits, electrical boxes, etc.). The removal was clean and professional. They stacked the panels on pallets, patched holes in the siding and left no trace of the old system.\n\nThe roof installation was amazing to watch. They replaced plywood as necessary. They installed flashings as you would expect, but little details like diverters in the corners to the gutters and folded over the gable ends just added to my satisfaction. At the end of every day, the grounds were cleaned and free of debris and nails.\n\nI am very happy with our new roof and highly recommend Pinnacle Roofing for the job.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vRaZ0-kS7DSQT3QpJd0VZZv8xsDxfFfItKaUeLej0uviMAnF6Ntl3W4rpZMAcdkRnFpobrWp9dzI3lVt-ZyoZIBe95IiOwJkxUdp1VDlyNWlpO3R7oOSWVSzfY0QwyFPPjET5JXwiz7yN=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Gg_2587Ev5uFpkmj2HaufkRM2JGzC7hQtfNRNJTHv6feL9aTikOS4mED-dYx8OcDC7x7vmW5Np9SxRvSBSi_eQrAf22m4oWMldrnAagJmlp2ntu37mBVX26EWzHH6AS5Dm8PLnHV44Ove=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0p8rZFFRQXZGGtQEO9qbCgH0Rb1T2cEkffMQwd2tokSJlhIA3m8LzvL9CFGhAiI6bA09cTLqGrX5XwgiR_1v7Emu_jw9v3Ry_mS43_KgWGzRJ_8Q6cHCBpPCMiDQykwdwJ9ghUiMeJYkM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0U0cMmxlMRc5WsH-MWdcesMSWr7sJKltiUa87pMp5ZOiy_VQJu3AqxAF2EnZJLPYMvjE5qxUbEqsm0LiJznYHVrngmITNE_qz9STXCfbDs5up4FaMxQlel57GLHg1pEoNKvJzieKnOqXg=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-16"},{"Name":"steve phelps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBiIwxpzpdTeOQ-11htKN_Z0XizfFWro__cfyIM-Jnm0YGhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pinnacle did an excellent job re-roofing my house and garage.  From the initial inspection and material selection through the roofing process itself they were professional and efficient.  The job site was also kept very clean.  I highly recommend Pinnacle Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nora Lansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5WvNdRxtUiD8rQoXt2uhP7AeEm9WRRSZGDWeEZCsfWpt1iea9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extraordinarily responsive and professional. After having tried (and failed) for months to get a roof repair project started with other roofers in the area, Pinnacle was on the job in literal hours. Absolutely amazing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINYRECCV3g_hvg3qlCJFSipXmMwEyHNX3okRQFwbidK4NOLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t usually write reviews, but I felt like I needed to for Pinnacle. One of our neighbors had their solar roof done by them last year and spoke very highly of their experience. We weren’t looking for solar, but decided to reach out anyway since our neighbors were so happy with the work. Later on, when our roof was being done, Lenny, the owner, stopped by to check on the progress and realized they had done our next-door neighbors’ roof a few years ago too!\n\nWe got bids from several companies (8 total... yeah, maybe a little excessive), but we chose Pinnacle for a few key reasons. Curt was friendly, knowledgeable, and incredibly patient with all our questions. He even went up into our attic when we pointed out some damp spots on the ceiling. After his visit, he sent us a detailed quote that included a smart vent (edge vent) for air intake and a ridge vent for exhaust to improve attic ventilation. Ridge vents seem to be the new standard for exhaust, but some other companies didn’t really address the intake issue, which was important to us since we only had small soffit vents.\n\nInstead of the large rectangular intake vents that a couple of other companies suggested, Curt recommended the smart vent option (“edge vent”). We really appreciated that he cared about both function and appearance. In our case, it wasn’t installed right on the edge, but about a foot in from the edge of the roof. Even so, we think it looks great and blends in nicely with the new roof. Curt even mentioned that once they removed the old roof, if the attic space over our covered patio turned out to be connected to the main attic, they would continue the smart vent there too, just to keep it uniform, and they’d do it at no extra cost. That showed a real level of care and attention to detail.\n\nThe work itself was done in two days (Friday and Saturday). The crew was efficient and left everything clean. There was one small issue: they forgot to install a new roof cap for our kitchen vent. But to be fair, it wasn’t their fault. The previous owners had remodeled the kitchen and removed the attic ductwork, so the old cap wasn’t actually connected to anything. We brought it up with Lenny since we were planning to do the proper ductwork, and he had someone come out and take care of it.\n\nAfter the roof was done, we had a few attic companies come by to give us quotes for insulation, and they all commented on how well the roof was done.\n\nWe’re really happy we went with Pinnacle and wouldn’t hesitate to recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwRvcHHI14d1CtD_pUI3VHYpoqPlJf_oB0NcyBe1Ior7h7VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Approximately a decade ago Pinnacle Roofing Professionals replaced our roof and did an excellent job. Recently we reach out to them again for a roof repair due to windstorm damage. It was a bit of an unusual situation, but they were willing to work with it. Keith was particularly helpful in facilitating the job. A very professional contractor which I would definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ryan mcphail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFhiZddtZ3iv3KXW5gLx4Q-FdzoM_srgAh-Yx_imyGyrJElQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my roof and gutters and had solar done on my house. They are an amazing company to work with, communication, workmanship, and cleanliness. I have been in construction for almost 30 years and will say these guys were a pleasure to work with. I would highly recommend if you are getting your roof replaced or gutters or solar, this is the team you should get.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_r2NbbzTBvUrrDhp1mKU15lItlaTrRRK41vZ94dhs-tPZIG7mcrWZisGxJJvsKE20mk3HapFFSQpr70g8U_XBe6yrkXZPSZQ_0cV7i8aq5mgLJIdAUXY0YLV_llit-ehuMfLt=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ksA54wFlUu8WIQN_lposHdM3zF-TP9KNv3vja57Pr3ilBHPuJ_d-anqYsXiCZ0MVrwctu51VS7A28UHmzqeSOWhV3mNfRlpZ265epZ_aJaNfhMzrajPPwE8D8Rw4aI_zYoc4DoA=k-no"],"When":"2020-7-20"},{"Name":"Bill Gunnells","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEGwPozP4W0gab6VB_5vmecjmKCYYT2vySlJFdEcBPGt58kd3H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pinnacle Roofing recently completed a solar installation at my residence, and their service was exceptional. The team was not only professional and courteous but also incredibly accommodating to unforeseen changes in the schedule, a testament to their flexibility. What I appreciated the most was their dedication to keeping me informed, allowing me to make a well-informed decision about the installation. Their attention to detail and customer service is truly commendable. I would definitely recommend Pinnacle Roofing for their outstanding work and customer care.\nBill","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andy Pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUW6iZW6sOaUnkzyi7j1jXBUaPUqCYmx7832RMmfWx_Mk5YjfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I interviewed 5 different roofers and ultimately landed on Pinnacle for my job. I needed a new roof and gutters and had been contemplating solar. Pinnacle won out on all three for their options, professionalism, and knowledge.\n\nI'm so pleased with the work they did and get frequent compliments from our neighbors!\n\nThey arrived on time, communicated frequently and nicely, cleaned the job, and did exactly what they said they would do when the said they'd do it. Truly a wonderful partner.\n\nBook them today with utmost confidence!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
