the winter months and the team that was doing the work did an amazing job of ensuring everything stayed dry even when we had some pretty wet weather between the time the old roof came off and the new went on.  I’m very happy with the outcome! Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olga Kuznetsova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5nSZ6-OcFRjMbFSxAVFCvyfPSIs5DLs11jume8iFhqTm_egh4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roofsmart is the best roofing company we’ve ever worked with. Everything — from the initial consultation to the new roof installation — was excellent, and we are very happy with the end result.\n\nJim was incredibly helpful and knowledgeable. He clearly explained our options and the reasons behind each recommendation. Jim discovered serious issues with our roof that every other company we received estimates from had overlooked. He also worked directly with our insurance to get a better coverage for us — our previous roof started leaking after a storm, and the initial insurance estimate covered only a small portion of the repair.\n\nWe’re very grateful to Jim for sharing his expertise and helping us make smart, informed decisions.\n\nThe Roofsmart team did an outstanding job replacing our roof — everything went smoothly and the results are top-notch. Our thanks go to:\n\nProject Manager: Omar\nProject Coordinator: Andrew\nCrew Lead: Jose\nBilling:Katie","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Ann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgmdeVK3ms_NNBEEFujWr_hiGtvVbD9CALGWc1SlIQg6YHpLc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My roof was damaged by a fallen branch during a wind storm. It did structural damage and we ended up needing to have the entire roof replaced. Jim with Roof Smart made it a seamless, stress-free experience. He communicated with insurance on our behalf and was always prompt with addressing our questions or concerns. Their team did a beautiful job from start to finish and we love our new roof. Highly recommend Roof Smart!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3t2rbuuR1VTRmHdOQYiGAxokE24gKA4kvp6SJNR4K6rQFPqxt6N9Fb1IAiAQxThQVsyRL4SbF5Ti0s62-ftH40FNA2CwRSwhKEOWon1hPe9TyKbuo_jyDCqkOGExNG2xRLGpk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VUnvEZSbP3W7gmIlHob15kxR329CJyhkCnBRDhBkYgjm7EXrnq96Qc17aAaKV3cmc6nqVeRDM_boxrl10YpghAg6Kl812o48TceFN3Oklauc34p-wNS9jyp0_A9qP-oDRos_oYw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0s-63glxCQMDF82plxj43QjzcbAZXAF_u0uwc_4ZxAR1a3tLfVZJLrB6Kis4y2B8rOo-89SfQ520q7TCptGM4L8fZvKMIR-d_cIzernoWAn2kjkrCMdeib-dy0B4ZDhm_RJsdh=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SQHlAmiY7Mk0vkeDitXBocdqsMvoFo-FS--kTxG2iHY1n8gYsXUxwLnqw4zyB60ClYwtZLsvdlhOlq55QUj2hUU_wVHcmGeIX5AL-aFHlh4YUse4kSjhUiWi9NSQQ79ksGyEzAg=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-24"},{"Name":"Sharon Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGQ9PDIde-6qkrZERcG9cPwCvNONdEmYCHKT8ZI2l5yeA2Kw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spoke with Chris Koenig who was so incredibly helpful.  He provided detailed information about roofing types, recommended maintenance, timeline for possible future repairs, and estimated costs.  Really appreciated his wealth of experience and honesty. We’ll be calling Roofsmart when the time comes!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandre Rezende Ferreira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf-yy6eCOUA_JjVU_Y8Irx6jwKFdTm2M0bPOukjmySp4ovTYAM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a small leak in my roof and they were great. I called, they came for an assessment, and gave me a fair estimate of the repairs needed. The repair team came a few days later. They were on time, worked fast, reliably, and they kept me updated during the whole process.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeffrey Thompson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIm0TiQTDhtq9rkzjOkmCJAdCjFCpgKaBA0KZMW2cnENr1THQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"RoofSmart replaced our roof in August. They did an outstanding job. For the estimate, Roof Smart used drones to take photos of the roof and inspected in the attic to show exactly the work they would do.  Estimators for other companies just walked around the house before writing an estimate. It was an easy decision to chose RoofSmart.\n\nThe RoofSmart crew arrived on time, was very professional and completed the roof in two days as promised with no surprises on the bill. The roof looks great and the crew did an exceptional job cleaning up. We have kids and pets and were worried about nails and other items left in yard. But the crew spent a large amount time meticulously inspecting and cleaning around the house.\n\nIf you want quality work done at a reasonable price, we highly recommend RoofSmart.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
