Ld=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEG5GlO_aflBpsROtfOhbTLQeaX8YWoWkN6tPpHLSnZeRL9U2cHAhyFacdxb3jzeKTuIRoi09_KcjBdx_o32z0105EHgXWrlE4xt1GLciUsGZtKV05wMq0kb_bbbMPe8_zLJMPz=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=7VpHvFFhxDlOrewCgUFekQ\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=78.19581\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"116135764232359172583","name":"Will's Roofing Company (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116135764232359172583"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"23825 35th Ave W","city":"Brier","postal_code":"98036","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jim Travis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6e1tiikiN3LX8QxEB6GdXU2cbEmdqy9koqNnX5MMXRjrB_CWClw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wilfredo and his team did such a fantastic job. When I was getting estimates, I could tell that he was the guy I wanted to work with; just so patient, knowledgeable, and obviously skilled. Wilfredo used the right materials, dealt with corrections to our venting and kitchen cooktop exhaust issues, made sure everything was done perfectly and the whole site was left spotlessly clean. They even fixed the water damaged siding near the roof and repainted it. I'm not an easy customer and I like to be involved all the decisions and understand all the details. Wilfredo was down for all of that and things went so great that I'm now going to have him and his wonderful team maintain the roof from now own so I can get the maximum value out of this investment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Koch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6XIOAs3p99UfoUWZH9PzR5WgF7im7X-EE80A2VA3xDtk7M7sjNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had our roof replaced by Wilfredo and his team this spring. He was very communicative, and his bid had a great detailed breakdown of what exactly they'd remove, replace and/or repair. It really stood out compared to the other bids we received and the price was competitive. They were professional and did a great job! We love the end result and will be recommending Will's Roofing Company to our family and friends in the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen McCallister","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJEAup7d3W7HkKxu1RmeGibrTT3kHahmn2Ni11obvcmxmqypeTXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed our roof replaced,  and we got three bids for our re-roofing, all within 15% of one another with similar materials.  We chose to work with Wilfredo as he was very thorough in his estimate and even pointed out a couple other issues that need to be taken care of (even though they were not within the scope of work he could do.)  The job started and finished very efficiently, and it all looks good and high quality.  Costs were exactly as bid.  A great experience for us.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvxj5VFpKQkS1vAEmh7FksGCvCuVk2ogz0Xmw8kl1g8ugVR-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wilfredo and his crew took on a big project for my home \u0026 detached garage which included the removal \u0026 disposal of the existing composition roofing, re-sheathing plywood over the existing shiplap roof decking, re-lining \u0026 repairing the existing built-in gutter system, installation of new downspouts, installation of new shingles \u0026 vents, replacement of rotting wood at the fascia \u0026 enclosed soffit, replacement of an existing leaky skylight and reinstalling flashing at 2 chimneys.  Wilfredo's close attention to detail and knowledge of how to best approach each facet of the project was outstanding.  Communication was never a worry as we were able to text or chat as needed at the end of each day to keep up with progress.  He also provided the only one, out of five, estimates that was very detailed to provide us a good, itemized understanding of what would be included in the scope of the project.  His cost was also very competitive with other roofers.  If you're looking for a roofing contractor where the owner of the company is going to be on-site every day making sure that the job is done right, look no further!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1A6HrSiGkb1Kn9zVCK4lledLcgFPE7OYqIzYYjaL1iXoVItDGizfuoXWIVq-qNegsiMF0fJO6-DWcYj6xm9uQRxdT9mSSjsWxxCN8xoRw433mDGrAM9VwpJnZAAEqW-N_NGLy6=k-no"],"When":"2021-4-28"},{"Name":"K S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgV6urgBgch0dOOngUSIHbYZauRtJHRyhtYMX55VIHyIDxnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did great work - very detail oriented, courteous and professional.  Price was reasonable.  I highly recommend Will’s.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wayne Schlappi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5h-_SJLsL0xLXPONGqabIEp2LEQ78HnzsJHI_Qu8Oa9cFFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Will’s Roofing did an amazing job. They were prompt and steady with their work schedule, communicated well, and their work quality was exceptional. They exceeded expectations on safety precautions, took great care to protect shrubs, and left the site cleaned up and organized at the end of each day. The final invoicing was more than fair. I would definitely recommend them for any roofing project.\n\nSent from my iPhone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Gunnell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJc-7GchWb38l05sgPUSCdtMqDnWsUC3pv_46wx6qsPLsNk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Will and his crew were fantastic. He was clearly busy but fit in my roof before the rainy season. It needed to be completely ripped off and redone. His crew was here for 3 days and were respectful and nice. He cleaned the property every day so we could use there yard free of debris in the evening. Will sent photo and video updates everyday and found a creative solution for my crumbling 100 year old chimney that was affordable and very attractive. The final invoice was very close to the original bid. I highly recommend Will!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jan BEdle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAs3xVrN-2zk_OjVGXqehS2QePkylibM_8uuJ6a-vSzxizOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An excellent experience!  Wilfredo is honest, very hard working, absolutely knows what he is doing (so knowledgeable!) - and very reasonable.  It was a difficult job on an older home and they went above and beyond!  I recommend them very highly.  I would definitely use them again!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
