the same day which was amazing. They did a quick fix for $250 and I thought I was good to go.\n\nTurns out the leak came back because there was a bigger issue with our old roof. They could've just kept doing patch jobs and charging me, but instead they were honest and said I needed a full replacement. Got me a quote that is comparable to other roofing company but they are the only one that are ready to start in the next two days. I don't want to wait further before the leak getting worse. That is the main reason I chose Royal Roofing.\n\nThe crew work HARD. I'm talking 7:30am to 6pm straight through. They had multiple people working and the quality was really good. Yuriy kept me updated on the progress.\n\nPayment was easy, no hassle. They cleaned up everything when they were done. They take care of the wet insulation inside my house from the leak and replaced it for free.\n\nThis is a newer small business and they're doing it right. If you need roofing work done, give Yuriy a call.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DmN_r1BJRvvTYJeArdEj-wamO0hYLsU9GAuwSUG2AIpPzacfjLeJ2HrjCln15WoXfUs8mah95RdHhTWBFwRAxKI5UV0cheyCcstuj1B4zThCprEvkkdTmLJ99CovsrY3Q4vh_o1XHeAxr=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-13"},{"Name":"Nicholas Riddell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNPSDeHLhJIjPaTql0kwDCEpAVsOpPWd4u3PHMmGyszhwWBBbl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Royal Roofing has been absolutely fantastic to work with. For the last few years, they’ve helped me extend the life of my roof by making timely, reliable repairs after several windstorms. Whenever I had missing shingles or leaking gutters, they showed up quickly, fixed the issues professionally, and kept everything in great shape.\nWhen it finally came time for a full roof replacement, Royal Roofing delivered above and beyond. The crew was efficient, respectful, and incredibly thorough—everything was cleaned up perfectly. The new asphalt shingles are high-quality, look amazing, and have completely transformed the appearance of my home.\nI couldn’t be happier with the craftsmanship, communication, and overall service. Highly recommend Royal Roofing to anyone looking for a trustworthy, skilled roofing company.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OJpqPLVK5pnaCu0do4BzOZVnrRHgl1bk43pLHjQRwL3z51HDSa_eywrMTLDI78k0TVnK5jVPd5Iff1tKK4dTk5bMaoy8rNr4yVIIQtJcEQcaB1Kjx0c0zrGyrsaMqbkd1vg78ox1JaUun=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-21"},{"Name":"John Lopez-Parada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2L7157CaIo6Htfey6TEbBg-fEvuzEPxJFKcm9MjvKrJSmPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Royal Roofing Service has been taking care of our older roof in Issaquah for the past couple of years—handling storm damage repairs and regular maintenance whenever we needed them. They’ve always been reliable, responsive, and fair.\n\nThis year we finally decided to replace the entire roof, and we’re so glad we chose Royal Roofing. Yuriy and the team gave us a great deal on high-quality 40-year performance shingles, walked us through all the options clearly, and answered every question we had. The communication throughout the whole process was exceptional—prompt responses, clear updates, and no surprises.\n\nThe crew was professional, respectful of our property, and did a beautiful job. Cleanup was thorough, and the new roof looks fantastic. We’re extremely happy with the final result and feel confident it will protect our home for decades.\n\nI highly recommend Royal Roofing Service. Yuriy and his team are the real deal—honest, skilled, and genuinely customer-focused. 5 stars all the way!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mellissa Burgy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI6FcRkmhY02nn-fkuUPdoIJ59B7UXx5JHP-ltpZ_jB1iMeK8_kQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m so glad we chose Royal Roofing Company for our seasonal roof cleaning and moss removal. They were fast at responding to 