yLJD9tXkXtFEU7QfaAfrUMl2DSPkCkq7UyVg_16RqzH0Ka2iZtbVXWiznUy05Ff_=w447-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=97VicxWVuEs6qscewesHmQ\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=53.2346\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"112277805477505359432","name":"Phillips Roof Repair (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112277805477505359432"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"1420 5th Ave suite 412","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Baby Daddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-JQbzRV4Ce2_nHQqgGS6hSDnWFRHwnlkGco9yC4g0xPfuQESx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their team was excellent! It was a quick turnaround from the time we called them to when they actually completed the repairs. The inspection was completely free and there was no need to pay for the estimate. Yuri, her team and our house were all treated with respect. Definitely recommend them for roofing and house repairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anmol Anmol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRkXMi1nQbVux8jGu6h-nNWB9XFukZrCa0RglNDXKzCjJIgg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very impressed by the professionalism and quality of service provided by this company. From beginning to end, the process was smooth and professional. Coby (my point of contact) was exceptional. Clear communication, prompt following-ups, and a true focus on customer satisfaction. The level of attention and service provided exceeded my expectations. Anyone looking for a reliable and top quality service should definitely consider this company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dhiraj Agivale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEybCPrMj4p-IpyFelztxTaDeY37aAnHWstjyLgSDHkZu62KI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alex recognized storm damage that others missed. New Roof managed everything from booking an inspection to contacting the insurance company. Never had to question what was going on. You wouldn't have known that this is a locally owned family business when it was time to replace the roof. In a 12 hour day, eight men stripped down my roof, replaced some of the plywood, laid all the material before shingles and then put on shingles. The men were very professional and told me that customer service is the priority. They have the right tools to do it in one day. Alex came back the next morning alone to do some final cleaning and fine work. All for the price of an insurance deductible. CALL THESE GIRLS!!! You won't regret it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Valentina Cinko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWzpXvprMeAiV1QqCFcuWcdxyFuyiZ3SOakV1xvXWYRaaa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team of roofers who worked on our house impressed me. They were very efficient and handled my large, steep roof in a professional manner. The rain started in the morning of the second day. But, because they had covered it the previous day, there was no way for water to get inside. You couldn't tell there had been any work done to my pool area after the job was finished. They cleared away all the debris that was there and even cleaned my gutters. They replaced some rotten fascia under the gutters neatly, without me asking. If you're unsure, it's best to ask. Although I was expecting to find nails everywhere on a roof this large, I only found ONE nail in the driveway. Wyatt Ashton and other guys ran blowers over the patio, driveway, roof, and yard. I have many plants and they took care to cover them so nothing would be damaged. All sprinkler heads had been checked before work started and none broke. Roof replacements cost a lot of money and nobody likes to spend it. I was able, however, to negotiate a great deal for my much needed new roof. It also helped me save on insurance and gave peace of mind before storm season. Negotiating is key. Also, choose your roof color very carefully. My old roof color was dark and ugly. But now, my neighbors as well as I love the new bright grey color. It made an enormous difference.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tunmise Oyeniyi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWl9XqmdVUgYzF6stMBz3JW58X3ziVgleti7SqPmK6qV7i8td_M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Francisco was very helpful with the insurance claims process. He was upfront about what needed to be fixed and what still looked good. The team was able to get everything done the same day. They also cleaned up nicely!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nurul Hidayah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi1f44iUq4HmjRQiSAjmcsBDeT8RcpuJfFbfy8r59pOOQYQRI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I requested an estimate. Tony came the same day, and the job was started four days later. The roof was stripped off and re-roofed the same day. The crew were professional and hard-working. The pricing was fantastic! I would highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Biswarup banerjee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIarcREymapmdeKL97I59tdaZFE2KW7N_BNQx9SFornPahkTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys are a great example of customer service for other roofing companies. This is a very professional company, from the sales representative to the project manger to the crews. William was a great person to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SamFury Gaming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNz_OMTjaiBqQSeIYWZ7Ksv0Ez5t6bS9oonoOW_5g0bwMnn7hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys did an excellent job. They completed my roof in just one day. Chris and Steve are super easy to work and their crew is awesome. If you are searching, I would definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
