ust honest advice.\n\nJuan and Mario showed up on time and worked super efficiently. In about three hours, they got everything done perfectly, roof and gutters cleaned, gutters fixed, everything spotless. I really appreciated their work ethic and the way they went above and beyond without me even asking. They cleaned the small shed roof that isn't connected to the house, adjusted other parts of the gutter that needed attention, and left the whole place so clean. Not just the debris from the roof and gutter, they even blew away the storm branches and leaves around the yard.\n\nHonestly, driving home and seeing how clean and fresh everything looked made me so happy. I highly recommend All Access Roofing \u0026 Gutters, and especially Juan, Mario, and Yolanda. If you want honest people who do excellent work, these are your guys.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Todd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwBD9aKRJEANfLlDXFJL-CWTZdaiaJV6c5UVGSgwF-J_QGPIo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our 34-year-old gutters were done, and we contacted All Access Roofing \u0026 Gutters for help.  Within hours, Pascal reached out and we set up a free estimate appt for 9/28.  The price was fair, he added a free moss roof treatment, and we booked a gutter/downspout replacement for 10/3.  On the day of, Juan and his crew arrived and went straight to work.  No lie, I watched in the beginning.  Impressive work ethic, great attention to detail and workmanship, I felt good about these guys.  By the late afternoon, it was done.  Their clean-up was excellent, Juan explained a few minor changes he made to help with water flow, and said to contact him for any issues.  On the morning of 10/4, it rained and you bet I was outside checking it all out.\n\nIt was all good, such a nice feeling.  Thanks to Pascal, Juan, his crew for doing a solid job.  I appreciate quality work, done well.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0MQ-aBXQDhO1o8CCgS0AC-g9O29TjJtSXAXPJ1reSHfQ6AjWE0dVl7d9zxaapmfC8I4GfMfmIMql98xiNI0xicXYBdsnQRpWWxeQMBRanUVKeLefR9Y1oYxNI4tqnVCIxal9pW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0D4nou7g0H3CTCYjsftnK33cH7iJBSt1so9vYBQc-v1AfSM3F8OFj43g9xWYKUFl-j2RoGB0LiK0NBX-UJmsd1ggW1ENH4Vp0tTIQG_cithORRc-a5jLBoZuFsghAsNa9mkdUb=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22CriRx5fm4tnsDeTOwZqb0xGYO4PCs_J716Y_pxk2-c0FBfqtUi4htG3kf6rnmLyjrt9syCt0IggLf4i3IWPF1V_gcATIppEFwyuVYFIH3O7wRF-VWnLiQEbl8tV2FDuGVeAuGg=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-4"},{"Name":"Paula Jurion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEMxILZaDTX5rxcHxEBKo90aF-4uGs60fQcoDqpJro4Pj3dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All Access Roofing \u0026 Gutter did a high quality job replacing our gutter and downspouts and cleaning our roof! We will use them again to replace our roof when needed. They were flexible with scheduling and came before a rainstorm, communicated well, and are priced reasonably.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Laha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwEioaDkIS24_pMAc-tk1hxxNVVYxcixxfKCaqCHV2IMWRg6ez=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Pascal and his crew at All Access Roofing and Gutters to clean our Ballard home's roof. He and his team did a fantastic job, even replacing a damaged vent flashing that they found during their time up on the roof. If I ever need roofing or gutter work done again, they will be the first people I call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ace King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDh1yxomaGMXYvNC_iJAint1lfk4G_DYtqj3pVxvd7hGXoV5Lo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found All Access Roofing and Gutters on Google.  When Pascal came out to give me an estimate, he was very personable and knowledgeable.  He explained to me what was wrong, what needed to be done, and what the cost was going to be, in such an honest manner, I hired him on the spot and cancelled the appointments with other companies.  The work his team did was great, too.  When my roof needs more work in the future, and it will, I will hire All Access Roofing and Gutters again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hans Olofsson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOreny80-HSU6oF4dyzRRlEIAMtdROrm2HmKifLoiC_t1TTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted All Access Roofing \u0026 Gutters based on favorable customer reviews and the fact they had experience with both roofs and gutters. Pascal was very helpful and informative, he ordered the supplies needed and had everything at the worksite on time. The crew worked long hard days, never complaining, they were  meticulous, very impressive. I was nervous at times but the crew leader had everything under control. I now have a beautiful new roof. I would highly recommend these guy's.\nAll Access Roofing \u0026 Gutters is first class, they also had the lowest bid.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chuping","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjGWLpfWem0LntAWwfnZ-QgZPCwTQBcH04zlCW8ifZMzwEFw639g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pascal and Juan - thank you so much for coming and fixing the house water damage problem with new gutter flashing replaced. Super professional and fast, I don't think you can find a better crew than these guys. Highly Recommended! I would come back for roof replacement next year.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"vdssszzvrshxh vddDavid Guo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYbsy1d7akXAH0Bx0DE4JNox2Xp0HOX6hrP90v7KS1ChJnhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All Access  team did a great job replacing my gutters and installing new gutter plus gutter guards. They are responsive, professional, attends to the detail, and are very customer focused. When the work was done, they went around the house and make sure all debris is cleaned up. Fantastic team and wonderful job! Highly recommend All Access for gutter replacement.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
