 industry. Thank you for being upfront and transparent. I will highly recommend him to my friend and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lorie Riser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwzpYLsbcQ6S-BEvdHpTi2vuemQ6xh1zz_qtW28g3ZHHB57Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Revolution Roofing did an outstanding job on our steep roof! Chris handled the challenging slope with skill and precision, installing a beautiful new roof using high-quality metal components. The craftsmanship and attention to detail were top-notch. Highly recommend their services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"alexander dayton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJr3aglr-togFxa4OhAQWQqQzoaPklIdBtKY62uTT7MoA1LHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience with Revolution Roofing. Chris went above and beyond in his attention to my roofing project. He was very kind and his pricing was more than fair. I received several bids from other companies and no one made me feel more comfortable than Chris. I would highly recommend giving them a chance!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Callie Maertz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXN56oKXtxQ-xwVsqPdiDxnJ8Jn_xuCX0GqioDffAqrS-X9hwQDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chris at revolution roofing is amazing. He helped me get my roof up to code quickly and he went soooo far above and beyond for me!! I will always recommend revolution roofing for their great customer service and genuinely kind and caring workmanship. One of the best examples of excellent customer service that I have ever experienced. Thank you revolution roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Boutwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzFyWkSS9D_1yAT6I1xyoRBYA3do8AMGs4Z0CJLoM-YQELEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a huge leak in my roof that was dumping water into my laundry room and these guys fixed it so fast! I thought it would take a lot longer. Super professional and personable as well. I definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
