"Saille White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJIK6v9GUg9SFiOFKCW9NEsjuUxr4eoBdr4oJ2f_y3wr5mpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Remik and his team were punctual, did a fantastic job, and he was completely honest and helpful about costs. They cleaned up everything well too! :) 100% would recommend. Very easy to work with and our roof looks great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jolene Cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPiavJgo1xpsVctovJ_t_gQh6OysN6oQeKRH6dwjcB8JLcyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Remik and his crew are amazing. I don’t often write reviews but Remik is an amazing person. We needed a new roof on our rental house and he kept us updated continually with emails and pictures. He went above and beyond and made sure I knew what was going on every step of the way. I felt completely part of the process even though I couldn’t be there all the time . They cleaned up beautifully. He is very knowledgeable and treats his customers very well. Their work is amazing and their prices are very reasonable. As I write this review I feel like I can’t even do them justice with my words. You would never regret using Alfa roofing for your roofing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Hartman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRdZgzIzY_KODwS__vAB7oJCfCSDkr5WO9hTp8ciiHNpAFoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Remik and his crew did an excellent job replacing our more than 20 year old leaky roof.  From estimate to completion they were on time and thorough. At each stage, when Remik discovered any problem he pointed out the issue and his proposed repair. The result was we now have a roof that will stand for a long time. He used top quality materials throughout and completed the job on time and on budget. I would not hesitate to recommend him and his crew for any roofing related task. Outstanding work, service and attitude!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Hake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzr7R1fNb0jFm3gC5GtAdkTjfjHensWaTFulVavoe2Q433yfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot speak highly enough of Remik and his team at Alfa Roofing!  The job was completed on time, on budget, and with utmost courtesy and professionalism.\nI would definitely recommend Alfa roofing for all of your roofing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian O'Mara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpDioDCpS8wzdmCLQZlTI-4tFYpQAPAvM3p9VFanjlcVrq-os1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used Remik at Alfa Roofing for a couple of jobs and this positive review is long overdue.\n\nHe is very clear in his deliverables and my expectations of the work were exceeded. Most recently, he came to perform some routine maintenance which should have only taken 1- 2 hours. He made some observations of some underlying issues where some rotted wood needed replacement. Remik and his crew patiently extracted the wood and replaced everything to good working order.\n\nAll in all, the job ended up taking 6 hours and Remik kept me updated with phone calls and pictures throughout the entire process. He also took it upon himself to do a thorough inspection of the roof and addressed additional items.\n\nRemik and his crew at Alfa Roofing are trust worthy individuals who I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Takuya Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTZDyeo_I2mNux5F7l8AUmphi_m2kq_QECm0M0fCzcb_8lIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience with Alfa Roofing and the business owner Remik was exceptional.  I live out in Boston and decided to hire Alfa Roofing/Remik, probably one of the best decisions I could've made!  He was really punctual and communicated with  me daily on the progress of the project including sending me 106 pictures throughout to show vs. tell me what was going on.  Couldn't have asked for a better individual to work with and I will be a huge net promoter of Alfa Roofing/Remik in the future endeavors.  Thank you for the great experience!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMe88fVqou0Qz1nSS3Zsnqbr9zfj48En7DmUHeQdRDFD0fUD_-XA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a property manager, managing over 100 properties in the greater Seattle area so I work with a lot of different vendors. Once trust has been established with my vendors, this relationship is invaluable.\n\nWhen I need a roof for one of the homes I manage, Remik and his team @ Alpha Roofing are my #1 go to roofer. He continuously gives my owners fair pricing, does excellent work and stands behind his work!\n\nA roof is a huge investment, It is important to me to have a vendor I can trust and know he's doing the best job for my homeowner's at a fair price. Remik makes my job a LOT easier! He has this property manager's seal of approval!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M ZML","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCJFQ5q9Tnu7gLoNdIihymU0DfGxbUBjBedMAevf0feFEMWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Remik is the best roofer I have ever met.   He is very honest and professional.   He is very responsive to my questions after the job is done.   I have strongly recommended him to my neighbors.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
