-Cfem32d=w545-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Roof shingle","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAH00p4LALnPUGFSIFFqgebxh1QjNYB_oJAwTrfezEjbyeMd4V9GGu4htCrA4JotrYCg4DS7E_nlK7NEjzySRhZ40cPsNdrguoviEUU7rLB-OoAliyck2zpfavhLYHZxgjJzmxPT=w403-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHqzWQfEHnVTWNmwjdbf69AqhY63xqVY82ZoNsPbalfm1gErgDHHqXPyujdvwPt00-EEu158KoQ0YTHUzuhEQMek_Wnum0dfXo3G2vcAZ3EIkPWBPqBUdAI1Higy-oOhiTnHGQ=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=KY2JdeuBSR2nMB2uTC2i5A\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=55.56426\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.johnmichaelroofing.com/john-michael-roofing-seattle-roofing-contractors-phone-206-201-1148/","source":"johnmichaelroofing.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"105786595228818216059","name":"John Michael Roofing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105786595228818216059"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Pike/Pine","street":"1400 Hubbell Pl","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Richard Watts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI95-3fLnE_-JxpOSs_AzOoxBsxZjoYXv6Dsyvgh544FXsw7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ira is a pro’s pro and a very decent human being in a business not always known for fostering either. The roof he proposed cost a bit more than the cheapest option, on the market, and he patiently explained the differences and likely long-term value of his option, but without ever being pushy. The work was done quickly, and the crew did a great job of cleaning the site. There were two callbacks, both of which related to gutters that had been previously installed by a different contractor, and Ira’s crew were on it immediately. No surprise, you get what you pay for…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eva Friedman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLC-L6ZHbpvre0sFRHAMT2fLWQDvwv0TUT2OEMrOgIjNBs84tC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ira and his team are true role models and professionals in their trade- definitely a cut abive the rest. You have to place your absolute trust in the roofers you hire - no other expensive purchase is fraut with such mystery as a roof and can make or break the longevity of your home and property.\nJohn Michael Roofing challenged the sterotype that roofers can be a tough/shady bunch.\nWithout high pressure sales tactics- just plain old fashioned great customer service and education they showed us the options that saved our property from certain  failure. They educated us on what was wrong with our roof and best practices for a long lasting, maintenance-free new metal roof.\nHe gave us real samples of the material to hold in my hands as he explained their installation techniques  - wow!\nHe gave us the technical and emotional support we needed to get through some of the most challenging times in our new home.\nThe job was done efficiently from beginning to end.\nBottomline:\nWe absolutely LOVE LOVE LOVE our new roof - this past Winter was the best one yet in our home and we whole heartedly recommended John Michael Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sara Thompson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3YmlLI3Rf8YTDpJMxeiQY-RxeOwFEiV-7veKBBHcWUbBgOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We selected John Michael Roofing after reading several reviews and collecting bids.\nThe metal roof John Michael's team installed looks great and made huge energy improvements in our house.\nThe workers were timely and respectful of our home during the job.  We also had them install color matched gutters, which are great quality and were expertly installed as well.  The best roofing company we've ever used!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Nichols","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOYFNJzr0W0DO3R-Bx1Ng6GzGf6evdYK_sB6aoUQdS-9d60g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just bought a house and knew that the gutters and roof needed some work. My gutters were 30 years old and falling off the house, my chimney was rotting away, the gas heater exhaust had rusted apart, and some unknown animal had chewed several holes in the siding under the roof line. John and his crew made all of these problems go away quickly and for a very reasonable price.\n\nI must have had six roofing contractors come out to my house to give me estimates, and John was the only one willing to take care of my entire roof and it's problems in a high quality and reasonably priced way. He takes pride in his work and treats your roof like it's his own. I can't recommend him highly enough for any roofing job, large or small.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aron Thompson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBX92xOkKDODKPgVVNE-ypyIB9xhm76Xo6gDWqwivwWREEdiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like a lot of homeowners, I'm careful and picky about who I hire to work on my home.  When it came time to have my house re-roofed, I did a lot of research and due diligence.  I decided to go with John Michael Roofing after meeting and consulting with him - in fact, since I also needed to update my rain gutters, and he could coordinate this too, I had him do both roof and gutters because I developed a lot of confidence in him.  The results completely validated that confidence:  I have the best roof and gutters I could ever hope for at a very fair price.  Believe me, if you're considering home improvements of this kind, you need to meet with John Michael Roofing. - Aron","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Salvata","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMblk8jYCV3nbQFdWUxMmoLjde59oDr17y_F-MvltUmdUdPAwt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John put a roof on our home about 8 years ago and did a terrific job. We have a 1926 Tudor with a steep roof that had cedar shingles on it. John and his crew were very professional. They replaced it with a composition roof that looks great! Highly recommend John Michael’s 𝐑𝐨𝐨𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐠.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paige Hanley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5IImus72dpMit1RFDAxnegvXDppmacwUzqAcieCFdjX7nBAvEQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent work from a solid team - love our new roof! We had been talking about getting a new roof so we had 3 companies come out to bid it. We knew instantly we like John Michael the best and were thrilled when he was also the most affordable. He and his team were extremely professional and the work was exactly what we'd hoped for. They even came out before the scheduled start when we sprung a leak so they could patch it. We also had them install new skylights as well as gutters. Highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rusty Welch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1tT71fYyCe2MYxjrsCbDg_Xz_5ckVSuDNMFDphJNXZR2g5LI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have a 6-year-old house that had a (flat) torch-down roof. It was poorly done, and we had several leaks. I had 4 different contractors out to bid the job, and after talking with all of them and looking at reviews, we decided to go with JMR. John was very patient as we spent over a year trying to get permits and costs for putting in a roof-top deck, only to find out that the costs of re-enforcing the roof, permits, and compliance ended up being way over our budget. We finally decided on doing a PVC roof with a hatch for access, and within a month of making that decision we now have a great new roof. John was fantastic - understanding, quick to respond, and willing to work with us throughout the whole process. The final cost was very reasonable, and the quality of work is true to his ratings. There are a lot of roofing companies / contractors out there - it pays to find one that takes pride in their work and is willing to work with their customers. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
