s://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102708089946256709365"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Industrial","street":"14102 NE 189th St","city":"Woodinville","postal_code":"98072","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Donald Hatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-XbYeZpB3RKCAlu8gaMDKLzcTnDEx-brcRruP2nEyMrMARA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough positives about this company. Starting with the free estimate through the finished work, they were friendly, professional and excellent craftsmen. They showed up when promised, cleaned up after and did a great job! I had them clean and treat the roof for moss and a year later it still looks good. We have a willow tree with long thin leaves that get everywhere.  Their gutter guards are the perfect solution. No more scary ladders on the second floor roof!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tC-6Nbz7OxIeS1_DTpZ-1PMe8bv5N3Qp2lICaxyHRdKGEW7jYYUMZB1k43kbagGXLhbr2mbB5mUpTz46ta_xhUGs05hYMuecxTknAGx41X8qJaq_it_P0faGPV1lw1CNpewQl_btzcmk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33pr0I2m7vuopfra8Ut_vvoJfhePk3Md9lMF7BXHtf2CxcXmUHqRnW-68eIrBhJhBg33xu3o6Bj0m3pTVCqeaabThwESQ2sn2UmOVZACQNXxX-o4fx2ubk93NId2z00g0-gzbV-g6ri00u=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-25"},{"Name":"Lori Hittle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkooTZG1ktS9ywhw5pvS15VZEjMY77hUjnSiPOBmcp3StoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High Point Gutter was a pleasure to work with. The estimator and crew were professional, great communicators, and their knowledge really showed. When questions came up about the best approach for gutters on our house, they made informed and helpful suggestions about how to lay out our gutters. They constantly kept in touch on the project day, and were great to work with. I would definitely use this company again and I know you can feel confident about working with them on your next project.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3JQ3w8229kfCyN0tljVLB1NYHUSFwND2Eh3G2fSrsv0flgsPwvLQcVoBdpmBBsyaM5vhYkKmsyWeMC7GOeQEf4EP7BIa_2Ix0KVhYpcaU2xkuLijSyKxKyeImeFDRM7YqoDe_M2YdSIocZ=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-20"},{"Name":"Marcia Binney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBXU79eYm4CHp30-IDOMUE8PO0p7nnABucIzGlUmo12Bw8Hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend High Point Gutter.   Everyone I interacted with was helpful, skilled and approachable, including the person who answered the phone and set up the estimate appointment,  the estimator and the crew who did the job.  A tree had fallen and damaged our gutters, and I honestly didn’t know how much work would be needed.  Everyone at High Point gave me honest, clear answers and no one tried to “oversell” the job.  The work was done on time, quickly and professionally.  Our property was left immaculate.  I will definitely be calling High Point Gutters for future gutter maintenance.   Great job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Matorin LePard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6twTsYDggbhDXueBGa5AKTWYa2ZEexV4snMDT2M9Ox7oBdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent company that goes the extra mile!  Unlike typical gutter contractors out there, they actually have the know how to properly install copper gutters and welded all the joints (never caulk!)  The finished gutters look stunning!  When I had my house painted, for a nominal fee they offered to remove, store and then reinstall the downspouts.  Their crew was so helpful, careful to secure all the unsightly internet and security wires behind the gutters and when on their high ladders, they even helped to  touch up some paint and installed a copper exhaust vent.  I highly recommend this company.  You will get honest, skilled service and pride in their work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2RmVywi8XU-0fkgH6xRXPUSN5nNeL9t5UmToJIQRC2xILIAGz9weZw8fnl63gQrMOxjx81US-0AfvPhqj-MeAHDhRPgwmPJoN5hzvh_GWOoc9df869FpeZe7oAK9lBNmTwGHJtgQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-3"},{"Name":"Mark Perry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFAD0XSSyBBg6PHC6h2MN9nOvAClKaufO-yGBzxdYBBrv--R7b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team did a high-quality installation of our new gutters. Very thoughtful crew and very professional service oriented working style. Can't say enough goodness regarding the installation team of Gwen and Will. Overall the organization is very professional and just top notch. I highly recommend High Point Gutter.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0TgVZMXAKqBWu64X4DkScws4fMtNoWFATtyRdaUXdh_DlMFni26odt8ypXz3Z28J-ikO4u4JAtqxf3p4-pyJ9p6AQldF8LlS6tcVk_iNkQTQZ573LaM-Zyyemt3i4twYwZW3Aj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tp3PyNPXcvwOonYMCs4aAuly06MGvLjAFvggnk038_5dp_v2KAqK7bcqduayRd-tckLBk1MFnJ6p7q1UMO6365VgPR57-dON0pmuH5ZpkPb0cm6HIYmqxFSILAJ_88UATKOOQig=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Ilq2CglZSJtDJ7qTHkElFbcAjdOgjGWuvU4SuVdoijyKVQRl1yZaxldHkofm35ObdI2-7u7JlhJ-jc3dscgxixj5nKrYcsTCUKDaUyCo5r1vg0StcQhp51QFyxA4BB4TFN3Y0=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Matt Warhol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNNh8rOgGeBxIGdv9AteSWfabUJrNSm380EPrO0VZ-0Pf-7HJKYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible. They postponed my gutter and downspout cleaning by a week. Didn't finish the work. Had to come out a second time to finish. Didn't provide proof of work in follow up emails. Half of the pictures they sent me providing 'proof' weren't of my house. With so many other options, I'll never be using High Point Gutters again. It's been a month now and I'm still dealing with their mess.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Delorey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp7nPO1u0s_lk4qMvN5MKDYJtW1rZex5vWD0cyv5_Otki-HDHJUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High Point Gutters did excellent work at my home replacing our 20 year old gutters with beautiful new ones. I compared several bids. High Point struck the right balance between cost, quality, service, and availability. They got us on the schedule quickly, and finished the work on schedule. They had several upgrade options their competitors did not, but they were never pushy in their sales approach.\n\nThe biggest differentiator for me, though, was the post-installation service. Our gutters were replaced in July when we get very little rain. Once the rains started in October, I noticed that there was a persistent pinging drip right outside our kitchen window that began to be quite bothersome as the precipitation picked up. I reached out to High Point, and Kenny came right out to check and correct the problem. This level of attention after an installation, even several months later, is exceptional in my experience. I'm glad I went with High Point!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandt Westing","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhkVDkreYeUO9a-FcNQXfxFMHp6aqBnOE4g21R5M6I3JVbQp1r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This team did a fantastic job on new gutters on my home after I had the home re-roofed. They were detail oriented and made sure everything fit correctly and was sloped correct for proper drainage at the roof edge. It looks great and after some rain I now have working gutters again. No leaks! My home had difficult access and required much of the install to happen from the roof - great job team!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1m7I7lcptQuhjkaki6MUM_4l80