mages":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mae Wynne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhmVqs_Ou2jrloclB5a0rEGd6J57tPBOxM2A7iIRGQObuOg9fc2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Rob and Crown roofing. He was referred to me by a friend whose roof he replaced last summer. The website was  very informative and when Rob came to assess my roof for an estimate he was personable, knowledgeable and patiently answered my questions. He was also very responsive to my texts. My roof was installed a couple of weeks earlier than I anticipated and Rob kept me updated with links to the pictures taken  each day.  The price was what I expected. My roof was 30 years old and  needed 10 new boards so the original estimate was a little bit higher but that was not unexpected. I can't comment on the crew as I was out of town when the work was done but I have been completely satisfied with the whole process.Thanks Rob!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Dinsmore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBBYoLc7hg--CaJvXUGpZq0fTYctP6dOcT_FyyRwgbaK9VSxEJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Crown Roofing did an amazing job repairing our roof after a large fir branch punctured a hole in our flat roof. We had our entire roof redone when we bought our house in 2018 and the repair was very affordable! We also had a rain chain installed near the front entrance, and they did a beautiful job. Crown Roofing was the most affordable and didn't try to upsell me like many other roofers after the storms that came through Washington this winter. I recommend using Rob and his team!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn16Lg2EsnN7GdD20BsrTBYI9LWhrKnBfZfM7QPXIOmI1gVlUqbLKvtvOnx53WR_ZWLkioS_jBqQm7l7RaXpDMwPwEXWS2wplnZoE_yMoS2F6tmnDr7hI_GJwT9aMiO_XEXvyTTJCw=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-23"},{"Name":"h p","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWowxwzyYpjNfcjQFhphwo9hl7VBtCirTEUenIsP2TD7FS4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 stars. Rob at Crown Roofing provides great service and walks you through the process. All questions were answered and he was always reachable. The roofers were friendly and professional. Very knowledgeable, very experienced and did a great job at a fair price. Do you want it done right or take a chance and try to do it cheap?  Trust me, get it done right on a 30, 40, 50 year roof. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"loisjean broadway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8AHfAk4pvThzkvIp11JWGGE0GO9BZ4yJvqP3wpobJSd65aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Crown team was responsive and attentive.  Making several visits to assess problem prior to scheduling roof replacement.  They were responsive, thorough and efficient.  Highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Grant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcg_BIgX9f6qiSw71pHfdTm3pvCk7-nGKAlo8kxPBjjOrkdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A pleasure working with Rob and his crew to replace my roof.  They were professional, reliable, and flexible on timing.  Rob patiently and promptly answered all of my questions.  A big investment where you want to be confident in who you are working with.  Happy to support a local contractor.  A++","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Cox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCoNFbLToKRDtJdGlSDDO9-08rVuzJ7erHW_LfYRht55dGTQY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a general contractor, it’s hard to find good, reliable teams. I recently hired Crown Roofing to replace an old torch-down low-slope roof on one of my customer’s homes. At first, I was skeptical since Robert’s bid was lower than the other three I received. But after working with him, I can confidently say he’s a solid, straightforward guy who doesn’t try to upsell unnecessary work.\n\nHis crew was skilled, and their workmanship was definitely above average. They paid close attention to detail and took real care in their work. If you need a new roof, Robert is your guy. Thank you, Crown Roofing, for a job well done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse Colangelo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVk3zeeM3Q5_zDTGjXHdSLaegVBPyqFRI-0s9GQDjBhbpmbxvwyjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rob and his team responded to a need within an hour, and arranged and executed on service the same day. One of the most impressive engagements I've ever had with a contractor of any sort.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
