r installation of my original roof. Imagine my surprise, though there was no way to determine that this would happen.  Vance was on it immediately. Maximus contacted me to explain in further detail what had transpired and worked the costs to make it a bit more palatable.\nAdrian worked tirelessly to ensure that the crew protect the flower beds by covering them with tarps, as well as, keeping the crew safe.\nThe crew were friendly, polite and worked extremely hard to complete the project on time.\nWith such a costly expenditure, I felt completely confident knowing that they were not cutting corners and took incredible pride in their workman ship!! I highly recommend Four Seasons Roofing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ga_XtJ9t4VgOrBNETq0QYivht0RGxvCoYbfgcvNWI7OjbxyCQbk-mmRlQmYgyXW9jKzIL1mrvWTFUr8a1zfBtgeCuy-DSGH4gc5f0hNfNtFWm8haACDNwXA-x0WNnGJguH90QI4lX06w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2LjAA8QhFnNsUh334lFP_iD3eIXBSRia7whJqGn02vjSz9WAsHvJ5ZqZnY2ExoByRx2RMllrHSTdhOZudfbtsSgYVDFMT2vxkXTAPIuux8bIAm3bRe7_UhPqB98x_jKiIoXZ--aV77kdZT=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1C2N9Xum33sLr4n92zY47mTTERI-9p7GLgglNO6eY2-OS2ExDTwY2e2Q3wHvUR2hpOHgOOztz1eTSXVcPurPQVM4jPe2Rjcws0ubHnd2i-WSRukFRNf55Gg58-baqUh_vk-Jobx30PJi_V=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1bHBocre06cgugHEzyeIv_3OHaStILaphTdTT6zocOxeek1tpUpUJKUsNVnZrOVcVZbhGH_vs_xUAa0Lz-ANIjHxUY5t8wel708YOFQaZIb87W0W677sD6XVoQmjC7pTJyPym3d4fTGYw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn01o_BbjygnTXqyxinbzXvSLlr0Y91Hd2SSQvt6pZl-jHLXbHtsLkPCRiKB28imc45NcWPZYnQclk20vSTipRpKxppx0DLQXobT7BhV2CKQcH_SrBTuRN_Bf_f103QViTGJgWGjX6NtCxLp=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3diadScN3tHjrGJABnK77J6bXpCWWaFJZe755c-tJ_nWIyoY1QTqFj8ROLtLRlSjxUlcEZzLEZoWWJSOHJbJV40lPpz-OJFh6dVtjHuhKxPpbeBgSSJ1HyXBPFh2Rae5qZ4yCzihN1Iao=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-unxtUTob5srnDhsQ5bHrYoc3c8l0ee6oFoqVP8Egu38XAH2IQ0