k1u9G3fTGFoBUM6VQPKb8UdUjreBlNoy_aKG4jflhcLXLHLrT=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-26"},{"Name":"David K. Farkas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZL8hW3-Nl4EGmTKTFsq5OjR5bPpqGFXMtU9mVcfaQwAhI0sVJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Compton Builder (John Stacey) completed an extensive remodel of our home--roof, siding, driveway, interior paint, and more. Great work. He has an excellent crew. The job went very quickly (most of it done in 3 weeks). To keep the project moving along, John asks customers to make quick decisions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sylvia Callies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUj7jjtaVWN3WggCOmRNIdyX19Cfqamdv-RWcnSukb0ySx5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so impressed with the team at Compton Builders. I own several investment properties in Washington state. Their work is top notch, John, the owner is a man of honesty and integrity. Their work is always on time and on budget. I highly recommend Compton Builders.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"harry bazerz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsyf9f4l8knNjgrfStWMyVMz5H4QUwZWP--GcwhjY-EmZJ_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Compton Builders just finished our bathroom remodel, and driveway. What a job this Seattle construction company has delivered. I cannot be happier. They were punctual, communicated effectively, and provided options for some hiccups that came along the way.  The best part is that we paid exactly what they quoted us, and no last-minute surprises!\n\nI totally recommend Compton Builders to any home owner looking for quality and is budget conscious!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adolf Lowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNExtgzmvkMfID4aJyAO_dexLiPuEOa0ATGp9Om1mmiIPsFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My driveway and sidewalks were a mess, and I lived with them for years. A friend recommended Compton Builders, and they gave me a very fair estimate. My response was let's do this! What a transformation, I'm happy with the results! The crew did an outstanding job in some rather rough weather, and everything was completed and cleaned up within a week.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGu9Zv1FY39Zt9pnA_0BwWHpjHDXPEKFpt0ha-jWkiazaLWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Compton Builders are great! My house is almost 100 years old, and needed a LOT of work. Sections of siding damaged and rotting. Sagging boards under eaves. Crumbling patches in basement walls. Time for a new roof. Time to paint the house. John looked over the house, came up with an estimate, worked with me on what I could afford. (Had to stop his enthusiasm to fix EVERY problem in my house.) Compton was very understanding when I had a delay getting money out of investments to pay them.\nThey did great work! Looks so good now, getting compliments from neighbors. Compton's employees were efficient and skillful. Took pride in their work. Friendly. Really cared that I was satisfied the job was done right and was what I wanted. In this COVID time, they were careful to maintain social distance from me, and wore masks when working inside the house.\nTwo small negatives: I had to do more cleanup afterward than I expected. Raking bits of old siding and shingles out of the lawn, discarding empty paint cans. And then there were problems with communication. The office never called to say if or when people were coming over to work. Did a lot of sitting and waiting when I thought people were coming; couple times answered the door in pajamas when I didn't expect people. (The workers almost always at the end of the day told me if they were coming back the next day.) I told Compton about these issues, and they promise improvement.\nI may get more work done in a year or two. I would definitely call Compton Builders again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marie Andersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9ZdtLOcXkOieJEuy1qqqBMKF_yYoqaflq7hUIaECGPLUDvg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our new deck is built by the excellent crew from Compton Builders.  We are so impressed by their hard work,  professionalism,  and knowledge.  The crew is always on time,  friendly and  does great work.   We are very happy indeed.  It has been a pleasure working with John Stacey and crew.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ganoi Qaib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXV29lDo_ENcY6jNuxjs4wWbP7NvPqnroFP3oXgWG-EmjMXApA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Remove old roof and install whole new roof. Their crews are the best. On Sat. March 27th 2021, the came with five guys, and they don’t mess around, so professional, and clean up all around my house after job was done. I am very happy with the new roof (I choose Certainteed, and loved it)\nI wish they let me post pics of my new roof.\nThank you Compton builder for an outstanding job. I would recommended to my family and friends. I am very happy 👌\nDon P\nWest Seattle.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
