 us scheduled quickly \u0026 Efren was out to take care of everything that we needed... All timely, professional and affordable. Efren also provided us with pictures of the finished work for the home inspection.\nWe highly recommend Unique Roofing!\n\nThank you so much for your thorough, professional services.\n\nKevin and Karen Richardson\nMonroe, WA","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erica Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK62gjJYePfoJ917OP-dKtLggOLfuL3R0RdR7ra5I_3hdp98w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so happy I ended up going with Efren! After having a couple of companies completely miss our scheduled meetings and not even reaching out to reschedule I was feeling pretty negative about the whole situation. Not only did he replace my roof in less time than expected he showed up early every day for work and was just so pleasant to work with. And the job was done beautifully!! I will always refer my friends and family to Unique roofing. Thank goodness I found you guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Paradis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnUd3co_4rz58Cm7D_Nb3bvpGQzucbvKI71gbUn4f5_L-mmYc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were so nice and professional! We had to have our roof re-graded and a lot of repairs. He was so amazing and talked us through our options and tried to give us the most cost efficient options! They were great the whole project was done quickly and I’m so happy with our roof! It’s gorgeous. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"coshin lepe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs4O_L-XOSSJr9LcQeVdgi5xHAC089lshxcLZyYgxWS1ON3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called for an estimate, friendly professional service. Arrived on time, Efren was very detailed and professional about my roof concerns. The work that was done turned out great. Very pleased with the service and price for what was done. I would recommend this company to my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marsha Keyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDaLjnp2xg8iM94lf7FBGuLiHlLqCZViIzlbIjCQpDDf33_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have had a great experience with Unique Roofing on two complex jobs. They have shown skill \u0026 knowledge of all facets of roofing, carpentry, painting. Very reliable and hard working.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Margarita Villaseñor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqJeqlRGv1IYCHfR64ufX6cmkAMZ9qH09oX0Zix6anjB0k_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mrs. Yulie over the phone was very polite and informative to schedule in our estimate, Efren came when expected, professional costumer service. Excellent work that was done on my new roof, recomend Unique Roofing to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daphne C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyOCcGxs05VYtuf0vUmVbEb45xuq-_8JG4DTfB4ecZFbF7Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Experienced same weird issue as other reviewers, I got ghosted by them. Efren came over and seemed very confident on issues. then he said \"I will send you the quote today or next business day, and we will start the work next week.\" then they disappeared.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
