ing and talented. Our roof looks fabulous!  A+++++\nThanks so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse Lunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2l0J_QokBGCAM5BzVAQlohy_7kLuno-FrstILqpk46zncO0rk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent job installing my garage roof. Quick to come out for the estimate and complete the job. Showed up as scheduled and cleaned up.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse Morton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4ifogR0OAxvrR0iEcNlSto2jmFldeVPTOS81qDRszG5Tjug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Drivers are aggressive and driving at high speeds and irratic all over highway while things fly out of the back of his truck. Black Ford f150","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joyce Ailinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTKW2pMQCsqnolx3BoO8v9bvUh3FGWS2MMDJxkHx7M29U2dHQM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service. The guys were great, cleaned up when done. Very happy and highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"c adolfine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmABms83IceokzLVuLiTqNZRAFzzogH6sygjWTzL8d6ex8uw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent workmanship","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
