"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=B7nsNGbdz6dFHLAOgk46tA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=10.956093\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"111504648727853314493","name":"Speedy Roofing Inc (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111504648727853314493"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"15731 2nd Pl W","city":"Lynnwood","postal_code":"98087","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Han Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyTp14cVjH83ltxjCdVxghouenqUCtrSedlAtd-eYroyXvhcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As homeowners with no background in construction, we needed professional help to understand why there were water stains in our attic. We had several highly rated roofing companies come out to inspect, and while each inspector gave us a different explanation, they all reached the same conclusion: we needed to replace the entire roof. The problem was—their stories didn’t match.\nThrough a recommendation from a friend in the construction industry, we found Don. After inspecting our roof, he was very direct and honest with us. He told us we did not need a full roof replacement, and that the real issue was the bathroom exhaust fan ducting, which needed to be rerouted.\nAbout a month later, two workers came and completed the work carefully and thoroughly. We are truly grateful for Don’s honesty and professionalism.\nThe construction industry often feels full of companies focused on making money—or making as much money as possible. As consumers, we really appreciate companies like Speedy Roof that are willing to tell the truth, do the right work, and earn an honest living while providing high-quality service. We hope more people get to see and choose companies like this.\nOne practical note: the phone number listed on Google never seems to go through. We recommend calling the office number listed on their official website, or calling Don directly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin Pfeffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC5kZHQXjmjYuikaVhnoWKUzY523wPne5qz1558ULPzYocnFdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Don and his team was a great experience. His team was professional, and they exceeded our expectations before, during, and after the completion of the project.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQ-dAxkx4AZlsTcVBcpalAevYN68RGbTcvCDDGKxHEDY-aIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got three quotes on a new roof. One was from a top rated company that sent out two people to tag-team me with high pressure. Watching them come up with their bid told me that they didn’t know what they were doing. They were also the highest bidders. (I was in construction for years, so I know what to look for.)\n\nDon Berry came by, measured us up and I knew immediately that he knew the business, and was not trying to get rich off of us, either.\nHis crew came promptly at 8:00 am, and it was like a well-oiled machine.\nThey had the old roof off, replaced three pieces of plywood, put the barrier down, new rims all around, and had the new roof down and everything cleaned up (several times) by 2:00 pm! It looks good and we haven’t had any leaks.\nIt was a really nice job.\nDon also noticed a couple of pieces of metal roofing needing to be replaced on my barn, and he came by a few days later and replaced them for me for FREE!!!\nWhat an awesome company/man!\nIf you need a new roof, you will not be disappointed with Speedy Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lando Calrissian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlgaTHvGEFoRsCGJUe_wPzCmNBi4OROc2T8fEguzW30EHg4MNG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did my roofing, unfortunately the boots get weird off so soon. so, we contacted the  Don Berry, he came rapidly and fixed it very fast and put new boots and also give the warranty of roofs as well if anything happened in this time frame they will taking care of. Thanks DON, appreciate it. Whenever, I will need near future any kind of roof problem, I know whom to contact. Also, I will highly recommend this company to others, specially Don is our guy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Toni Semanskee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV1p2Z-yc0WfSECcpBPqbSZS1aw0gs0Kq6F2dv1DCAummNESw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David did the initial inspection and quoted us a very reasonable price for a new roof. He sent his team led by Don and they did a fantastic job. They arrived on time, cleaned up the mess, and were very professional. The new roof looks amazing. The installation was top notch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Sykes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCMDQhq17v5K8MEq7P5_VEz-RZli6paswa2tEgjzWFX7R7DQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We used Speedy Roofing to re-roof my parents’ home prior to listing it for sale. We found Don to be extremely knowledgeable and his estimate was the best of the 3 we received. He always responded with thorough answers to my questions. The job was completed in a timely and professional manner.  I would use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin McLaughlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLdLJCds-DJbXVUXb32oZrUn2d1L-ifK8zu4P7aJzrs_62mC08=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I saw one of their drivers going about 83mph on I-5 in an old beat up van. He was just a few feet behind the car in front of him and he gas old steering and an old brake system.We don’t need drivers like this on the roads. Don’t hire these guys. Keep this jerk at home. License plate number c32671y","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Macandog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa7m3l9nkYzw9oOw_BaEkPS9cp66S1GExDZaItljuAvOSO10Qa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don, Monica, and team have been a pleasure to work with. Fast and efficient, but did not sacrifice on quality. Our new TPO flat roof replaced an old and leaking Torch Down flat roof. We also had our Fascia replaced along with the new roof. All the previous down spouts, gutters, and any wires were put back after a successful install. I would highly recommend Speedy Roofing to all my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
