rts, came in with a competitive and transparent bid, reused as much material as possible and then executed the work beautifully. Look at all that perfect detailing in all it's waterproofed glory!\nOur home looks even better than when it was first built. Even the clean up was pristine - it's been 3 months and I've only found one screw (there were thousands in our siding)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3c1Jivz9nUwsrvyUAZvNQZ5h0w9YsLgf9SQNldZY1G-fiYyo6-LXN82P8C-FncMzuTMR9phGR-Zo-nknMyBYruliw6FQuxmiaiYY47kocTwcyIu6UD9kiHxrFMUwWlBABcXVpfvAUZbaM9=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn05JH_7wVyUE-3XOe41SRONTGD2bxq08_f7QL3i8hrppaeNxZdOYmBlx7trLFUdcIAmTdimU4Fxo51dZp5BabkpxA4yxyxPcdcJVR_7UECIZhnV-Kjbryw8CQ7nSzVnorTX1ERt8hhdkME=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wCKrtJo3vgiFZp9js4E-O8h7RhOvgRR9iU6WjQE5ndVi72UJAkN9tKQ3f4JmksEgVZRaI8Z9buSvjdaJwGFMvTt4vigHNfG6TVGDhMTcYla4yopLp5khJKmgFkpawkC5sF2mnVfr-NamA=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-15"},{"Name":"Faye Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZqOxAQxqMGmcBO0Evo9ZP0wUy-P2D51N7T2leha0RfpT8Voft=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Side Pro, thanks to Alex, the estimator. He was friendly and listens well, and was quick to address my concerns throughout the project.  His professionalism and the competetive rate , and the strong reputation of the company convinced me to go with this company after 4 other bids. Sidepro replaced 4 sides of my house with cedar planks and repaired several fascia boards that has worn out over the years. They found rot in the plywood behind the cedar planks  and the additional rate to repair were reasonable.\nThe two crew members that did the work were Jose and Federico. Jose was the main guy, highly skillful, very strong and friendly. They came on time, worked hard, always pleasant. Thank you Sidepro for having such an excellent crew and staff to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Han Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyTp14cVjH83ltxjCdVxghouenqUCtrSedlAtd-eYroyXvhcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For homeowners without professional construction knowledge, the industry feels confusing, with different companies giving different explanations and costs for the same issue.\n\nWhat we appreciated most about Side Pro was their honesty and professionalism. Alex, DJ, and Jack shared their opinions directly and transparently, which we respect.\n\nWhen a small issue came up during the project, their manager Sam took the time to explain it clearly, making us feel that Side Pro cares about its customers. The crew, Jman and his coworker (sorry I’m not sure how to spell his name), were detail-oriented and did careful, quality work.\n\nWe hope more people can find a professional company like Side Pro.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuXP4FX4oxTPnB2xD0el7uHeughACPO4DmzoikjA7nOJHgjg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our Cottage in Queen Anne (Seattle) was transformed by Side-Pro Exteriors!  Including removal of asbestos and lead paint siding, install of painted hardiboard siding and trim.  Ryan and his team were professionals, met budget and timelilne and exceeded expectations on quality!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1TSWC_BkQP2SnqkxWAKNQoa4PXdXa15Bz_I5OCej_zXNnxiKDe74vmRX_bsl7jTZsDnWstzeQnrJW19Ik9I1H2ljAwFhVEYyPfzUvWp05v8P3ZJkeG4ilNZFj7AmZh_-70iPnCa39J6wZD=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1xnsSPZjEQ6ZsYFdO1me0XOM4Ja-65sE2jIgsEyc1D0I5xfftzJR2d3TW2LtpcyX9iB6MRdctmoqsFW8CB_HhOH8YskS2ePdVfyOafj8GP6lOJzsG0Uq5UlBAAYBjDp0IwYk_hXFIUvkCn=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-3"},{"Name":"Daniel C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCyUVDbpoviDtQ4JqNJtLx65RwytCxE7_lNNmVWMj-nFefRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Side-Pros by their competitor (Northern Pacific Exteriors) for siding repair on a home in a HOA. As most people know it can be restricted on what can be done depending on the HOA bylaws and covenant. Instead of spending $25-30K in doing a full backside replacement of the home, which would go through lengthy reviews. And I needed it done before fall weather and rains began. I worked with DJ on an estimate and Faith to coordinate repairs on the +20 year old home. They were able to source the rare siding and make repairs for a fraction of the price. Highly recommended!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Mielenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXHPlZZRT6jKQBRF3G9VkbeFjSBhnVSdf70Id-MyUSGhB2YB5ogw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a fantastic company. On our house they did siding, roof, paint, installed replacement windows and gutters. Every crew was as professional as anything I've seen in the construction business, and they all had good people skills. They performed every phase of work timely, and with low impact on our lives; good scheduling.  It seemed their primary goal was quality.  They had contracts for all work performed, and communicated changes. The billing process was fair with adjustments both up and down, and excellent documentation.\nAll of this reflects good management.  I'm guessing these are top-down management values. Every crew started their part of the project with a supervisor on site, and after that, the supervisor would reappear and inform me of the phase progress. There was  excellent communications through all the phases with me,  the property owner.\nIt seems everyone I know has contractor stories that are bad news. Side-Pro is a shining example of how contractors SHOULD perform and communicate... it has been an excellent experience working with them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barbara Bender","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWomEGkMyReZuFU12cacnKGsMgHzUPzby-JE5eIfK9H1Ie9Vq8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed to have old broken shingle siding replaced on the side of my 90 year old house.  I had a good idea of what I wanted and Ryan was great at explaining all the options.  The bid was very thorough.   Billing, scheduling the bid and the work etc was efficient and easy.  The crew came did the job and  cleaned  up immaculately.\nIt looks fantastic and I am confident that it will last another 90 years.  It was not the cheapest bid that I got- but it was the bid and the company I had the most confidence in.  Thank you Side pro.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ginelle M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpkDlCKRlSRIT_roSrVA3YPaqko5PfLYZWPFG4M-jJ65BPimQi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"TLDR: Side Pros has been amazing to work with.  Siding, windows, deck repair, wall repair, and painting is complete!  The end result is fabulous and we are so happy with their quality of workmanship and communication. I highly recommend them.\n\nWe started getting bids to replace our siding in July 2021 when our plans of doing a full remodel were not feasible.  The Side-Pro estimators Russ and Matt were on time, friendly and very thorough when they did the walk through.  I never felt pressured or like they were trying to make a quick sale.  We had a unique circumstance where we needed someone to not only put new siding and paint, but we needed them to repair a wall that was under a deck, replace rotted wood, remove a chimney, replace windows and cut off an overhang that didn't make sense.  They captured all these details and gave me a very thorough proposal with options in just a few days.  Matt continued to respond to me promptly throughout the entire process of selecting, adding and removing items from the proposal and finalizing with the foreman.  There were so many things I had questions on like, \"what kind of WRB options are there, can we add furring strips, should we go with pre-primed or pre-painted Hardy, how will the boards be attached and spaced on the wall? etc\" that they were very patient in answering and educating me on. For things outside of their wheelhouse, they had great recommendations like for Waterproof Decking and Flat Roofing.  After about a month of going back and forth with details, I finally put down my deposit and signed the contract so we could get on the schedule.  It wasn't cheap, because it was a big project, but we wanted to work with someone who had all their contractors in-house on staff, and the pricing was competitive with other siding quotes.\n\nFast forward to January 2022: Duane and Teo walked around the whole house with me and made note of the unique issues we needed fixed.  They made a plan and Teo and his crew showed up on-time at the same time every day and left on time too.  Overall, I really enjoyed working with Teo and his crew.  They are truly masters of their craft.  As someone who is detail oriented and curious, I had so many questions about the process and wanted to make sure that things were going to end up how we wanted them since it was such a big undertaking.  They were super nice and professional about answering all of the questions and made sure to confirm with me about placement of vents and what special things we wanted done.  I was also working from home, so I had the ability to answer questions quickly as they came up.  They were organized and cleaned up the site at the end of each day, my neighbor even commented on how clean it was!  All the workmanship was excellent, and they went above and beyond to make sure we were happy with the result.  I pulled the city permits I needed and they left things ready for inspection which passed every time with no issues.  We had some change orders due to finding surprises with the house (rot, fiberboard sheathing, nonstandard door framing, etc) but they did what we needed them to do for a reasonable additional cost.  They even finished the project earlier than planned and everything went smoothly with the billing and payments.  We had to wait a while for painting, due to the unusually rainy weather we have had this year  but it got completed in July! Thank you Side-Pro Exteriors for being such an awesome, cohesive team and for being clear, detailed and focused on the customer.  It has been a pleasure working with you!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15sSBs9TsIRTrQMdnp9kGdy5a3nzJcpHZ1pq7ReGKu7nN5geXNTSsj5xp65ESuROG3dhFJJqxrwvGa-UoyH6LWnhRgrLl5M7mx769Zd2MTVMsyOTGHi13zSD40cT3RaLti2sZ0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_KrP8Ux2-47boJLsNu_TGS3p9PBorXoMsKi27Ub3umcs2DBqx1YqD-xOL_ZLEPKdWaogVpbC_QKs2ZC2zJ4aE0kQk1kTy6xmvxA79BwqNXz8JPe658HRT2m9cUYnFeIaXwwwOPA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3z9AXCiIHiMCat7p3IG3hfiTRrN5arOpzNG8DEQrc-K2Uyo1thNvb26Vv-O0ldUxr8JC-r06GWvJxWKbc5ewqySOGRR6jUGCOyGgBzlrT92481OnkyXodvmVYX2AZKIcK9_6kB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AeAmgPZaWj4PY2YPWlHvZvudzNwUZHv2765IQqJcLbkCXwunv98XR6MEfSI2TojgZwG48i6xM5y49oNOfUGBibOP-DsqYtEbw1YQnLPMbwsY9A5zUwSiyGBJR36g7tksJuGo3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0_bsGBq6lkC1lwhHuZNlHIn05bdNJfiQich9GqJpLc03cvTTxVeDCBe79I_1UFmQeRmzZCRVvzDseKsqzuz9wV2N47QwzI5p9gSc3Je67VNubdjWnzs6bn3EaHV4y6o2S8_PaF=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2vxm2Yff57nCWe-c5ysZ-RlV9LkIsCZbcD0gKOCW9XLO9UHGNT6zaS3rojq2wT8wKH_H0u_wMHlY5M9zl6pS-Jf9vK72Mz7AvLLVZ8htTRmyAayLXVhV-_heFFMr-1wG4AbxGE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KOcTGhUH8qVMqREROFkEfD5tXmXxIDXBQcdTcE-yMhwnRqO-egGd7_JbNITW_Qs0sQ7iqzPDpYpPsOGnntLdTTaUpyfrSNNQWTCVBs1mawebDwj1glewEZ7pqF9j6sKFVJ9wP=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FwWye-AxSWk2-NdTQwTgepYElGXKspOhnyBtqJRAA5LqJ3kTFmiddCy2SZ1rGWmQF4ez387Q7T0pUah3arkxDreAQMxELNE77xq-kWp4R8i8cvlwuVWW3PY3HbmVgmwQO9opeyg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0z3z133y_ko7sl8yeLCr55Uj