, we had a bunch of issues with our existing gutters so this was a great convenience.\n\nThe project went by rather flawlessly, the dumpster coming in on time and thoughtfully placed out of the way, the crew worked tirelessly for over a week with all the demo, redecking, upgraded venting, and everything else. I had found a new things I wanted addressed, but little did I know they had their own quality assurance crew that addressed everything I was concerned about (mainly some siding that was damaged due to replacement flashing) and found more than I even saw and got the roof and house looking great.\n\nThe gutter crew also did awesome, I had all of this installed in July and now it’s after the atmospheric river and the gutters no longer leaked or backed up, it’s fantastic.\n\nOverall great experience, there were so many checkups and permitting and whatnot that you can’t help but feel taken care of.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jgGjo6lO8-rLOF7PLFEaimgUkoEVtrwMn-LJzaJLNvFqS0gbOCxZqCK35LJpXirF9VoB-yykurAB5-8aMsG-rmeinWP4dUITrqBvI7dRm5eYj68VTxJ5mxTCELcmmlQD4mFc09ncKFOzV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2xQZW3zXjA5ZCxDapsNPnySbuAuOrEYw7v9UmmMpOn-9NeHzNMpmiQngTa3i_YeUCCIq_oCimzwJsJLEy1sWhUYt4FUomRr2xAgs7NDYllS1CeW5-Pq-kXQw4lFM1Kq-dp3TVF4Cc68OEw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vKJfge3nRq9iPQCe7_GWL2MDkVlBymWRklY8sCjvIlBSYLY5wuiYysH2C0rSMsGNl5Mc9d-NBtqS3Up7DzgHfpFJSL3Qp2OUf7EblS_L8mAgHKShdXvXzcxBWim9DsbT5TZTSGsaIXBQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn02oDX6QpjMy32jX1DlIz0JuEhgSkr3jZA6Gl_hZTp_9qhbtf7rbcdxIjvaSxMpQEElRPIRJSICT26vgzA0kY28mPioBCC2fZvXUpiFy9CpE-mhjlVyEJTmq2oVmNyn1jtV5ZNAapA2771i=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lmuP7Dl1zKPEY4FEoVSFzROpMZPi_ACvtmlYo5m-7TrDx_4Mx-7R9kiUr4JdkCFTN4k4iy5A7mw6eU1RHPDiz2o6k5rPoJK5rgWyVPHXTrCicESGkMjaAeZyoKKN8gdw-h2QS974Jl3CX=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-21"},{"Name":"Jeanne Geroux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleu