was a great representative for his company and very nice to deal with. I felt he was being honest at all times with the process.\nI wish I had the reducers to hire his companies I’m sure based on my interaction with him, I would be pleased with the work and would get a quality roof.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"deboleena ganguli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZgeRpSNW7royiIPddCbrr5QrqQxhpl-LPTDev-r31Oq0e1R5P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with our roof installation. The project was completed on time and everything was very well coordinated from start to finish. Elijah was fantastic to work with—he made the estimate process clear and straightforward and walked us through the financing options with ease. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karman Eng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMiu2qLMQ4akpRNKeejncjX2bkdFyzpc_dhCVnI5UxwXbpcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Michael Teiman of North Creek Roofing came out to do an inspection when I discovered my upstairs bathroom had a leak in the ceiling, a sign of a deteriorating roof that needed a replacement. He was a pleasure to work with. Conducted a thorough assessment by going into the attic, testing with a moisture meter, going onto the roof, taking pictures and reviewing them with me. Answered my many questions with patience and provided a fair proposal that reflected what other reputable roofing companies were estimating. Ultimately, we chose a competitor due to referrals but had we chosen North Creek Roofing, our roof replacement project would have been in good hands.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Warwick Dodds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTgLt_F6MQpWSZpsELkoQcMgL4jU-xJEDbTGVkZRN97xt1R57u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had North Creek Roofing replace my roof in February. They were very professional and kept me up to date with any changes on the project. The crew was on site in the morning and ready to go by 9am. They worked all day as long as there was daylight.\nI would recommend North Creek Roofing to anyone looking to get work done on their roof.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe Anglin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLV2IBV2HZtuZxJjuCYOmEecFuYOoMr8GBMg0NqSiA-AirgTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"North Creek Roofing did a fantastic job on our roof replacement.  Professional, friendly and was done from start to finish in under two weeks!!  The crew was great, conducted their work in three days and when they finished there wasn't one piece left on site.  I would recommend North Creek Roofing to anyone in need of a roof.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
