er his review of my home.  We decided on the product and correct path.  He quickly got me a detailed scope and within two weeks the job was done…and that was waiting for weather days in February.  In just a few short days we had a beautiful new roof and the work and detail was just as described.  Quality work and effort from this team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joey Yi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPzt9cmon4tFUrXblzVx9K7H9OZEU8Z7yYHtNr_mk-X1kbSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cornerstone Roofing has the best roofing material along with a 50 yr guarantee. The crew was very professional, very competent and did a great job cleaning up after and leaving everything as it was before they started. Cornerstone came from a friends recommendation who use to work with them. Everything he said was correct about them being very competent and reliable. The roof is the highest point in our house and not self serviceable. It's really important we get a quality reliable roof along with a company that backs their workmanship. And they are really nice people to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yibing Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNIgtx3c_iTEONGBZVgiivvFKDyhM9bNo9B_nogS7h-LfHBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cornerstone did a great job on my roof replacement. They were professional, thorough with the final inspection, and the workmanship warranty gives me great peace of mind. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rucker Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbJkUxwmtMf7TVeApkp2WxTwQF6FdaBFKR7mImglRuBJv7PzfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cornerstone Roofing did a terrific job from start to finish with replacing our roof. I requested 3 free quotes from well-respected roofers and Cornerstone’s was the most prompt and by far the most professional and detailed. And it was considerably less money than the competition. The staff was great at communication throughout  the process, including when needing to reschedule due to rain. And at the end, when the recent rain produced mud splatters on some of our windows, they went above and beyond to arrange cleaning. One note is to make sure to request photos of the finished roof from the manager on the day the roof is QC inspected (easier for submitting proof to insurance, which resulting in a premium deduction).  I highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Divino almeida","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAb6mWw6LWs7Ucx7LWDwuVQPFdeqGCYXmZroHWRfuy8tfNqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent work and very charismatic, I highly recommend him.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1B-x3rXYoz4L_sAtw_lwvrJxIkTHQPXc7BiHbO38m_2j79dux0JC0oTUbIuxwi6B5Od8UyFUvis_teybxjh6QZu4rAVr1AhYvvdshCyVcEkKn8gaehxywXzp7LpmM3TSyHsP6EaIqUoXoN=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn08eEQ-DJ4H0FyM6AOg0Ly87rxA1labDt1nq93ulZ5701GqrGwvzODVXILKJM3JB6yhvGLGwlN5o1mU-GyJipVIunHmJGJ3bNa7cmo4_yj4BXHfIasObNC0eynNdjA4bLWZGNF93Ysgkh7p=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zlgOiTgUtynzu0tqVit3AKKpMtKGiEutUL1pEBO05pTi-7KCe1tVGG_PG0CzUYORr-wsL_kKhZdG19SNuiVxXy-5pewPHek-Pg3zxbayCtjDpqzeWYw8kX7UyizNRRlwg7iv8M7lABl4Y=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-4"},{"Name":"Suraj Kumar Mehta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbMmbVOzjDjCOZXYp3YC6SkPzqnaKzhyowCUwEgeKBEaL4FA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cornerstone Roof delivered exceptional service with professional technicians who inspected thoroughly, explained every step clearly, and completed our roof replacement efficiently with high-quality results.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J TaSsAnI7","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS1MWx-GO0_nHrsTYikSO0Bv8S2GeISGvDz37AFV5w0H3uPToR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really lucked out with these guys.  My neighbor Greg S. highly recomended them and we're glad he did.  The estimator Mike L.  came out with a ladder and he wasn't a salesman or snarky.  He was very matter of fact and to the point, it was quite refreshing. You could tell he's a construction guy and I don't speak \"roofing\" so yeah, heading in the right direction.  He gave us his suggestion for the shingle type and man was he right.  Then he sent us a packet outlining everything with pictures, insurance info, material type etc.  Very professional outfit.  I'll fast forward to completion...So now the new roof is on and it looks 100%...Then they come out again with a magnetic rolling thing to make sure there's no nails around the house...I thought that was pretty cool but at first I was like \"umm why are they here?\"  Then they come out the next day to do a final inspection!?!?  The guy was here for three hours on the roof making sure nothing was missed.  Talk about under promising and over delivering.  Remember that?  Then I get a call from their office verifying our info because they are submitting our warranty info for us.  Yes really!  This is a no brainer-THANKS CSR-we'll probably add pics this summer after a proper paint job.  The before and after will be  night and day.  414 167th PL SE Before CSR picture posted***\nOk here's a few added post install and post High Point Gutters leaf guard recommendation-Paint to follow...","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LjPhVuJJ208Uic3GVfYy532Vbsaxn53GnynI64I8NVgHKDSSfsBdzeQUmLK_zGr6KIxdb5ZAJFsgNfdObDDmnE9C-xUfKd0mSLjHpe1NxiokyZdoTRy0rPZrtjj8q1z3JMUEN=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31JriT1EORRr3QJ4P4PKZCvfNzxg66dnTEijurnEXztc0qSoF8KA4jjdCIhE5WyJrV4iGxgXNu-vjwXWtBGPOkbKFLTuGcpB5ggfIjwQb7pHoXQb4Yy-515fTSkntrLUDmzpMx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DkiqFanqw-Mop5nmgG2HSTPe-3Y3gTUNgVxIOihp5BznlLCs2tjt57PurMYweZLtIRVQwrQb5YdwRdNSwM93eRfhS7Io-h1ZnjR9Ol8dpdu2j21z0a_C7d